\v 26 Wun kwo ngumba njangi l…®gowun. Wan vak n…®ma vat ana nd…®. Ngwutnogwinala t…®ga njambwi nyan ngil…®ga. Njamwi nyanat t…®nda vat ngwuk ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk.  
