\v 28 Kan vak Betani wal…®nja k…®pmamba kak kiyand…®. Wan k…®pma Jodan wal…®nja ndandang…® nat naang…®mba l…®ga k…®pma. Wan kavamba Jon ndinyangu kat ngu yagul…®nd…®.   
\s1 GOD KAT KWUNAT∆óGA NYAN  
\p
\v 29 Nat nandinya Jisas yal…®nd…® maa v…®l…®…® Jon ndinyangu kat wand…®. Nd…® kat av…® ngwula. God kat kwunapmat kwil…®nja sip sip t…®ga vla t…®gand…®. God wand…® maa yalaa l…®gand…®. Ndinyangu aywaa ndinai yil…®ga kavle vak kat God nyingi maawut t…®nda vak kwunakiyand…®.  
\v 30 Wan nyan tak mbut…®wa nyan. Tak wowun. Wuna kwupmba yaiga nyan wuna njambwi nyana. Tak wun kat name kwutapman t…®l…®, nd…® tamba t…®nd…® waa tak mbut…®wun.  
\v 31 Tak Jisas njambwi nyanat t…®nda vat wun ana v…®ga l…®wun. Ngwuk Isrelna n…®mba njambwi nyan yaigand…® waa s…®mogwivat ndinyangu kat ngu yagul…®gowun waa wand…® Jon.   
