\v 3 Wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. M…®n kat wowun. M…®n kat ana woseka waigowun. K…®ta nyan mand…®t kupi nyanat t…®lapman yindeyan God v…®ga l…®ga kava nd…® ana v…®giyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 4 Nikodimas nd…® kat wand…®. Wun tamba av…®t ndu wun. Ng…®ni angamak yigiyowun. Nyimena yaatnat wuleiwun maa nat samba wun kat kwut…® maa mand…®t nyanat t…®giyowun? Waa wagaland…® Nikodimas.   
\p
\v 5 Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. M…®n kat wowun. Ana woseka waigowun. K…®ta nyan ngu yagulapman t…®ga Godna waagan klalapman yindeyan God v…®ga l…®ga kava nd…® ana wuleigiyand…®.  
\v 6 Mbutuwa nyaang…®t kapma vatna. Godna waagano l…®giyaa nyan mand…®t maawut klalaa l…®giyaa nyana. Wan kapma vatna.  
\v 7 Mand…®t kupi nyanat t…®giyam…®n waa waweya vak wutaa ke ng…®paliga ndaga.  
\v 8 Mwuk kwut…®ga vatnogwi k…®ta vatna. Mwut nd…®na yelav…®k vapmba nj…®vwa kwuka yi ya l…®gand…®. Nd…®na mbang…® ana v…®l…®gan…®n. Nd…®na kak m…®na wut…®gan…®n. Godna waagano l…®giyaa nyan mand…®t maawut klaiga nyan nd…®no wungivatna. Nd…®na maawupmba l…®ga vat Godna waagan kwut…®nda nj…®vwa n…®na m…®nimba ana v…®l…®gan…®n waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 9 Jisas wand…® maa Nikodimas wand…®. Wan wama vat anda yamb…®mba yalaa kak kiyalaa t…®giyand…® waa wand…®.   
\p
\v 10 Wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. M…®n Isrel waa Juda wal…®nja n…®mbana njambwi nyan m…®n. M…®n agamak kan vak v…®lapman yil…®gam…®n. M…®n ana nglaapm…®n.  
\v 11 M…®n kat woseka ana waigowun. Wunogwi wuna mbaapma n…®mba kwo ana mbut…®gan…®n. V…®ga wuka l…®na vak m…®na mbut…®gan…®n. Mbut…®na vak wupmak kat ngwuk Juda kai wal…®gangwuk.  
\v 12 K…®pmamba kapmba l…®ga nda kat m…®n kat mbukwun maa m…®na maawut ana yelav…®ka l…®gam…®n. Nyinangwupmba l…®ga nda kat m…®n kat mbukweyan m…®na maawut ana al…®ps…®ga yelav…®ka l…®giyam…®n.  
\v 13 Kan k…®pmamba la k…®ta nyan nyinangwutna vat ana wokelaa v…®nd…®. Nyinangwupmba l…®ga kan k…®pma ngaga yaa k…®ta nyan m…®na v…®ga l…®gand…®. Wan nyan wun wunay…®. Wun ndinyangu kat nyinangwutna vat s…®mogwil…®ga nyan wun.  
\v 14 Tamba la nyan Moses kapamba kwutnja kamboy kwutaa kwo n…®nd…® kava ndinyangu kat kwunapmak katsond…®. Katsonda vak ng…®ni wuno wun kat kwutaa katsogiyandi. Wun ndinyangu kat kwunapmak ya nyan wun.  
\v 15 Wun kat katsondi maa k…®ta nyan v…®laa wun kat t…®ga katsondi waa yelav…®tndeyan wan nyan ana kavle yigiyand…®. Nd…® nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat t…®giyand…®.   
\p
\v 16 God k…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mba kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka l…®nd…®. Ngi kat t…®ga nd…®na nyan wun kat ay wand…® maa laataa yawun. Nat nyan kat wupma ana wand…®. K…®ta nyan wun kat v…®laa wun kat kwunapmat yand…® waa yelav…®tndeyan wan nyan ana kavle yigiyand…®.  
\v 17 Kan k…®pmamba yeta kavle vat yiga yeta n…®mba kat s…®wangat ana God wun kat ay wand…®, yawun. Ndina kavle vak kat kwunapmak kat yawun.  
\v 18 K…®ta nyan wun kat v…®laa wun kat kwunapmat yand…® waa yelav…®tndeyan God nd…® kat ana s…®giyand…®. K…®ta nyan wun kat kai wandeyan wan nyan kat God s…®giyowun waa tamba wand…®. God kwiya nyan k…®ta. N…®ma sakwat ana l…®gand…®. Wun kat kai wanjeyan nd…® kat kwunakiya nat nyan kai. Kavle vat m…®na yiga yet…®l…®giyandi.  
\v 19 Kan k…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mba ndi kavle vat m…®na yiga yet…®l…®gandi. Kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®nja vak kulun walaa l…®ga ngan vla l…®gand…®. Wan nandinya s…®l…®ga nya vla l…®gowun. Ndi kavle vat yiga yet…®vak kat m…®na woviyaguga l…®gandi. Ndi kat s…®mogwi vat yil…®wa apma vak kat v…®laa ndi kai wal…®gandi. Ngi kat t…®ga ndi kat s…®giyowun waa God wand…®.  
\v 20 Kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®ga n…®mba apma vat yiga yet…®l…®ga n…®mba kat waigandi. Apma vat kat v…®laa yet…®l…®na vak kavle vatna waa yelav…®kiyandi. Ngi kat t…®ga wan apma vak kat kai wal…®ngandi.  
\v 21 Apma vat yet…®l…®ga nyan nd…® wan apma vak kat ana vaat…®gand…®. Nat n…®mba wan yiga yet…®nda apma vak kat v…®laa waigandi. Nd…® God waa vapmba yet…®l…®gand…® waa waigandi waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 JISAS JUDIAT YALAA NAT N∆óMBA KAT NGU YAGUND∆ó  
\p
\v 22 T…®ga l…®ga Jisasagwi nd…®na mbaapma n…®mbo Judia wal…®nja n…®ma k…®pmat yindi. Yila yet…®ga wan k…®pmana n…®mba kat ngu yagul…®ndi.  
\v 23 Jon nd…®no nat ngepmamba nat n…®mba kat ngu yagul…®nd…®. Nd…® Inon wal…®nja ngepmamba l…®ga nat n…®mba kat ngu yagul…®nd…®. Wan ngepma Selim wal…®nja ngepma ngwaymba l…®ga ngepma. Wan kavamba ngu n…®ma sakwat t…®nd…®. Kava kavamba la n…®mba wan kavamba ngu yaguvat yal…®ndi.   
\p
\v 24 Wan nj…®mbla Jon kwo l…®nd…®. Ana nd…® kat kwutaa kalabusmba taagandi.  
\v 25 T…®ga l…®ga Jona kwupmba la n…®mbo nat Judo laataa awat sowat waleal…®ndi. Mbang…®na nglambi s…®l…®mbwil…®nja vak kat t…®ga waleal…®ndi.  
\v 26 Waleal…®ndi maa Jona mbaapmamba la n…®mba Jon kat yala wandi. Njambwi nyan, tak Jodan wal…®nja ndandang…® nat naang…®mba m…®nogwinala ta nyan nd…®no ngu yagul…®ngand…®. Tamba nyaang…®t mbut…®ma nyan nd…®no ngu yagul…®nd…® maa n…®ma sakwat n…®mba nd…®na kwupmba yil…®gandi. Ndi n…®na kwupmba ana yal…®gandi waa wandi.  
\v 27 Wandi mala Jon ndi kat wand…®. N…®mamba ke yelav…®kngwa. God nd…® kat apma vak kwondu kwind…® maa n…®ma sakwat nsmba nd…®na kwupmba yil…®gandi. Kwo nyanat t…®gendan ana nd…®na kwupmba yigenja.  
\v 28 Tak ngwuk kat mbukwa nyaang…®t tamba wukngwuk. Wun Kraist ana wun. Wun ndinyangu kat kwunat…®ga nyan ana wun. Wun tat ya nyan wun waa tak ngwuk kat mbukwun.  
\v 29-30 Taagwa klal…®na vak k…®ta vatna. Taagwa klaiga nyan nd…® k…®ta nyan m…®na taagwo woviyagul…®, klaigand…®. Nd…®na nat n…®mba ana kaligandi. Ndi kwo l…®ga klandeya vak m…®na v…®ga l…®giyandi. V…®ga solat s…®giyandi. Nd…® Jisas taagwa klal…®ga nyan vla l…®gand…®. Nd…®na kwupmba n…®ma sakwat nsmba yindi maa v…®laa wun kwo l…®ga v…®laa nd…® kat solat s…®l…®gowun.   
\p
\v 31 Nd…® ny…®nangwupmba l…®ga yaa nyana. Wun k…®pmamba l…®ga nyan wun. Wun k…®pmana vak kat m…®na v…®ga l…®gowun. Nd…® ny…®nangwupmba l…®ga vak kat m…®na v…®ga l…®gand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga wun kat kwulataa njambwi nyanat t…®giyand…®.  
\v 32 Nd…® v…®ga wutnda vak nat n…®mba kat mbut…®gand…®. Ndi wupmak kat kai wal…®gandi.  
\v 33 K…®ta nyan nd…® kat v…®laa nd…® n…®n kat God wand…®, yaa nyana waa yelav…®tndeyan wan nyan God waa nayaang…®t wukiyand…®. God woseka ana wal…®gand…® waa wal…®ga nyan vla l…®gand…®.  
\v 34 God nd…® kat ay wand…® mala yalaa God waa nyaang…®t n…®n kat mbut…®gand…®. God nd…®na waagan ana samat nd…® kat kwind…®. N…®mamba aywaa kwind…®, nd…®namba taqvind…®.  
\v 35 God nd…®na nyan kat v…®laa woviyaguga l…®gand…®. God nd…®na vak nd…®na nyan kat aywaa kwind…®, l…®gand…®.  
\v 36 K…®ta nyan Godna nyan kat v…®laa wun kat kwunapmak yand…® waa wandeyan nd…® nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat t…®ndeya vak klaigand…®. K…®ta nyan Godna nyan kat kai wandeyan nd…® wan apma vak ana klaigand…®. God wan nyan kat tamba wand…®. Nd…® kat s…®giyowun waa tamba wand…® waa wand…® Jon.   
\c 4  
\s1 K∆óG∆óN NGU VLA L∆óGOWUN WAA WAND∆ó JISAS  
\p
\v 1-2 N…®ma sakwat n…®mba ngu yagulaa Jisasna kwupmba yindi. Nd…®na kwupmba ya n…®mbana sakwat Jona kwupmba ya n…®mba kat kwulatndi. Jisas ana ndi kat ngu yagund…®. Nd…®na kwupmba la n…®mba ndi ndi kat ngu yagua. Wan kavamba la ndi Ferisi ngu yagul…®nja vat wutaa ndi kai wandi.  
\v 3 Ngi kat t…®ga Jisas wan kava Judia kwagalalaa Galiliat yind…®.  
\v 4 Judiagwi Galilina n…®nd…®mba la k…®pma Sameria. Galili yivat Sameriamba ta ava yamb…®mba yind…®.   
\p
\v 5 Yiga Sameriamba t…®ga ngepma Saika wal…®nja ngepma wuleind…®. Tamba Jekop nd…®na nyan Josep kat kwiya k…®p ma wan ngepma ngwaymba l…®nd…®.  
\v 6 Wan ngepmamba tamba Jekop ngu k…®ga l…®vak kat wanda waangu t…®nd…®. N…®ma nandinya yiga l…®ga Jisasna mbang…® k…®l…®pang…® yind…®, ngu k…®l…®nja kavamba ndaal…®nd…®.   
\p
\v 7-8 Jisasna kwupmba ya la n…®mba ndi k…®g…®nda klavat ngepma wuleindi. Jisas wumba kapma l…®nd…® maa wan ngnepmamba la taagwa k…®ta ngu tuvak yal…®. Yal…® maa Jisas l…® kat v…®ga wand…®. Wun kat ngu tulaa agwi waa wand…®.  
\v 9 Wand…® maa wat taagwa ng…®paliga ndalaa wuli. M…®n Judana nyan m…®n. Wun Sameriana taagwa wun. An kapma kapma mbaapmamba l…®gali waa wal…®. Kan mbaapmamba l…®ga n…®mba k…®ta kavamba l…®ga ana ngu nao k…®l…®gandi. Wan vak kat Jisas ana wuka v…®ga l…®gand…® waa ng…®paliga ndalaa wal…® nd…® kat.  
\v 10 Wal…® maa Jisas l…® kat wand…®. God ndinyangu kat kwigiyaa vat ny…®n ana v…®ga l…®gany…®n? Wun anda nyan wun t…®ga wun kat ana ny…®n v…®ga l…®gany…®n? V…®ga l…®genyan nj…®mbla nj…®mbla t…®giyaa ngu kat wun kat wagalageny…®n. Wagalagenyan ny…®n kat kwigewun waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 11 Wand…® maa nd…® kat wal…®. Anda vapmba wan ngu tulaa wun kat kwigiyam…®n. Kan waangumba l…®ga ang…®nda s…®vlamba l…®gand…®. Yisenda tumeya nda ana l…®gand…®. Wan njsmbla nj…®mbla t…®giyaa ngu andamba klalaa wun kat kwigiyam…®n.  
\v 12 N…®na walanga Jekop tamba vanda waangua. Vand…® maa nd…®na nyangu, nd…®na kwanda kwanda nda, nd…®, aywaa k…®ngi waangumba ngu k…®ga l…®ndi. Nd…® n…®ma nj…®vwa kwuka waangu vaga ngu kland…®. M…®n nd…® kat kwulapm…®n? Nj…®vwa kwutapman kwo l…®ga ngu m…®na kwigiyam…®n? Waa wal…®.  
\v 13 Jisas at nat njamb…® l…® kat wand…®. K…®ta nyan kan waangumba l…®ga ngu k…®ndeyan ng…®ni nd…®na mbanj…®ge pugiyand…®.  
\v 14 Kwiweya ngu kapma ngua. Kwiweya ngu k…®giyaa nyan ng…®ni ngu k…®vak kat ana yelav…®ka l…®giyand…®. Wan kwiweya ngu k…®l…®nd…®, ana ng…®l…®giyand…®. K…®l…®nd…®, n…®ma ykl…®giyand…®. k…®laa nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vak t…®giyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 15 Wand…® mala taagwa nd…® kat wal…®. Wama ngu wuno wun kat agwi. Ng…®ni kan kava ngu tuvak ana yaigowun. Kwo l…®giyowun waa wal…®.   
\p
\v 16 Jisas l…® kat wand…®. Ny…®na lan kat yiga walaa kiya waa wand…®.  
\v 17 Wand…® maa wal…®. Wun ndu kai wal…®. Wal…® maa Jisas wand…®. ngiyambak wanya wun ndu kai waa.  
\v 18 Ny…®na lan tambanat n…®mba ndi. Mbambala ngy…®nogwinala l…®ga ny…®na ndu ana nd…®. Kwo nyana. Ngi kat t…®ga ngiyambak wanya waa wand…®.  
\v 19 Wand…® maa wal…®. Pagwuga yet…®luwa vak m…®n v…®ga l…®gam…®n. M…®n profet m…®n. V…®ga l…®gowun.  
\v 20 N…®na valanga kan nduwimba God kat kwunaka wal…®ndi. Ngwuk Juda yet…®l…®nja vak kat kai wal…®gangwuk. N…®na angwa ngepma Jerusalem m…®na wuleilaa God kat kwunaka waigangwuk waa wal…®gangwuk waa wal…®.   
\p
\v 21 Wal…® maa Jisas l…® kat wand…®. Ny…®n taagwa awut ny…®la. Wanya nda n…®ma nda angwa nda ana nd…®. Ng…®ni kava kava God kat kwunatnjeya kava kai. Wan wanya nduwimba ana kwunakiyangwuk. Jerusalemba ana kwunakiyandi. Kava kavamba l…®ga God kat maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®giyanguwk.  
\v 22 God n…®n kat kwunapmak kat kwigiya nyan kat yelav…®tapman kwo kwunat…®gangwuk. N…®n Juda wan yaiga nyan kat yelav…®ka kwunat…®gan…®n.  
\v 23 Wan wawa nj…®mbla yaiga nj…®mbla tamba yalaa l…®gand…®. Mbambala k…®pmana kava kat yelav…®tapman n…®ma maawupmba m…®na God kat yelav…®ka l…®giyan…®n. Tamba la n…®mba k…®ta kavamba m…®na God kat kwunat…®ndi. Mbambala wupma ana yigiyan…®n. Tamba la n…®mba God ta vak ana v…®ga l…®ndi. Mbambala n…®n al…®ps…®ga v…®ga l…®giyan…®n. Ngi kat t…®ga s…®mblan ana nd…® kat yelav…®ka l…®giyan…®n. Savagu l…®ga vak m…®na yelav…®ka l…®giyan…®n. Givak vapmba nd…® kat yelav…®kiya n…®mba kat God kwat…®gand…®. Wan maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®njeya vak kat v…®laa ndi kat woviyaguga l…®giyan…®n.  
\v 24 God k…®pmamba l…®ga nda kat ana n…®mamba yelav…®ka l…®gand…®. Nd…® God ndinyanguna kait vla l…®gand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga k…®pmana nda kat yelav…®tapman nd…® kat savagu vapmba yelav…®ka l…®giyan…®n waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 25 Jisas wand…® mala wal…®. Mbambala n…®ma sakwat pagwula l…®ga nda ngil…®ga. God kwigiya nyan Mesaia wal…®na nyan yalaa n…®n kat aywaa s…®mogwigiyand…® waa wal…®.  
\v 26 Wal…® maa Jisas wand…®. Wun Mesaia wun wand…®.   
\p
\v 27 Ngambul…®mb…®t maa nd…®na mbaapmamba la n…®mba ngepmamba l…®ga yalaa mb…®k kat v…®laa ng…®paliga ndalaa yil…®mba waa l…® kat manda kat ngambul…®gam…®n waa ana wandi.  
\v 28 Yandi mala wat taagwa ngu tuvat kiyalaa nda taagalaa ngepmat ndu kat mbupmat wuleil…®.  
\v 29 Ngepma weleilaa ndu kat v…®laa wal…®. Yagwa ngwula. Pagwuga yiga yetuwa vak v…®laa waa nyan ngil…®ga. yagwa yigat. Nd…® kat yiga av…® ngwula. Nd…® Kraist anagand…® waa wal…® wat taagwa.  
\v 30 Wal…® maa wan ngnepma n…®mba n…®ma sakwat Jisas kat v…®vat yindi.   
\p
\v 31 Yal…®ndi maa Jisasna kwupmba l…®ga yaa n…®mba nd…® kat wal…®ndi. Njambwi nyan k…®g…®nda tamba kiyan…®n. Wg…® m…®la wal…®ndi.  
\v 32 Wal…®nd…® maa ndi kat wand…®. K…®luwa k…®g…®nda ngwuk ana v…®l…®ngwuk waa wand…®.  
\v 33 Wand…® maa awat sowat wandi. Nd…® kat k…®g…®nda kandana kwiya waa awat sowat wandi.  
\v 34 Wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Wun kat ay waa nyana nj…®vwa kwuka yil…®weya vak wuna k…®g…®nda vla l…®gand…®.   
\p
\v 35 Kan k…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mba ambugat kat v…®laa wal…®gandi. Mbak aynat yind…® maa k…®g…®nda vagiyan…®n waa wal…®gandi. Ngwuk wupma ke yelav…®ka wangwa. ngwuk tanamb…®ka yite yite av…® ngwula abugat kat. Vanjeya nj…®mbla mbambala wal…®gowun.  
\v 36 Ambugapmba k…®g…®nda val…®ga nyan val…®nda nj…®vwa kat wenga klaigand…®. Ngwutno n…®mbun. Wawa nj…®vwa kwukngweyan nat n…®mba kat nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat t…®ngweya vak ndi kat kwigiyangwuk. Ndi klangwuk maa v…®laa apma wenga klan…®n waa waigangwuk. Ambugat kwut…®nja vak k…®ngiyan. Nat nyan s…®nd…®, nat nyan vaigand…®. Vand…® maa v…®l…®l…®k pal…® k…®ta vak solat s…®giyamb…®t.  
\v 37 Nat nyan ambugapmba s…®k yaagil…®gand…®. Wan mi s…®k kwand…®, nat nyan s…®g…®t…®gand…® waa wal…®gandi. Wan kwukngweya nj…®vwa k…®ta vakna.  
\v 38 Ay wowun maa nat n…®mba nj…®vwa kwutaa kavat wuleilaa nj…®vwa kwut…®ngwuk. Nat n…®mba tua mina s…®k s…®g…®t…®ga n…®mba vla l…®gangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 39 Kan ngepmamba Saikamba la n…®ma sakwat n…®mba ndi Sameria ndi wat taagwa mbuta nyaang…®t wutaa Jisas God wand…®, yaa nyana waa yelav…®tndi. Wat taagwa wal…®l…®. Pagwuga yiga yetuwa nat n…®ma sakwat vak kat v…®laa mbutnd…® waa wal…®l…®.  
\v 40 Sameriamba la n…®mba nd…®nai la kava yalaa n…®na ngepmamba kawiga al…® m…®la waa wagalaga nd…® kat wandi maa nandinya v…®l…®l…®k wumba ndinogwia yet…®nd…®.  
\v 41 Nat n…®ma sakwat n…®mba Jisas waa nyaang…®t wutaa nd…® God wand…®, yaa nyana waa yelav…®tndi.  
\v 42 Yelav…®taa wat taagwa kat wandi. Mbutnya nyaang…®t wutaa Jisas God wand…® yaa nyan waa ana yelav…®t…®n…®n. Nd…®na kwundi wutaa wupma yelav…®tn…®n. Nd…® Kraistna. Nd…® ndinyangu kat kwunapmak yal…®ga nyana waa yelav…®t…®gan…®n waa wandi.   
\s1 JISAS NGEPMA NGEPMA YILAA K∆óTA NYAN KAT KWUNATND∆ó  
\p
\v 43 Nandinya v…®l…®l…®k yind…® maa ndi kat kwagalalaa Galiliat yind…®.  
\v 44 Nd…®na angwa ngepmat ana yind…®. Jisas tak wal…®nd…®. God waa nyaang…®t mbut…®ga nyan ns…®na angwa ngepmamba l…®ga n…®mba kat mbutndeyan ndi ana wukiyandi. Kai waigandi waa Jisas wand…®.  
\v 45 Galili wuleilaa wan kavamba la n…®mba nd…® kat v…®laa wovun yam…®n waa wandi. Tak Jerusalemba la n…®ma pesto kat yinda nj…®mbla Jisas kwunat…®nda n…®ma nj…®vwa kat v…®ndi. Ndino yindi wan pesto kat. Ngi kat t…®ga nd…® kat wovun yam…®n waa wandi.   
\p
\v 46 Galili wuleilaa Kena wal…®nja ngepmat wuleind…®. Wan ngepma tak kwo ngu klalaa n…®ma ngu kwutaa ndinyangu kat kwind…®, k…®ndi. Wan ngepmamba l…®nd…® maa Kapaneam wal…®nja ngepmana njambwi nyan nd…® kat vivat yind…®. Nd…®na nyan yelogwen kat t…®nd…® maa nd…® kat kwagalalaa yand…®.  
\v 47 Jisas Judia kwagalalaa Galiliat tamba yind…® waa wal…®nja nyaang…®t wutaa yand…®. Yalaa wand…®. N…®ma nyan wuna nyan kiya m…®na l…®gand…®. Nd…® kat yaa v…®laa kwunapmba m…®n waa wand…®.  
\v 48 Wand…® maa Jisas wumba la n…®mba kat wand…®. N…®ma nj…®vwa kwunat…®ga nj…®vwa kwutapman yiweyan wun kat v…®laa nd…® God wand…®, yaa nyana waa ana yelav…®kiyangwuk waa wand…®.  
\v 49 Wand…® maa Kapaneamna njambwi nyan wand…® nd…® kat. Kwiyatapman yagwa. Yalapman yimeyan wuna nyan wundumbu yigiyand…® waa wand…®.  
\v 50 Wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. M…®n ay m…®la. M…®na nyan ana kiyalgand…®. Kwo l…®giyand…® waa wand…®. Jisas wand…® maa wutaa ngiyambak wanda woseka ana wand…® waa yelav…®taa yind…®.  
\v 51 Ava yamb…® yil…®nd…® maa nd…®na nj…®vwa kwutaa n…®mba yaa aya yamb…®mba v…®ndi. V…®laa mbutndi. M…®na nyan kwo apma vat t…®gand…® waa mbutndi.  
\v 52 Mbutndi maa ndi kat wagaland…®. Nya angamak t…®nd…® maa nd…®na yelogwen ng…®l…®nd…® waa wagaland…®. Wagaland…® maa mbutndi. Napmba belo bek ng…®l…®nd…® waa mbutndi. Mbutndi mala wutaa yelav…®tnd…®.  
\v 53 Napmba belo bek Jisas wand…®. M…®na nyan ana kiyaigand…® Kwo l…®giyand…® waa wand…® wun kat waa yelav…®tnd…®. Yelav…®taa nd…® God wand…®, yaa nyana waa yelav…®tnd…®. Ngepma yilaa nd…®na ngaymba la n…®mba kat mbutnd…® maa ndino yelav…®tndi.  
\v 54 Jisas Judia kwagalalaa Galiliat wuleilaa wan v…®l…®l…®k wan n…®ma nj…®vwa kwunat…®ga nj…®vwa kwut…®nd…®.   
\c 5  
\s1 JISAS MAN K∆óV∆ó WATNA NYAN KAT KWUNATND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 T…®ga l…®ga Judana pesto v…®vat Jisas Jerusalemat yind…®.  
\v 2 Jerusalem t…®ga sip sip klal…®nja kava ngwaymba waangu ngu l…®gand…®. Wan waangu la kavamba wegwuga mbale tambanat kwutndi, l…®nd…®. Wan nguna s…® Hibruna kwundimba Betesda wandi.  
\v 3 Wan mbalemba yelogwen kat ta n…®mba n…®ma sakwat yiga t…®l…®ndi. Nat n…®mba m…®ni kiyaa n…®mba. Nat n…®mba kaawiya k…®la n…®mba. Yilaa ngu biyaiga vak kat kwaiga mbalemba l…®ndi.  
\v 4 Nat nj…®mbla God wand…® maa ensel ngumba ndand…® maa ngu biyal…®nd…®, v…®laa tak wan ngu wuleigiyaa nyan kwo l…®giyand…®. Yelogwen ng…®l…®giyand…®.  
\v 5 Wumba la k…®ta nyan naambi 38 yelogwen kat t…®l…®nd…®. Nd…® nguat kawiga l…®nd…®.  
\v 6 Jisas nd…® kat v…®laa maawupmba yelav…®tnd…®. Wan nyan naambi n…®ma sakwat yelogwen kat t…®l…®nd…® waa yelav…®taa nd…® kat wagaland…®. Yelav…®ka l…®man m…®na mbang…® kwo l…®ndangat yelav…®ka l…®gam…®n? Waa wagaland…®.   
\p
\v 7 Wand…® maa yelogwen kat ta nyan Jisas kat wand…®. Ngu biyal…®nd…® maa wun kat kwutaa ngumba laagagiyaa nyan kai. Ngu kat yil…®wun maa nat nyan taka yil…®gand…® waa wand…®.   
\p
\v 8 Wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Laap m…®la. S…®ndu kwaal…®ma nda laataa mbaka kwutaa kali waa wand…®.  
\v 9 Jisas wand…® maa wan nyana yelogwen ng…®l…®nd…® maa s…®ndu kwal…®nda nda mbaka kwutaa kalind…®. Wan Jisas nd…® kat kwunatnda nandinya Judana n…®ma nandinya. Nj…®vwa lapman nandinya.   
\p
\v 10 Yelogwen kat kwa nyan s…®ndu kwal…®nda nda kwutaa kalind…® maa Juda nd…® kat v…®laa wal…®ndi. Wan mandana yil…®ma. Mbambala kan nandinya nj…®vwa lapman nandinya. Manda kat n…®na njambiya kat kai walaa s…®ndu kwal…®ma nda kwutaa kalil…®gam…®n waa nd…® kat wal…®ndi.  
\v 11 Wandi maa wand…®. Wun kat kwunata nyan s…®ndu kwal…®ma nda kali waa wun kat wand…® maa kalil…®gowun waa wand…®.  
\v 12 Wand…® maa nd…® kat wagalandi. S…®ndu kwal…®ma nda kwutaa kali waa kandana m…®n kat waa waa wagalandi.  
\v 13 Yelogwen kat kwa nyan Jisasna s…® ana v…®ga wuka l…®nd…®. Jisas nd…® kat kwunataa kwagalalaa yind…®. Wan nd…® kat kwunatnda kavamba n…®ma sakwat n…®mba yisolaa l…®ndi.   
\p
\v 14 Ng…®ni wan nyan God kat kwunat…®nja ngay wuleind…® maa Jisas nd…® kat v…®laa wand…®. M…®n tamba apma vat kwo l…®gam…®n. Kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®ma vak kwagalalaa apma vapmba yet…®giyam…®n. Kavle vat yiga yet…®meyan ng…®ni m…®na mbang…® n…®mamba kavle yigiyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 15 Wand…® maa wan nyan yilaa Juda kat wand…®.  
\v 16 Jisas nd…® kat nj…®vwa lapman nandinyamba yinda vak kat v…®laa Juda Jisas kat kai walaa ndi n…®ma kavle vat yil…®ndi. Nd…® kat vatnyavat yelav…®ka l…®ndi.  
\v 17 Yelav…®ka l…®ndi maa Jisas ndi kat v…®laa wand…®. Wuna nyaek God nd…® mbambala nj…®v…®wa lwit…®gamd…®. Wuno nj…®vwa kwut…®gowun. K…®ta k…®ta kwut…®gali waa ndi kat wand…®.  
\v 18 Wanda nyaang…®t wutaa Juda nd…® kat vatnyavat n…®mamba yelav…®ka l…®ndi. Tak nj…®vwa lapman nandinyamba nj…®vwa kwuta vak v…®laa nd…® kat vatnyavak t…®ndi. Mbambala God wuna nyaekna, k…®ta k…®ta nj…®vwa kwut…®gali wanda vak kat wutaa nd…® kat vatnyavak n…®mamba yelav…®ka l…®ndi. Wun Godno k…®ta njambwi li waa wal…®nda nyaang…®t kat wutaa aki wandi.   
\s1 JISAS ND∆óNA KWONDU NDI KAT S∆óMOGWIND∆ó  
\p
\v 19 Jisas wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Ngwuk kat woseka ana waigowun. Wun Godna nyan avla wuna yelav…®k vapmba ana nj…®vwa kwut…®gowun. Wuna nyaek kwut…®ga nj…®vwa v…®laa kwut…®nda nj…®vwa vla kwut…®gowun. Kwut…®nda nj…®vwa m…®na wun nd…®na nyan kwut…®gowun. Kapma nj…®vwa ana kwut…®gowun.  
\v 20 Wuna nyaek v…®ga l…®ga kwut…®nda vak aywaa wun kat v…®s…®mogwi l…®gand…®. Ng…®ni wun kat n…®ma v…®laa ng…®paliga ndaigangwuk.  
\v 21 God kiyalaa l…®giyaa n…®mba kat wand…® maa laakiyandi. Wuno nd…®na nyan kavle vat ya n…®mba kat wuna maawupmba yelav…®taa wowun mala ndi laataa apma vak yet…®giyandi.  
\v 22 God ndinyangu kat l…®giyaa vak kat v…®laa ana s…®ga nagugiyand…®. S…®ga nagul…®ndeya nj…®vwa wuna lak kwind…®, s…®ga nagugiyowun.  
\v 23 Mbambala ngwuk Godna s…® kwutaa katsol…®gangwuk. Wun Godna nyan wun wuna s…® kwutaa katsongwangat God wun kat s…®ga naguweya nj…®vwa kwind…®. God wand…® maa yawun. Wuna s…® kwutaa katsolapman yingweyan Godna s…® ana kwutaa katsol…®gangwuk.   
\p
\v 24 Ngwuk kat woseka ana waigowun. K…®ta nyan wuna nyaang…®t wutaa God wand…® maa yand…® waa yelav…®tndeyan wan nyan nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat t…®giyand…®. Ng…®ni God nd…® kat ana s…®giyand…®. Wan nyan kiyaa l…®ga laakna nyan vla l…®giyand…®.   
\p
\v 25 Ngwuk kat woseka ana waigowun. Wan yaiga nj…®mbla mbambala tamba yand…®. Mbambala kavle vak ya n…®mba kat wun Godna nyan waa nyaang…®t wutaa ndi kwo apma vak t…®giyandi. Kiyalaa l…®ga laakna n…®mba l…®giyandi.  
\v 26 God kavle vat ya n…®mba kat apma vak ndi kat kwindeya vla wuno Godna nyan wupma kwil…®gowun. God wand…® maa kwil…®gowun.  
\v 27 Wun kat ndinyangu yiga yet…®l…®ga vak s…®ga naguweya kwondu kwind…® God. Wun God yil…®ga vapmba ndinyangu kat yil…®ga nyan wun.  
\v 28 Wan waluwa nyaang…®t wutaa ke ng…®paliga ndangweya ng…®ni kiyalaa waangumba l…®ga n…®mba God waiga nyaang…®t wukiyandi.  
\v 29 Wutaa laakiyandi. Apma vat yeta n…®mba nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat t…®njeya vak klavak laakiyandi. Kavle vak yeta n…®mba nj…®mbla nj…®mbla kavle vat t…®njeya vak klavak laakiyandi.   
\s1 TAK JON MBUTNDA VAK KAT JISAS MBUTND∆ó  
\p
\v 30 Wunai yelav…®ka l…®ga vapmba ana nj…®vwa kwut…®gowun. Wuna nyaek waiga nyaang…®t wutaa ndinyangu kat v…®laa s…®ga nagul…®gowun. Ana s…®mblan s…®ga nagul…®gowun. Wuna maawupmba ana s…®ga nagul…®gowun. Wuna nyaek yelav…®ka l…®ga maawupmba s…®ga nagul…®gowun. Nd…® wand…® maa yawun.   
\p
\v 31 Wun njambwi nyan wun wuna s…® avla waweyan wan ana nglaatnd…®.  
\v 32 Njambwi nyan tuwa vat nat nyan mbut…®gand…®. Nd…® wan nyan woseka wal…®ga nyan ana nd…®.   
\p
\v 33 V…®l…®gowun. Njambwi nyanat tuwa vat nat nyan tamba mbutnd…®. Nd…®na s…® Jon. Tak wangwuk maa nat n…®mba Jon kat wagalavat yindi. Wagalandi maa njambwi nyanat tuwa vak Jon mbutnd…® ndi kat.  
\v 34 Kan k…®pmana n…®mba njambwi nyanat tuwa vat wanjeyan wan n…®ma vat ana nd…®. Jon nd…® apma nyana waa ngwuk yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk. Ngi kat t…®ga Jon njambwi nyanat tuwa vak tamba mbutnd…® waa ngwuk kat mbukwun. Mbambala mand…®t maawut s…®kngwangat ngwuk kat wowun.  
\v 35 Jon ya sagalanja lam vla l…®nd…®. Nd…®nai waa nyaang…®t kat wutaa samat woviyaguga l…®ngwuk.   
\p
\v 36 Njambwi nyanat tuwangat Jon wal…®ga nyaang…®t kat kwulakiya nyaang…®t ngil…®ga. Wuna nyaek kwind…®, kwutuwa nj…®vwa kat v…®laa njambwi nyanat tuwa vak v…®l…®gangwuk. God wand…®, yaa nyan wun tuwa vak kat v…®l…®gangwuk.  
\v 37 Wuna nyaek wun kat ay waa nyan nd…®no njambwi nyanat tuwa vak ngwuk kat mbut…®nd…®. Ngwuk nd…®na kwundi ana wuka l…®gangwuk. Kavle maawut yelav…®ka nd…®na s…® wuka nd…®na m…®ndama ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk.  
\v 38 Nd…®nai waa nyaang…®t kat ngwutna maawupmba ana yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk. Nd…® ay wand…®, yaa nyan kat nd…® kat kai wangwuk.  
\v 39 God wand…®, tawmba la n…®mba p…®l…®wukna nyaang…®t v…®ga nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vak t…®ngweya vak kat kwat…®gangwuk. Wan tamba p…®o…®wukna n…®mba wun kat p…®l…®wutndi. Ngwuk ana v…®ga wuka l…®gangwuk?  
\v 40 Nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat yet…®ngweya vak wunamba klavak kat kai wangwuk.   
\p
\v 41 Wuna s…® kwutaa katsongwangat kan nyaang…®t ngwuk kat ana mbut…®gowun.  
\v 42 Ngwuk kat v…®ga l…®gowun. God ndinyangu kat woviyaguga l…®gangwuk. V…®l…®gowun. Nat n…®mba kat woviyaguga l…®ngwangat ngwuk kat kan nyaang…®t mbut…®gowun.  
\v 43 Wun nyaekna s…®mba yalaa l…®wun maa wun kat kai wal…®gangwuk. Ng…®ni nat nyan nd…®na s…®mba avla yalaa l…®ndeyan ana nd…® kat kai waigangwuk.  
\v 44 God k…®ta nyana s…® kwutaa katsondeya vak ngwuk ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Ngwuk awat sowat ngwutna s…® m…®na kwutaa katsol…®gangwuk. Ngi kat t…®ga God k…®ta nyana s…® kwutaa katsol…®nda vak ngwuk ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Wan vak n…®ma vakna. Wan n…®ma vak kat kai walaa njambwi nyanat tuwa vak ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk.  
\v 45 God kat yiga v…®laa ndi kavle vat yindi waa ngwuk kat ana waigowun. N…®na njambwi nyana waa wal…®ngwa nyan Moses nd…® God kat v…®laa ndi kavle ak yindi waa ngwuk kat mbut…®nd…®.  
\v 46 Moses waa la kwundi wukengwan wunai wal…®ga kwundi wukengwuk. Nd…® tamba la nyan Moses wuna s…® waa p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\v 47 P…®l…®wutnda nyaang…®t v…®laa wupmak kat kai wangweyan wunai wal…®ga nyaang…®t ana wukiyangwuk. Kapma kapma nyaang…®t ana nd…®.   
\c 6  
\s1 JISAS 5,000 N∆óMBA KAT AO KWIND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 T…®ga l…®ga Jisas Galili waa Taibirias wal…®nja sak nat naang…® satnat yind…®.  
\v 2 Yind…® maa n…®ma sakwat n…®mba nd…®na kwupmba yindi. Yelogwen kat ta n…®mba kat kwunat…®nda n…®ma nj…®vwa kat v…®laa yingi.  
\v 3 Yindi maa nd…®na mbaapma n…®mbona nduwiat wokendi. Wokelaa ndaa kwo l…®ndi.  
\v 4 Pasova wal…®nja Judana pesto ngway toland…®.  
\v 5 Ndaa l…®ga n…®ma sakwat n…®mba nd…® kat yal…®nja vak kat v…®l…®nd…®. V…®laa Filip wand…®. Kan yalaa l…®ga n…®mba kat ndinai k…®giyaa nao andamba klaigan…®n waa wand…®.  
\v 6 Jisas Filip ngambugiyaa vak kat wupmat wand…®. k…®g…®nda kat ana n…®mamba yelav…®t…®dn…®. Ng…®ni yindeya vak tamba nd…® yelav…®ka l…®nd…®.   
\p
\v 7 Wand…® maa Filip wand…®. 200 dola yaagilaa klaneya bret-nao ana al…®ps…®giyand…®. N…®ma sakwat n…®mba ana al…®ps…®ga k…®giyandi waa wand…®.  
\v 8 Wand…® maa Jisasna mbaapmamba la nat nyan Pitana yakwa nyan Endru wutaa wand…®.  
\v 9 Mat kwand…® nyan kiyaa bret-nao tambanat kami v…®l…®l…®k ngil…®ga. Wan n…®ma sakwat n…®mba k…®ngi k…®g…®ndamba ana al…®ps…®giyand…® waa wand…® Endru.  
\v 10 Wand…® maa Jisas nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat wand…®. Kwand…® yuwimba nda al…® ngwula waa ndi kat awa ngwula waa wand…® maa yiga wandi, ndaa l…®ndi. Ndaa la nduna sakwat 5,000.   
\p
\v 11 Jisas bret-naogwi kamio klaa kwutaa God kat s…®vu k…®laa l…®mbaga nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat kwind…®, ndi yiga wan yalaa la n…®mba kat kansaga kwindi. N…®ma sakwat k…®vak yelav…®ka la nyana n…®ma sakwat k…®l…®nd…®. Samat ka nyan wun ngiyambak kuwa wand…®, ana nd…® kat n…®ma sakwat kwindi.  
\v 12 Al…®ps…®ga k…®gan…®n wandi maa Jisas nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat k…®lamb…®nja nao kami klalaa mbanimba naanga ngwula. Kk…®lamb…® k…®g…®nda kwo l…®ndeya vak ana nglaatnd…® waa wand…®.  
\v 13 Wand…® waa yiga naangandi. Mbani tamba v…®li kiyeli v…®l…®l…®k naangandi wan k…®lamb…® k…®g…®nda.   
\p
\v 14 Nao k…®laa kwo l…®ga Jisas kwukna nj…®vwa kat va n…®mba yelav…®ka ngambundi. God n…®n kat kwiya profet, kawiga l…®na nyan k…®ngiyan waa yelav…®ka ngambul…®ndi.  
\v 15 Ndi Jisas kat kwutaa n…®ma kingat taagagiyan…®n waa yelav…®tnja vak Jisas v…®laa ndi kat kwagalalaa nat nduwiat kapma yind…®.   
\s1 JISAS NGU TAGUMBA VEIGA YIND∆ó  
\p
\v 16 Ngan yand…® mala Jisasna mbaapma n…®mba t…®vagawiat ndaindi.  
\v 17-18 Ndailaa njaamb…®t kulaa Kakpaneam wal…®nja ngepmat yindi. Yiga l…®ga Jisas kat kuvat kawilaa Jisas kat samat kawiga l…®ga tamba ngana walaa Jisas ta kava kwagalalaa val…®gendi.  
\v 19 Ngusa kaga 3 mail o 4 mail yiga l…®ga Jisas ngu tagumba veiga yal…®nd…®, v…®ndi. Jisas yil…®lnja njaamb…®tna ngway yand…®, v…®laa vaatndi.  
\v 20 Ndi kat wand…®. Wunay…®. Ngwuk ke vaaka wand…®.  
\v 21 Wand…® maa v…®laa vaaka l…®nja vak kwagalalaa nd…® kat kwutaa njaamb…®pmba kund…®. Kund…® maa njaamb…®t kwiyatapman avla yind…®, yinja ngepmamba kawindi.   
\s1 JISAS KAT KWAT∆óNDI  
\p
\v 22 Yindi maa nat nandinya kwagalalaa yinja kavamba la n…®mba Jisas kat kwat…®ndi. Nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba vaala kulaa val…®genja vak tamba v…®ndi. Jisas ndinogwinala ana yind…®, v…®ndi. Jisas ndinogwinala ana yind…®, v…®ndi.  
\v 23 Taibirias wal…®nja ngepmamba l…®ga ya njaamb…®t anagand…® kulaa kalia waa yelav…®ka l…®ndi. Jisas God kat s…®vu k…®laa ndi kat nao kami kwinda kava kat Taibiriasmba yaa la njaamb…®t v…®g…®va yil…®ndi.  
\v 24 Jisasogwi nd…®na mbaapmamba la n…®mbo ana l…®gandi waa walaa njaamb…®t kulaa Kapaneasm Jisas kat kwaka val…®gendi.   
\s1 JISAS BRET-NAO VLA L∆óGA VAK  
\p
\v 25 Yiga l…®ga sak t…®vagawimba l…®nd…®, v…®laa wagalandi. Njambwi nyan anda s…®va kupma yam…®n waa wagalandi.  
\v 26 Wagalandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Njambwi nyanat tuwa vak n…®ma nj…®vwa kwuka s…®magawun, v…®laa ana kupma yangwuk. Ngwuk kat kwiwa nao kami k…®ga yaat tata vak kat t…®ga yelav…®taa yangwuk.  
\v 27 Kan k…®pmana k…®g…®nda klavak kat ke n…®mamba yelav…®ka n…®ma nj…®vwa kwuka. nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat t…®ngweya vak klavak kat m…®na yelav…®ka n…®ma nj…®vwa kwuka yet…® ngwula. Wun Godna vak ndinyangu kat kwil…®ga nyan wun. Wan apma vak ngwuk kat kwigiyowun. Tak God wun kat wand…®. Wan nyan wuna nyana waa wand…®. ngi kat t…®ga Godna apma vat kwil…®gowun waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 28 Jisas wand…® maa nd…® kat wagalandi. God n…®n kat kwiya nj…®vwa anda nj…®vwa. Anda vapmba wan nj…®vwa kwukiyan…®n waa wagalandi.  
\v 29 Wagalandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. God kwiya nj…®vwa k…®ngiyan. God wand…®, yawun. Yaa nyan wun. Wupma ngwula maawupmba yelav…®kngweyan God waa nj…®vwa kwukiyangwuk waa wand…®.   
\p
\v 30 Wand…® maa nd…® kat wandi. God wand…®, yaa nyan t…®ma vak anda n…®ma nj…®vwa kwut…®ma nj…®vwa v…®laa God wand…® yaa nyan m…®n waa maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®giyan…®n.  
\v 31 Tak bret-nao taamba kwutaa l…®mbaga kwil…®ma vak kupi vak ana nd…®. Tamba n…®na ngwat walanga kwo kavamba l…®ga mana wal…®nja nao ndino k…®l…®ndi. Ndina yaat taatnd…®. Moses nyinangwupmba l…®ga ndailaa nao ndi kat kwind…®, klalaa k…®l…®ndi waa wandi.   
\p
\v 32 Wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Ngwuk kat ana woseka waigowun. Moses nyinangwutna nao ana nd…® ndi kat kwind…®. Kwil…®nda nao ana nd…® ndi kat kwind…®. Kwil…®nda nao k…®pmamba vla l…®ga nda. Wuna nyaek God nyinangwupmba la nao nd…®nay…® kwiya.  
\v 33 God kwiya nao ndu nyana. K…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mba kat apma vat t…®njeya vak kwivak nyinangwupmba l…®ga ngaga yaa nyana. Nd…® God kwiya nao vla l…®ga nyana waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 34 Wand…® maa wandi. Njambwi nyan n…®n kat kwivat wama nao nj…®mbla nj…®mbla n…®n kat agwi m…®la waa wandi.  
\v 35 Wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Ndinyangu kat apma vak kwil…®ga nao vla l…®ga nyan wunay…®. K…®ta nyan kwiluwa apma vak klandeyan ng…®ni nat vak klavak kat ana yelav…®kiyand…®. K…®ta nyan wun kat v…®laa God wandi, yaa nyana waa yelav…®tndeyan ng…®ni nat njambwi nyan kat ana kwaka yiga v…®giyand…®.   
\p
\v 36 Ngwuk kat wowun. Ngwuk wupma kai. Kwutuwa n…®ma nj…®vwa v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Ngwuk wupma kai. Kwutuwa n…®ma nj…®vwa v…®ga l…®gangwuk. God wand…®, yaa nyana waa ana wun kat yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk.  
\v 37 Wuna nyaek wun kat kwiya n…®mba aywaa wuna kwupmba yaigandi. Wun kat yandi maa ndi kat ana kai waigowun.  
\v 38 Nyinangwupmba l…®ga ngaga wawan wuna maawupmba yelav…®ka nj…®vwa kwupmak ana yawun. Wun kat ay waa nyan yelav…®ka l…®ga vapmba nj…®vwa kwupmak yawun.  
\v 39 Wuna nyaek yelav…®ka l…®ga vak k…®ngiyan. Wun kat kwinda n…®mba aywaa ndi kat kwutaa l…®giyowun. K…®ta nyan ana s…®l…®wokiyand…® wun kat. Ng…®ni yaiga nandinya wowun maa ndi kiyalaa laakiyandi.  
\v 40 Wuna nyaek yelav…®ka l…®ga nat vak k…®ngiyan. K…®ta nyan wun Godna nyan wun kat v…®laa God wand…®, yaa nyana waa yelav…®tndeyan nd…® nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat t…®ndeya vak kland…®, ng…®ni yaiga nj…®mbla wowun maa kiyalaa laakiyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 41 Jisas wand…® maa Juda awat sowat waleaga wandi. Wun nyinangwupmba l…®ga God kwiya nao vla l…®ga nyan wun waa manda kat wal…®gand…® waa waleaga l…®ga wandi.  
\v 42 Wan nyan Jisas. Nd…®na nyaek Josep. Nd…®na nyaek ny…®me kat v…®ga l…®gan…®n. Nd…® manda kat nyinangwupmba yawun wal…®gand…® waa waleaga l…®ga wandi.   
\p
\v 43 Waleaga l…®ga wal…®ndi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Awat sowat ke walea l…®ngwa.  
\v 44 Kwo nyan wuna kwupmba ana yaigand…®. Wuna nyaek yagwa waa wanda nyan wuna kwupmba yaigand…®. Yand…® maa ng…®ni yaiga nj…®mbla wowun ma kiyalaa laakiyand…®.  
\v 45 Tamba la profet God waa nyaang…®t tamba p…®l…®wutndi.  
\li1 God ndinyangu kat apma vat yelav…®ka l…®njeya vat  
\li1 s…®mogwigiyand…®  
\p waa p…®l…®wutndi tamba. Ngi kat t…®ga wuna nyaeknanamba apma vak yelav…®ka l…®njeya vat klal…®ga n…®mba wuna kwupmba yaigandi.   
\p
\v 46 Ngwut ngwutna k…®ta nyan wuna nyaek t…®ga vat nd…®na m…®ndama ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk. God t…®ga kavamba l…®ga yaa nyan wun. Wun v…®ga l…®gowun.  
\v 47-48 Ngwuk kat ana woseka waigowun. K…®ta nyan wun kat v…®laa nd…® God wand…®, yaa nyana waa yelav…®tndeyan nd…® nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat kwil…®ga nyan wun.  
\v 49 Ngwutna ngwat walanga kwo n…®nd…® kavamba l…®ga mana wal…®nja nao k…®ga l…®ga kiyal…®ndi.  
\v 50 Nyinangwupmba l…®ga yand…®, mbut…®wa nao k…®ta nyan k…®ndeyan nd…® ana kiyaigand…®.  
\v 51 Nyinangwupmba l…®ga yaa apma vat kwil…®ga nao vla l…®gowun. K…®ta nyan wunamba wan nao klalaa k…®ndeyan nd…® apma vat nj…®mbla nj…®mbla t…®ndeya vat klaigand…®. Ndinyangu kat kwil…®wa wuna mbang…® nao vla l…®gand…®. Ndinyangu apma vat t…®njangat kwil…®gowun waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 52 Jisas wand…® maa Juda awat sowat waleaga l…®ga wal…®ndi. Anda vapmba ind…®na mbang…®na w…®mbu nao vla l…®nd…®, k…®giyan…®n waa wal…®ndi.   
\p
\v 53 Wal…®ndi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Ngwuk kat ana woseka waigowun. Wun Godna vak klalaa nginyangu kat kwil…®ga nyan wun. Wuna mbang…®na w…®mbogwi yelogweno klalapman yigiyaa n…®mba nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat t…®njeya vat ana klaigandi.  
\v 54 K…®ta nyan wuna mbang…®na w…®mbogwi yelogweno klandeyan nd…® nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat t…®ndeya vat klaigand…®. Ng…®ni yaiga nj…®mbla wowun maa kiyalaa laakiyand…®.  
\v 55 Wuna mbang…®na w…®mbu k…®g…®nda vla l…®gand…®. Wuna yelogwen k…®l…®ngwa ngu vla l…®gand…®.  
\v 56 Wuna mbang…®na w…®mbogwi yelogweno klal…®ga nyan wuna mbaapmamba l…®giyand…®. Nd…®na maawupmba t…®giyowun.  
\v 57 Wuna nyaek nyinangwupmba l…®ga wun kat wand…® maa ngaga yawun. Kan k…®pma yalaa yet…®nda vla yet…®giyand…®.  
\v 58 Nyinangwupmba l…®ga yaa bret-nao wunay…®. Ngwutna ngwat walanga tamba mana wal…®nja nao k…®ga l…®ga kiyal…®na vla wuna w…®mbu k…®giyaa n…®mba wupma ana kiyaigandi. Nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vatt…®l…®giyandi waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 59 Wan nyaang…®t Kapaneamba l…®ga Juda yisola l…®nja ngaymba l…®ga mbut…®nd…® Jisas.   
\s1 APMA VAK KWIL∆óGA NYAANG∆óT JISAS MBUTND∆ó  
\p
\v 60 Nd…®nai mbuta nyaang…®t wutaa nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba wutaa wandi. Mbut…®nda nyaang…®t wupmak kat n…®n n…®mamba ana woviyaguga l…®gan…®n. Wan nyaang…®t wupmak kat anagan…®n kai waiga waa wandi.  
\v 61 Kai wal…®nja vak kat Jisas nd…®na maawupmba yelav…®taa wand…®. Mbut…®wa nyaang…®t kat wupmak kat ngwuk kai wangwuk?  
\v 62 Wun God kwiya vat klalaa ndinyangu kat mbut…®ga nyan wun. K…®pma kwagalalaa nyinangwut wokewun mala kan wokeweya vat kat kai waigangwuk?  
\v 63 Maawupmba yelav…®t…®ngwa vak wan apma vat n…®ma vatna. M…®nimba v…®l…®ngwa vat wan n…®ma vat ana nd…®. Mat vatna. Ngwuk kat mbut…®wa nyaang…®t wutaa klangweyan apma maawut yet…®l…®ngweya vat klaigangwuk.  
\v 64 Ngwula nat n…®mba wun kat v…®laa kai wal…®gandi waa wandi Jisas. Jisas kat kai wala n…®mbowi kamwin kwiya nyano Jisas tamba v…®ga l…®nd…®.  
\v 65 Wan vak v…®ga l…®gandi kat wand…®. K…®ta 65 nyan wuna kwupmba kwo ana yaigand…®. Wuna nyaek wand…® maa yaigand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 66 Wand…® maa nd…®na kwupmba la n…®ma sakwat n…®mba nd…® kat kai waa kwagalalaa yind…®. Nd…®nogwinala ana k…®ta vat yet…®ndi.   
\s1 JISAS NJAMBWI NYANAT T∆óNDA VAK PITA MBUTND∆ó  
\p
\v 67 Yindi maa wan tamba v…®li kiyeli v…®l…®l…®k n…®mba kat wagaland…®. Ngwutno ndinogwinala wun kat kai waa kwagalalaa ygiyangwuk waa wagaland…® ndi kat.   
\p
\v 68 Wagagland…® maa Pita nd…® kat wand…®. Njambwi nyan m…®n kat kwagalalaa anda nat nyan kat yigiyan…®n. Yineya nat nyan ana l…®gand…®. Mut…®ma nyaang…®t nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat t…®neya vat n…®n kat v…®s…®mogwil…®gand…®.  
\v 69 M…®n Kraist m…®n. M…®n Godna nyan m…®n. M…®n God yet…®l…®ga vak vla yet…®l…®gam…®n waa maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®gan…®n waa wand…® Pita.   
\p
\v 70 Wand…® maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Ngwuk tamba v…®li kiyeli v…®l…®lk pal…® ngwuk kat wowun maa wuna kwupmba yangwuk. Ngwut aywaa apma maawut t…®ga n…®mba m…®na ana l…®gangwuk. Ngwutna k…®ta nyan Seten kwiya maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®ga nyana waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 71 Judas Iskeriot Saimona nyan kat wupma wand…®. Nd…® tamba v…®li kiyeli v…®l…®l…®k ta n…®mbana k…®ta nyana. Nd…® ng…®ni Jisas kat s…®giyaa n…®mba kat kamwin kwivat ta nyana.   
\c 7  
\s1 JISASNA YAKWA N∆óMBA PESTO KAT YINDI  
\p
\v 1 T…®ga l…®ga Jisas Galilimba yi ya yet…®nd…®. Judiamba l…®ga njambwi Juda nd…® kat vatnyavat t…®ndi. Ngi kat t…®ga judia kwagalalaa Galilimba yiga yet…®nd…®.  
\v 2 Judana pesto tamba ndina ngwat ndu haus sel kwutna yet…®la nj…®mbla kat yelav…®t…®nja pesto tamba ngway toland…®.  
\v 3 Ngi kat t…®ga nd…®na yakwa n…®mba nd…® kat wandi. Wan kava kwagalalaa judiat ay m…®la. Judiamba l…®ga m…®na mbaapmamba la n…®mba n…®ma nj…®vwa kwut…®ma nj…®vwa v…®giyandi.  
\v 4 Kwut…®ma nj…®vwa pagwumeyan ana nglaatnd…®. Kapmba kwupmeyan apma vala. N…®ma sakwat n…®mba v…®giyandi. Njambwi nyan t…®ma vak v…®laa yelav…®ka l…®giyandi waa wandi.  
\v 5 Ndi kwo wandi. Njambwi nyanat t…®dna vat ana v…®ga l…®ndi nd…®na yakwa n…®mba.  
\v 6 Wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Njambwi nyanat t…®wa vat ndi kat s…®mogwiweya nj…®mbla wata ana ngway tolaga l…®gand…®. Pesto kat yilaa ngwutna m…®ndama ndi kat v…®s…®mogwingweya vat n…®ma vat ana nd…®.  
\v 7 Wundi Juda ngwuk kat ana kai wal…®gandi. Wun kat kai wal…®gandi. Ndi kat v…®laa ngwuk kavle n…®mba ngwuk waa wowun maa wun kat kai wal…®gandi.  
\v 8 Ngwuk kapma ay ngwula. Wan pesto l…®ga nj…®mbla wun ana yigiyowun. Njambwi nyanat t…®wa vat ndi kat v…®s…®mogwiweya nj…®mbla ana ngway tolaga l…®gand…® waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 9 Jisas ndi kat wand…® maa yindi maa Jisas kapma Galilimba l…®nd…®.   
\s1 JISAS PESTO KAT PAGWUGA YILAA NYAANG∆óT MBUT∆óND∆ó  
\p
\v 10 Nd…®na yakwa n…®mba pesto kat yindi maa nd…® kapma pagwuga ndina kwupmba yind…®.  
\v 11 Pestomba la ndi Juda Jisas kat kwaka nd…® andamba l…®gand…® waa wal…®ndi.  
\v 12 N…®ma sakwat n…®mba nd…®na s…® waga awat sowat waleal…®ndi. Nat n…®mba nd…® woseka wal…®ga nyana. Kavle nyana waa wal…®ndi.  
\v 13 Walea l…®ga wal…®nja vak kapmba m…®na ana wal…®ndi. pagwuga m…®na wal…®ndi. Juda kat vaaka pagwuga m…®na wal…®ndi.   
\p
\v 14 Pesto la n…®nd…® nandinya Jisas God kat kwunat…®nja ngay wuleilaa nyaang…®t mbut…®nd…®.  
\v 15 Mbut…®nda nyaang…®t wutaa Juda ng…®pali walaa wand…®. Manda kat v…®l…®nja vat kaawa viyaga ngambu l…®nja vak wut…®nd…®. Nd…® skul ya nyan ana nd…® waa ng…®pali walaa wal…®ndi.  
\v 16 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Mbut…®wa nyaang…®t wuna nyaang…®t ana nd…®. Wun kat ay waa nyana nyaang…®tna.  
\v 17 K…®ta nyan wun kat ay waa nyan yelav…®ka la maawut vla yelav…®ka l…®ndeyan mbut…®wa nyaang…®t wutaa God kwiya nyaang…®tna? E. K…®pmamba l…®ga nyana nyaang…®tna waa s…®ga naguga yelav…®kiyand…®.  
\v 18 Wuna nyaang…®t mbukewan. Wupma ana mbut…®gowun. Wun kat ay waa nyana s…® kwutaa katsongwangat mbut…®gowun. S…®mblan ana mut…®gowun. Kavle vat ana yiga yet…®l…®gowun.   
\p
\v 19 Ngwula tamba la nyan Moses ngwuk kat nyaang…®t mbuka njambiya taagand…®. Nd…®nai kwiya njambiyana vapmba ana yiga yet…®l…®gangwuk. Nd…® Moses kwiya njaambiyamba ana yet…®l…®gand…®. Nd…® kat vatnyagiyan…®n waa manda kat wun kat wal…®gangwuk waa wagaland…®.  
\v 20 Wagaland…® maa ndi wandi. Kavle waagan m…®n kat tavind…® maa m…®n apma maawut ana yelav…®ka l…®gam…®n. M…®n kat ana vatnyavat t…®gan…®n waa wandi.  
\v 21 Wandi maa Jisas wand…®. Nj…®vwa lapman nandinyamba n…®ma nj…®vwa k…®ta kwukwun maa v…®laa manda kat wupma yind…® waa wangwuk wun kat.  
\v 22 Mbang…® p…®t…®ngwa vak Mosesnanamba klangwuk. Tamba la n…®mba Mosesna ngwak walanga ndino mbang…® p…®t…®ndi. Nj…®vwa lapman nandinyamba mbang…® p…®t…®ngwuk.  
\v 23 Nj…®vwa lapman nandinyamba k…®ta nyan kat samat kwunapmak nd…®na mbang…® p…®taa n…®n Moses waa nj…®vwa lapman nandinyana njambiya kat ana kai wan…®n waa wal…®gangwuk. Wun nj…®vwa lapman nandinyamba yelogwengat ta nyan kat aywaa kwunakwun maa v…®laa wun kat kai wangwuk. Manda kat.  
\v 24 M…®nimba v…®ngwa vak kat m…®na yelav…®taa s…®ga nagungweyan ana s…®mblan s…®ga nagugiyangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 JISAS ND∆ó KRAISTNA ANAGAND∆ó WAA WAL∆óNDI  
\p
\v 25 Nat n…®mba Jerusalemna n…®mba Jisas kat v…®laa wal…®nd…®. Wan vatnyavat t…®nja nyan k…®ngiyan? E? Kai.  
\v 26 Nd…® ana pagwuga mbut…®gand…®. Kapmba mbut…®gand…® Judana njambwi n…®mba nd…® kat v…®laa nd…® n…®n kat kwunapmak God wand…®, yaa nyana waa anagandi yelav…®kna.  
\v 27 Nd…® wan nyan Kraist ana nd…®. Wan nyana angwa ngepma v…®ga l…®gan…®n. Kraistna angwa ngepma ana v…®ga l…®giyan…®n waa nat n…®mba wal…®ndi.   
\p
\v 28 Wandi maa Jisas God kat kwunat…®nja ngay wuleilaa laataa ndi kat nyaang…®t mnbut…®nd…®. Wuna m…®ndama v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Wuna angwa ngepma wuka l…®gangwuk. Wun kat ay waa wan nyan kat ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Wun kat ay waa wan nyan kat ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Avla ana yawun. Nd…® wand…® maa yawun.  
\v 29 Nd…®na m…®ndama v…®ga l…®gowun. Nd…®nai l…®ga kavamba l…®ga yawun. Ay wand…® maa yawun waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 30 Wand…® maa nat n…®mba nd…® kat kwutaa kalilaa kavle vat yivat wandi. Nd…® kat ana kwutndi. Nd…® kat kwutnjeya nj…®mbla ana ngway tolaga l…®nd…®.  
\v 31 Nat n…®mba nd…® kat v…®laa nd…® Kraistna. Nd…® God wand…® maa yaa nyana waa yelav…®taa wandi. Ng…®ni nat nyan yalaa kwut…®nda n…®ma nj…®vwa kat ana kwulakiyand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga wan nyan God kwiya nyana waa wandi.   
\s1 WANDI MAA PLISMAN JISAS KAT KWUPMAT YINDI  
\p
\v 32 Wundi n…®mbandi awat sowat waleaga wal…®nja vak Ferisi wutaa Ferisio God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mbo wandi maa plisman Jisas kat kwupmat yindi.  
\v 33 Nd…® kat kwupmat yandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. N…®ma nj…®mbla ana ngwutnogwinala l…®giyowun. samat t…®ga ngwuk kat kwagalalaa wun kat ay waa wan nyan t…®ga kavat yigiyowun.  
\v 34 Yiwun maa wun kat kwaka v…®levilaa l…®giyangwuk. Yiwa kava ngwut ana yaigangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 35 Wand…® maa Juda ndi awat sowat wal…®ndi. Anda kaya yinda nd…® kat kwaka v…®levilaa l…®giyan…®n. Kava kavamba l…®ga Juda kat ndi kat v…®vat anagand…® yiga. Juda ana ndi nat n…®mba l…®ga kava kavat anagand…® yiga. Yilaa ndi kat nyaang…®t s…®mogwigiyaa.  
\v 36 Wun kat kwaka v…®levilaa l…®giyangwuk waa manda kat wand…®. Yiwa kava ana yaigangwuk waa manda kat wand…® waa awat sowat wal…®ndi.   
\s1 JISAS KWINDEYA APMA K∆óG∆óN NGU  
\p
\v 37 Wan Judana pesto ng…®ni la la nandinya Jisas laataa n…®ma kwundimba walaga wand…®. K…®ta nyan nd…®na mbanj…®nge pundeyan wuna lak yaigand…®. Nd…® kat apma l…®s…®k ngu kwigiyowun.  
\v 38 K…®ta nyan wun kat v…®laa nd…® God wand…® maa yaa nyana waa yelav…®tndeyan tamba p…®l…®wutnja vak nd…®namba t…®giyand…®.  
\li1 Waangumba wogwel…®ga ngu nat n…®mba kat kwinja vla  
\li1 wan nyan wupma nat n…®mba kat kwunatnd…® maa  
\li1 nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat t…®giyandi  
\p waa tamba p…®l…®wutndi waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 39 Jisas k…®g…®n ngu kat ana wand…®. Godna waagan kat wand…®. nd…® kat v…®laa nd…® God wand…® maa yaa nyana waa yelav…®ka l…®giyaa n…®mba God wand…® maa yaa nyana waa yelav…®ka l…®giyaa n…®mba God kwiya waagan klaigandi waa Jisas wand…®. Wan nj…®mbla Jisas mbukna nj…®mbla God nd…®na waagan ana kwiga l…®nd…®. Jisas nyinangwut wokend…® maa kwind…®.   
\s1 MBAAPMA V∆óL∆óL∆óK S∆óNDI  
\p
\v 40 Jisas mbuta nyaang…®t n…®ma sakwat n…®mba wutaa wandi. Nd…® kawiga l…®na profetna waa wandi.  
\v 41 Nat n…®mba wandi. Nd…® God kwiya nyana. Nd…® Kraistna waa wandi. Nat n…®mba wand…®. Nd…® Kraist ana nd…®. Kraist Galilimba l…®ga nyanat ana l…®giyand…®.  
\v 42 Tamba la n…®mba God waa nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutndi. Kraist Devitna yelang…® nyanat t…®giyand…®. Devitna angwa ngepma Betlehem wal…®nja ngepmamba l…®ga yaigand…® waa tamba p…®l…®wutndi waa wandi.  
\v 43-44 Ngi kat t…®ga awat sowat waleaga wal…®ndi. Ndina nat n…®mba nd…® kat kwutaa kalilaa kavle vat yivat wandi. Nd…® kat ana kwutndi.   
\s1 NJAMBWI N∆óMBA JISAS KAT WANDI  
\p
\v 45 Nd…® kat kwupmat ya plisman ndi kwo l…®ga lungwamataa yindi. Yindi maa God kat kwunata njambwi n…®mbo Ferisio ndi kat v…®laa wagalandi. Manda kat nd…® kat kwutapman kwo yangwuk waa wagalandi.  
\v 46 Wagalandi maa plisman wandi. Tat ta k…®ta nyan nd…®nai ngambula vla ana ngambul…®nd…®. Nd…®nai waa nyaang…®t wutaa ana al…®ps…®ga nd…® kat kwukiyan…®n waa wandi plisman.  
\v 47 Wandi maa Ferisi ndi kat nj…®ka wagalandi. Woseka wal…®nda nyaang…®t n…®ma sakwat n…®mba wutaa yelav…®ka ndina maawupmba kwutaa l…®ndi. Ngwutno kwutaa l…®gangwuk? Waa nj…®ka wagalandi.  
\v 48 N…®n Ferisio Judana nat njambwi n…®mbo nd…®nai ngambulaa nyaang…®t wutaa yelav…®ka n…®na maawupmba ana kwutaa l…®gan…®n. Ngwuk manda kat mand…®t vat yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk.  
\v 49 Wundi n…®mba wan tamba la nyaang…®t ana wuka l…®gandi. Ngi kat t…®ga kavle maawut yelav…®ka l…®ga Jisas waa nyaang…®t wuka l…®gandi waa Ferisi nj…®ka wandi.   
\p
\v 50 Wandi maa ndina k…®ta nyan laataa wand…®. Nd…®na s…® Nikodimas. Tak wan nyan nganat Jisas kat wagalavat yind…®.  
\v 51 Nd…® wand…®. N…®na ngepma yel…®na vak vla ana yil…®gangwuk. N…®n k…®ta nyan kat ana kwo kai wal…®gan…®n. Nd…®na kwundi wutaa s…®ga nagugiyan…®n. N…®na ngepma vat k…®ngiyan waa wand…®.   
\p
\v 52 Wand…® maa nd…® kat nj…®ka wandi. M…®no Galilina nyan m…®n. Tamba p…®l…®wutnja nyaang…®t m…®n av…® m…®la. Wan kawiga l…®na profet Galilimba ana laapkiyand…® waa v…®giyam…®n waa nd…® kat nj…®ka wandi.  
\v 53 Wandi maa yisolaa l…®nja kava kwagalalaa k…®ta nyan k…®ta nyen laaptaa m…®na ngegavat yindi.   
\c 8  
\s1 YAMB∆óS∆óK YILA TAAGWAT  
\p
\v 1 Ndina ngegavat yindi maa Jisas Oliv wal…®nja nduwiat wokend…®.  
\v 2 Nat nandinya ngambi nglei dailaa God kat kwunat…®nja ngay wuleind…® maa n…®ma sakwat n…®mba nd…® kat yandi maa nd…® ndaa l…®ga ndi kat v…®s…®mogwind…®.  
\v 3 V…®s…®mogwi l…®nd…® maa Judana lo kat s…®mogwi la n…®mbo Ferisio taagwa kwutaa nd…®na lak kalindi. Wat taagwa yamb…®s…®k yil…®nja vak kwutaa l…®la vak v…®laa l…® kat kwutaa kalindi.  
\v 4 Kalilaa Jisas kat wagalandi. Njambwi nyan wat taagwa yamb…®s…®k yil…®nja vak kwutaa l…®l…®, v…®n…®n.  
\v 5 Moses n…®n kat tamba kwiya lomba wand…®. Yam…®s…®k yil…®ga n…®mba kat tamba kwiya lomba wand…®. Yamb…®s…®k yil…®ga n…®mba kat vatnya ngwula waa wand…®. M…®n angamak wal…®gam…®n waa Jisas kat wagalandi.  
\v 6 Kavle nyaang…®t mbutndeyan nd…® kat n…®ma vat yigiyan…®n waa yelav…®taa wagalandi. Wagalandi maa Jisas ndi kat ana awat wand…®. Valolaa l…®ga s…®t taambamba k…®pmamba p…®l…®wutnd…®. N…®n kat ana wut…®gand…® waa yelav…®ka l…®ndi.   
\p
\v 7 Ngi kat t…®ga nd…® kat wagala wagala l…®ndi. Jisas laaptaa ndi kat wand…®. Ngwutna k…®ta nyan kavle vat yilapman yil…®giya nyan nd…® kambak kwutaa wat taagwa kat vatnyvat tat yaagigiyand…®  
\v 8 waa walaa valolaa nat njamb…® k…®pmamba p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\v 9 Nd…®nai waa nyaang…®t wuta n…®mba ndina maawupmba yelav…®tndi. N…®n kavle vak yiga yet…®lapman n…®mba ana n…®n waa yelav…®taa wup yilaa kwagalalaa wogwendi. Njambwi n…®mba tak wogwendi. Nat n…®mba ndina kwupmba wogwendi. Wogwendi maa Jisaso wat taagwo mb…®k kapma l…®mb…®t.   
\p
\v 10 Jisas laaptaa taagwa kapma l…®langat v…®laa l…® kat wand…®. Ny…®n kat vatnyavat yalaa la n…®mba andambpa l…®gandi. Ny…®n kat kai wal…®ga n…®mba andamapa l…®gandi waa wand…®.  
\v 11 Wand…® maa wal…®. njambwi nyan ndi tamba yindi. Wal…® maa wand…®. Ny…®n kat wuno kai ana waigowun. Ng…®ni kavle vat wata yinyeya. Kwo ay ny…®la waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 WUN GODNA NYAN WUN WAA WANDI JISAS  
\p
\v 12 Jisas nat njamb…® ndi kat wand…®. Wun k…®pma l…®ga n…®mba kat apma vat kwil…®ga nyan wun. V…®kemba ya vla l…®gowun. K…®ta nyan wuna kwupmba yandeyan kulun wala kavle vat kwagalalaa ya v…®t…®giya kavamba yet…®vla apma vat yet…®giyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 13 Wand…® mala Ferisi Jisas kat wandi. Wun njambwi nyan wun avla wal…®ma vat ana nglaatnd…®.  
\v 14 Wandi maa Jisas awat ndi kat wand…®. Wuna lak waweyan nglaatnd…®. Yawa kava v…®ga l…®gowun. Ng…®ni yiweya kava v…®ga l…®gowun. Yalaa yiweya kava ngwut ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk.  
\v 15 Ngwuk k…®pmana vapmba nat n…®mba kat v…®laa s…®ga nagul…®gangwuk.  
\v 16 Ndi kat v…®laa s…®ga naguweyan ndina maawupmba l…®ga vak kat v…®laa apma vat savagu s…®ga nagugiyowun. Wun kapma l…®ga ana s…®ga nagugiyowun. Wun kat ay waa nyan wuna nyaek wunamba l…®nd…®, s…®ga nagugiywoun.  
\v 17 Ngwutna ngepmana vak k…®ngiyan p…®o…®wutnja. V…®l…®l…®k pal…® laataa k…®ta vak k…®ta nyaang…®t mbupmbeyan wan nyaang…®t ana ndaigiyand…® waa wal…®gangwuk.  
\v 18 Wun k…®ta nyan njambwi nyanat t…®wa vat wun avla wal…®gowun. Wun kat ay waa nyan wuna nyaek nd…®no njambwi nyanat t…®wa vat d…® wal…®gand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 19 Wand…® mala ndi wandi. M…®na nyaek andamapmba l…®gand…® waa wandi maa Jisas wand…®. Wun kat ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Wun kat v…®ga l…®gengwan wuna nyaek kat v…®ga l…®gengwuk waa Jisas wand…®.   
\p
\v 20 Wan nyaang…®t God kat kwunat…®nja ngay ndi kat s…®mogwivat wuleilaa sanya nagil…®nja kavamba mbut…®nd…®. Mbut…®nd…® mala nd…® kat kavle vat yivat ana kwutaa kalindi. Nd…® kat kwutaa kalinjeya nj…®mbla wata ana ngway tolaa l…®gand…®.   
\s1 YIWEYA KAVA ANA YIGIYANGWUK WAA JISAS WAND∆ó  
\p
\v 21 Jisas ndi kat nat njamb…® wand…®. Yiwun maa wun kat kwaka v…®leviga kavle vat t…®ga kiyaigangwuk. Yiweya kava ana yaigangwuk waa wand…®.  
\v 22 Wand…® maa Juda wagalandi. Avla anagand…® vatnyagiya. Yiweya kava ana yaigangwuk waa manda kat wand…® waa wagalandi.  
\v 23 wagalandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Ngwut k…®pmana n…®mba ngwuk. Wun nyinangwutna nyan wun. An kapma kapma nda li.  
\v 24 Ngi kat t…®ga ngwuk kat wowun. Kavle vat t…®ga liyaigangwuk waa wowun. Wun kat v…®laa nd…® God wand…® yaa nyana waa yelav…®tapman yingweyan ngwut kavle savle l…®ga kiyaigangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 25 Wand…® maa wandi. M…®n anda nyan m…®n waa wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Tat ngwuk kat t…®wa vat tamba mbukwun. Mand…®t vak ana mbukiyowun.  
\v 26 Ngwuk kat mbukweya nyaang…®t n…®ma sakwat t…®nd…® maa v…®laa s…®ga nagugiyowun. Wun kat ay waa nyan savagu vapmba v…®ga s…®ga nagul…®gand…®.  
\v 27 Wanda nyaang…®t wutaa wuna ngaek waa God kat wanda vak ana wuka v…®ga l…®ndi.  
\v 28 Jisas ndi kat nat njamb…® wand…®. Wun Godna vat ndinyangu kat mbut…®ga nyan wun. Ng…®ni wun kat kwutaa katsolaa wun kat diwai krosmba kaalandi maa ndi wun kat v…®laa d…® God wand…®, yaa nyana waa waigandi. Nd…® nd…®nai yelav…®t…®ga vapmba ana nj…®vwa kwut…®gand…®. Nd…®na nyaek wand…® maa nyaek waa vapmba nj…®vwa kwuka nyaang…®t mbut…®gand…® waa waigandi.  
\v 29 Wun kat ay waa wan nyan wun kat ana kwagalaa l…®gand…®. Kapma ana t…®l…®gowun. Nd…®nai maawupmba yelav…®ka wanda vapmba m…®na nj…®vwa kwut…®gowun waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 30 Wan nyaang…®t wand…® maa n…®ma sakwat n…®mba wutaa ndi ndina maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa l…®ndi. Jisas God wand…®, yaa nyana waa yelav…®ka l…®ndi.   
\s1 JISAS WAA NYAANG∆óT NDI KAT KWUNAKIYAND∆ó  
\p
\v 31 Nd…® kat wuka kwutaa l…®ngwa vak ke kwagalangwa. Kwagalapman yingweyan wuna mbaapma n…®mba t…®giyangwuk.  
\v 32 Wun kat kwagalalapman yingweyan wunai waa nyaang…®t wuka kwutaa l…®ngweyan mbambala ngwuk kat ngila la v…®ga la kavle vat ng…®l…®giyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 33 Jisas wand…® maa Juda nd…® kat wandi. N…®n Ebrahamna nyangu n…®n. Nat n…®mba n…®n kat ana kandi kwutaa kalilaa n…®n kat v…®ga l…®ndi. Manda kat ngwuk kat kwutaa v…®ga la vak ng…®l…®giyand…® waa wam…®n waa wandi.   
\p
\v 34 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Ngwuk kat woseka ana waigowun. Awuk ngwula. Kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®ga nyan wan kavle vat nd…® kat ngilaa l…®gand…®.  
\v 35 K…®ta nyan ngayna nj…®vwa kwupmak kat nd…® kat kematndi maa t…®ndeyan nd…® wan ngaymba nj…®mbla nj…®mbla ana l…®giyand…®. Wan ngayna apma nda ng…®ni nd…® ana klaigand…®. Nd…® nj…®vwa kwuta nyan m…®na l…®gand…®. Wan ngay v…®ga la nyana nyan nd…® wan ngaymba nj…®mbla nj…®mbla t…®ga ngayna apma nda klaigand…®.  
\v 36 Wun Godna nyan wun. Ngwuk kat ngilaa l…®ga nda njalakweyan apma nglei vat t…®ga Godnana apma nglei nda klaigangwuk.   
\p
\v 37 N…®n Ebrahamna nyangu n…®n waa wal…®gangwuk. V…®ga l…®gowun. Mbut…®wa nyaang…®t wupmak kat kai waa wun kat vatnyavat t…®gangwuk.  
\v 38 Wuna nyaek t…®ga kavamba t…®ga v…®wa vat ngwuk kat mbut…®gowun. Ngwutno ngwutna nyaek yeta vla yet…®gangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 NGWUTNA NYAEK SETEN WAA WAND∆ó JISAS  
\p
\v 39 Wand…® maa Juda wandi. N…®na nyaek Ebraham waa wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Ebraham ngwutna nyaek ana nd…®. Ebraham ngwutna nyaekna t…®gendan nd…®nai yeta vla yet…®gengwuk. Wupma kai.  
\v 40 Wun Godnanamba wutuwa nyaang…®t ngwuk kat mbut…®gowun. Woseka waluwa vat ana nd…®. Wan nyaang…®t wutaa wun kat vatnyavat t…®gangwuk. Mbambala God kwiya nyan kat kai wal…®ngwa vla tamba la nyan Ebraham wupma God kwiya nyan kat ana kai wal…®nd…®.   
\p
\v 41 Ngwutna nyaek nat nyana. Ngwutna nyaek yeta vla yet…®l…®gangwuk waa Jisas wand…® maa Juda nd…® kat wandi. N…®n avla ana laataa l…®gan…®n. God wand…® mala laataa l…®gan…®n. God n…®na nyaekna. Nd…®na kwundi m…®na wuka ligan…®n waa wandi maa Jisas wand…®.  
\v 42 God ngwutna nyaeknat t…®gendan gwuk wun kat v…®laa woviyaguga l…®gengwuk. Nd…®nai l…®ga kavamba t…®wun maa wun kat wand…® maa yawun. Wunai yelav…®kna vapmba ana yawun. Nd…® wand…® maa yawun.  
\v 43 Ngwuk kat mbut…®wa nyaang…®t ngwutna maawut ana yelav…®ka l…®gand…®. Mbut…®wa nyaang…®t ana al…®ps…®ga wuka l…®gangwuk.  
\v 44 Ngwutna nyaek yelav…®ka vapmba yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk. Ngwutna nyaek Seten. Ngwutna nyaek kavle vak yil…®nda vla wupma yil…®gangwuk. Tamba nat n…®mba kat vatnyalaa nyana. Nd…® woseka wal…®ga nyana. Nd…®na maawupmba yelav…®ka kwovak kwovak woseka m…®na wal…®gand…®. Nd…® woseka wal…®ga n…®mbana njambwi nyana.  
\v 45 Wun ana ngwuk kat woseka wal…®wun maa nd…® woseka wal…®gand…® waa wal…®gangwuk wun kat.  
\v 46 Wun kavle vat ana yil…®gowun. Wan y…®wa kavle vat wun kat s…®maga ngwula. V…®lu. Ana al…®ps…®ga s…®magaiyangwuk. Ngi kat t…®ga nd…® woseka wal…®gand…® waa manda kat wal…®gangwuk wun kat.  
\v 47 Godna nyangu ndina nyaek waa vak wuka l…®gandi. Ngwuk Godna nyangu ana ngwuk. Ngi kat t…®ga God waa vak ana wuka l…®gangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 48 Wand…® maa Juda wandi. Tak nd…® kat Sameriana nyana tungwengwan yiga l…®ga nyana waa wal…®n…®n. Tak nd…®namba kavle waagan tavind…® mala kavle vat yil…®nd…® waa wal…®n…®n. Ngiyambak wal…®n…®n waa wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®.  
\v 49 Wun kavle waagan tavi l…®ga nyan ana wun. Wuna nyaekna s…® m…®na kwutaa katsol…®gowun. Ngwuk wuna s…® kwutaa viyasanda l…®gangwuk.  
\v 50 Wuna s…® avla kwutaa katsovak kat ana kan nj…®vwa kwut…®gowun. Nat nyan wuna s…® kwutaa katsovak wal…®gand…®. Wuna s…® kwutaa viyesanda l…®ga n…®mba kat nd…® kat n…®ma vat yigiyand…®.  
\v 51 Ngwuk kat woseka ana waigowun. Awuk ngwula. K…®ta nyan mbut…®wa nyaang…®t wuka yet…®ndeyan nd…® ana kiyaigand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 52 Jisas wand…® maa Juda wandi. Wama vak wutaa kavle waagan m…®namba tavilaa l…®nda vak v…®ga l…®gan…®n. Tak m…®n wam…®n. K…®ta nyan mbut…®wa nyaang…®t wuka yet…®ndeyan nd…® ana kiyaigand…® waa wam…®n. Ebrahamo tamba la profetno tamba kiyandi luwa.  
\v 53 N…®na walanga Ebraham nd…® tamba kiyand…®. M…®n nd…® kat kwulat…®gam…®n? E? Nd…® mat nyana? M…®n nd…®na njambwi m…®n? Tamba la profet ndino tamba kiyandi. M…®n ndi kat kwulat…®gam…®n? Waa nj…®ka wagalandi.   
\p
\v 54 Wagalandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Avla wuna s…® kwutaa katsoweyan n…®ma nda ana nd…®. Wuna nyaek God nd…® wuna s…® kwutaa katsol…®gand…®.  
\v 55 Ngwuk nd…®na m…®ndama ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Wun wuka v…®ga l…®gowun. Ana v…®ga l…®gowun waa waweyan woseka wal…®ngwa vak vla wupma wigowun. Woseka ana waigowun. Nd…®na m…®ndama v…®ga l…®gowun. Nd…®nai waa vapmba yet…®l…®gowun.   
\p
\v 56 Ngwula walanga Ebraham t…®wa vat v…®laa solat s…®l…®nd…® waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 57 Wand…® maa Juda wandi. M…®na nd…®mwe ndumi v…®li kiyeli tamba v…®li ana nd…®. Ebraham kat angamak yila v…®m…®n waa nj…®ka wagalandi.   
\p
\v 58 Wagalandi mala Jisas ndi kat wand…®. ngwuk kat ana woseka wowun. Tamba wunai ta nj…®mbla Ebraham wata ana l…®nd…® waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 59 Jisas wand…® maa nd…® kat vatnyavak kambak klaa kwutaa l…®ndi. Jisas pagwuga yiga God kat kwunat…®nja ngaymba l…®ga wogwend…®. Ndi n…®ma sakwat n…®mba yisolaa l…®ndi, nd…® pagwuga yiga yisolaa la n…®mba kat kwagalalaa yind…®.   
\c 9  
\s1 M∆óNI V∆óLAPMAN NYAN  
\p
\v 1 Jisas ava yamb…®mba yiga l…®ga way ava yamb…®mba la m…®ni v…®lapman nyan kat v…®nd…®. Nyime nd…® kat kwukna nj…®mbla m…®ni kwitaa l…®nd…®.  
\v 2 V…®nd…® maa Jisasna kwupmba la n…®mba nd…® kat wagalandi. Njambwi nyan, kanda ya kavle vatna nd…®na m…®ni t…®v…®laa l…®nd…® maa v…®lapman yil…®nda. Nd…®nai ya vatna? E? Nyaek ny…®me ya vatna? Waa wagalandi.   
\p
\v 3 Wagalandi maa wand…®. Kai nyaek ny…®me ya kavle vat ana nd…®na m…®ni kavle yind…®. Avla yinda kavle vat ana nd…®na m…®ni kavle yind…®. Avla yinda kavle vat ana nd…®na m…®ni kavle yind…®. God nd…® kat kwunatndeya vat nat n…®mba kat v…®s…®mogiwangat nd…®na m…®ni kavle yilaa l…®nd…®.  
\v 4 Mbambala God waa nj…®vwa kwukiyowun. Mbambala nya s…®l…®ga nandinya vla l…®gand…®. ng…®ni yaiga nandinya ngan vla l…®giyand…®. Wan ng…®ni yaiga nj…®mbla Godna nj…®vwa ana al…®ps…®ga kwuka l…®giyan…®n.  
\v 5 Mbambala wun k…®pmamba l…®wan ndinyangu kat apma vat yelav…®t…®nja vak kwil…®wa nj…®vwa kwukiyowun n…®mamba waa wand…® maa  
\v 6 k…®pmamba s…®pmiya sand…®. S…®pmiya salaa k…®pmamba l…®gangind…®. l…®gagilaa wan k…®pma klalaa kavle m…®ni la nyana m…®nimba taagalaa  
\v 7 Siloam wal…®nja nguat yilaa yagu m…®la waa wand…® Jisas. Wan ngunana s…® dina kwundimba Siloam wal…®ndi. Siloamna angwa nyaang…®t Ay M…®la. Jisas ay wand…® maa yilaa ngu yagund…® maa nd…®na m…®ni v…®nd…® apma vat.  
\v 8 Nd…®na m…®ni v…®l…®nd…® maa nd…®na ngepma n…®mba nd…® kat v…®laa wagalandi. Wan nyan tat m…®ni v…®lapman t…®ga sanya kat yawila nyana? Kai? nat nyana? Waa wagalandi.  
\v 9 Nat n…®mba wandi. Awa luwa k…®ngiya nd…®. Nat n…®mba wandi. Kai. Nat nyana. Nd…®na m…®ndama vla l…®gand…® waa wandi. Nd…® wand…®. Kai. Wunay…®. Tat m…®ni v…®lapman yeta nyan wun.   
\p
\v 10 Wand…® maa nd…® kat wagalandi. Anda vapmba yilaa mbambala wan m…®na m…®ni v…®l…®gam…®n waa wagalandi maa wand…®.  
\v 11 Jisas wal…®nja nyan k…®pma kwutaa wuna m…®nimba taagalaa Siloam wal…®nja ngu yiga yagu m…®la waa wand…® maa yiga yaguwun maa wuna m…®ni kemband…® maa v…®gowun waa wand…® maa nd…® kat wagalandi.  
\v 12 Wan nyan Jisas andambapmba l…®gand…® waa wagalandi maa ana v…®gowun wand…®.   
\p
\v 13 Nd…®na ngepma n…®mba m…®ni v…®lapman ta nyan kat kwutaa Ferisi yisolaa la kavat kalindi.  
\v 14 Jisas k…®pma kwutaa nd…®na m…®ni kwunatnda nandinya ndina nj…®vwa lapman t…®l…®nja nandinya.  
\v 15 Ferisi ta kava yand…® maa nd…® kat wagalandi. angamak yilaa m…®n m…®ni v…®m…®n waa wagandi maa wand…®. Wan nyan k…®pma kwutaa wuna m…®nimba taagand…® maa ngu yagulaa m…®ni apma vat v…®gowun waa wand…®.  
\v 16 Wand…® maa nat Ferisi wandi. Nd…® kat kwunata nyan God wand…® maa yaa nyan ana nd…®. Nj…®vwa lapman nandinya kwo t…®l…®na vla nd…® wupma ana nj…®vwa kwagalalaa kwo l…®l…®gand…® waa wandi. Ndina nat n…®mba mand…®p vak mand…®p vak wandi. Kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®ga nyan kan nj…®vwa ana al…®ps…®ga kwukiyand…®. Nd…® apma nyana waa wandi. Wungi vapmba waga mbaapma v…®l…®l…®k s…®ndi.   
\p
\v 17 Tat m…®n kiyala la nyan kat nat njamb…® wagalandi. M…®n angamak yelav…®ka l…®gam…®n. Nd…® apma nyana? E? Kavle nyana? Waa wagalangi maa nd…® profetna waa wand…®.  
\v 18 Wundi Juda nd…®nai waa nyang…®t wutaa yelav…®tndi. nd…®na m…®ni tak kavle yind…® maa yet…®nd…®? E? Woseka wal…®gand…® waa yelav…®ka nd…®na nyaek ny…®me kat yagwa wandi.  
\v 19 Wandi maa yamb…®k maa mb…®k kat wagalandi. Kan mb…®la nyana? M…®ni kavle ya nyana? Angamak yilaa kan m…®ni v…®nd…® waa wagalandi maa wamb…®k.  
\v 20 Awa luwa kan nyan ana nyana. Ny…®me nd…® kat kwutaa nj…®mbla nd…®na m…®ni kavlea.  
\v 21 Angamak yilaa mbambala v…®nda vak ana yelav…®ka l…®ga. Nd…®na m…®ni anda nyana kwunakna. Ana v…®ga l…®ga. Nd…® kat wagala ngwula. Nd…® tamba n…®ma ndua. Nd…® avla mbukiyand…® waa wamb…®k nd…®na nyaek ny…®meo.   
\p
\v 22 Nd…®na nyaek ny…®meo kapmba ana mbupmb…®k. Pagwuga mbupmb…®k. Juda kat vaaka l…®ga pagwuga mbupmb…®k. Tak Juda wal…®ndi. K…®ta nyan Jisas God wand…®, yaa nyana Kraistna waa waiga nyan kat wungi nyan kat k…®klin…®n maa yisolaa l…®l…®na ngay ana wuleigiyand…® waa tak wal…®ndi. Ngi kat t…®ga nd…®na nyaek ny…®meo vaaka l…®l…®mb…®t.  
\v 23 Ngi kat t…®ga wamb…®k. Ngwuk nd…® kat avla wagala ngwula. Nd…® ngwuk kat mbukiyand…® waa wal…®mb…®t nyaek ny…®me.   
\p
\v 24 Wamb…®t maa nat njamb…® m…®ni kavle yila la nyan kat yagwa m…®la walaa nat njamb…® wandi. M…®na m…®ni apma vat t…®nda vak kat God kat s…®vu ag…® m…®la. Wun kat kwunatnd…® waa wama nyan kavle vat yilaa nyana. Nd…® ana m…®n kat kwunatnd…® waa wand…®.   
\p
\v 25 Wandi ma wan nyan wand…®. Wun ana v…®ga l…®gowun. Kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®ga nyana? E? Apma vat m…®na yil…®ga nyana? Ana v…®ga l…®gowun. K…®ta vak m…®na v…®ga l…®gowun. Tak wuna m…®ni ana v…®l…®wun. Mbambala tamba apma vat v…®ga yet…®gowun. Ngi vat m…®na v…®ga l…®gowun wun kat yinda vat m…®na waa wand…® maa  
\v 26 ndi wandi. Wan vak anda vapmba m…®na m…®ni kwunatnd…® maa v…®ga l…®gam…®n waa wandi waa Juda.   
\p
\v 27 Wandi maa wand…®. Manda kat nj…®mbla nj…®mbla wagalal…®gangwuk. Wun kat ya vat tamba mbukwun maa wuka l…®gangwuk. Nd…®na kwupmba yivak kat nat njamb…® wupmak wunkat wagalal…®gangwuk? Waa wand…® maa  
\v 28 nd…® kat nj…®ka wandi. n…®n nd…®na kwupmba la n…®mba ana n…®n. M…®n nd…®na kwupmba la nyan m…®n. N…®n Mosesna kwupmba l…®gan…®n. Nd…® n…®na njambwi nyana.  
\v 29 Tamba God nd…®nai waa nyaang…®t Moses kat mbut…®nd…®. V…®ga l…®gan…®n. Wan nyan Jisas wupma kai. Nd…® andamba la nyana. Ana v…®ga l…®gan…®n waa nd…® kat nj…®ka wandi.   
\p
\v 30 Wandi maa ndi kat wand…®. Wan vak n…®ma vatna. Ngwuk ana v…®ngwuk Jisas andamapmba yand…®. Nd…® n…®ma njsvwa kwuka wuna m…®ni kwunatnd…®. Wan vat n…®ma vatna.  
\v 31 Kavle at yiga yet…®l…®ga n…®mba God kat wagalal…®nja vak ana wut…®gand…®. V…®l…®gan…®n. K…®ta nyan God kat yelav…®ka nd…®nai wal…®ga vapmba yet…®ndeyan wagalandeya vak God wukiyand…®.  
\v 32 Tamba njlei mbambala v…®na vat ana l…®nd…®. Ny…®me kwut…® maa kavle m…®nio la nyan kat nat nyan kwunatnda vat tak ana l…®nd…® kan k…®pmamba.  
\v 33 Jisas God wand…®, yaa nyanat t…®lapman yigenda wan n…®ma nj…®vwa kwunatnda nj…®vwa ana kwukend…® waa wand…®.   
\p
\v 34 Wand…® maa nd…® kat kimbut yiga wandi. M…®na ny…®me m…®n kat kwut…® maa m…®n kavle vat yiga yet…®ga nyan m…®n. Manda kat n…®n kat v…®s…®mogwi vat yelav…®ka l…®gam…®n waa kimbut yiga walaa nd…® kat k…®klindi.   
\s1 NDINA MAAWUT KAVLE VAK YELAV∆óKA L∆óNDI  
\p
\v 35 Nd…® kat k…®klinja vat Jisas wutaa nd…® kat kwaka yiga v…®nd…®. V…®laa wand…®. Godna vak ndinyangu kat v…®s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan kan k…®pma ngaga yand…® waa yelav…®ka l…®gam…®n? Waa wagaland…® Jisas.  
\v 36 Jisas wand…® maa wan nyan wand…®. Godna vak ndinyangu kat v…®s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan anda nyana? Wun ana v…®wun nd…® kat waa wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat v…®laa wand…®.  
\v 37 Nd…® kat tamba v…®m…®n. Wunay…® waa Jisas wand…® maa wan nyan wand…®.  
\v 38 Ngiyambak wama. God wand…® maa yaa nyan m…®n. Njambwi nyan m…®n waa walaa kwali kwali s…®laa nd…® kat s…®vu k…®l…®nd…®.   
\p
\v 39 Jisas wand…®. Ndinyangu kat mbaapmba v…®l…®l…®pmba taagavat yawunkan k…®pma. Nat mbaapma n…®mba n…®n nabuo l…®ga n…®mba n…®n waa wal…®gandi. Ndi but…®wa nyaang…®t wutaa ndina maawupmba ana yelav…®t…®gandi. Nat mbaapma n…®mba n…®n n…®ma sakwat vak kat ana yelav…®ka l…®gan…®n waa wal…®gandi. Ndi mbut…®wa nyaang…®t wutaa ndina maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®gandi waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 40 Wand…® maa wumba la ndi Ferisi nd…® kat wagalandi. M…®n n…®n kat wam…®n? Ngwuk mbut…®wa nyaang…®t ngwutna maawupmba ana yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk wam…®n n…®n kat? Waa wagalandi.  
\v 41 Wagalandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Awa luwa. Ana yelav…®ka l…®gangwut tuwa. N…®n n…®ma sakwat vak kat ana yelav…®ka l…®gan…®n wangweyan God ngwutna kavle vak kat s…®lsmbwigiyand…®. Wupma ana wal…®gangwuk. Aywaa yelav…®ka l…®gan…®n. Apma vat t…®ga n…®mba n…®n wal…®gangwuk. Ngi kat t…®ga ngwutna kavle vak kat God ana al…®ps…®ga s…®l…®mbwigiyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\c 10  
\s1 JISAS PAGWULAA L∆óGA WAPUSEPUT SIP SIP KAT MBUT∆óND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 Jisas laataa ndi kat wand…®. Ngwuk kat woseka ana waigowun. Awuk ngwula. K…®ta nyan sip sip kwaa l…®ga t…®vwina suwi yamb…®mba wuleivak kat kai walaa t…®vwi saka yiga wuleindeyan wan nyan s…®kwut…®ga nyana. Kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®ga nyana.  
\v 2 Suwi yamb…® savagu wuleil…®ga nyan nd…® wan t…®vwina sip sip kat v…®ga l…®ga nyana.  
\v 3 Ndi kat v…®ga l…®ga nyan yand…® maa suwi yamb…® kat v…®ga l…®ga nyan lavwigiyand…®. Sip sip nd…®na kwundi wuka l…®gandi. Sip sip k…®ta k…®ta ndina s…® v…®ga wuka l…®gand…®. Nd…® yagwa wand…® maa nd…®na kwundi wutaa nd…®na kwupmba yil…®gandi.  
\v 4 Nd…®na sip sip t…®vwimba l…®ga wogwenjeyan ndi avla ana wogwel…®gandi. Nd…® tak suwi yamb…® wogwel…®gand…®. Ndi nd…®na kwundi wutaa nd…®na kwupmba wogwel…®gandi.  
\v 5 Kwo nyan kat v…®laa vaka p…®l…®giyandi. Kwo nyana kwundi ana wuka l…®gandi waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 PAGWULAA L∆óGA WAPUSEPUTNA ANGWA NYAANG∆óT  
\p
\v 6 Wan pagwulaa l…®ga wapuseput Jisas mbutnd…® maa wan wapusepuk kat wutaa ana ndi yelav…®ka l…®gandi.   
\p
\v 7 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Nyaang…®t mbupmat yigowun. Awuk ngwula. Wan sip sipna t…®vwina suwi yamb…® wunay…®.  
\v 8 Wun t…®wun mala tata ya n…®mba ndi s…®kwuka kavle vat t…®giyandi. Sip sip ndina kwundi ana wuka l…®ndi.  
\v 9 Suwi yamb…® wunay…®. Ndi kat v…®ga l…®l…®wun maa ndi apma vat t…®giyandi. Sip sip apma yuwi kat vlaa k…®l…®nja vla apma vat t…®giyandi.   
\p
\v 10 S…®kwut…®ga n…®mba apma vat kwutaa yet…®vak kat ana yal…®gandi.  
\p S…®kwupmat, vatnyavat, kavle vat yivat m…®na yelav…®ka yal…®gandi. Wun ndinyangu kat nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat yet…®jeya vak kat kwivat yawun.  
\v 11 Apma vapmba sip sip kat v…®ga l…®ga nyan vla l…®gowun. Sip sip kat v…®ga l…®ga nyan vla l…®gowun. Sip sip kat v…®ga la nyan sip sip kat t…®ga kiyal…®nda vla wuno ndinyangu kat v…®ga l…®ga kiyaigowun.  
\v 12 Nat k…®ta nyan sanya klavat sip sip kat v…®ga l…®giyand…®. V…®ga l…®nda sip sip kat val…®vat yandeyan nd…® vaakaa p…®l…®nd…® maa sip si pkat vatnyand…® maa v…®laa nat sip sip kava kavat vaaka p…®l…®giyandi.  
\v 13 Sanya klavat sip sip kat v…®ga l…®ga nyan nd…® sip sip kat ana n…®mamba yelav…®ka l…®gand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga ndi kat kwagalalaa p…®l…®nd…®.   
\p
\v 14 Wun wupma ana kwagalalaa vaaka p…®l…®giyowun. Sip sip kat ama vat v…®ga l…®ga nyan vla l…®gowun. Wuna n…®mbana s…® k…®ta k…®ta v…®ga wuka l…®gowun. Dino wun kat v…®ga wuka l…®gandi.  
\v 15 Wuno wuna nyaek Godno awat sowat v…®ga l…®gali. Wuna sip sip kat t…®ga wun kiyaigowun.  
\v 16 Nat mbaapmamba l…®ga sip sip ndino wuna sip sip ndi. Ndi kat yiwun wuna kwundi wutaa wuna lak yaigandi. Yandi ma aywaa wuna sip sip k…®ta t…®vwimba taagawun maa t…®giyandi. Ndi kat aywaa wuna lak v…®ga l…®giyowun.  
\v 17 Kiyalaa l…®ga laakiyowun waa yelav…®taa kiyaigowun. Kiyaweya vak kat v…®laa wuna nyaek wun kat woviyaguga l…®gand…®.  
\v 18 K…®ta nyan nd…®na maawupmba yelav…®taa wun kat ana al…®ps…®ga vatnyagiyand…®. Wun wowun maa wun kat vatnygiyand…®. Kiyalaa l…®ga laakiyowun. V…®ga l…®gowun. Kiyalaa l…®ga avla laakweya kwondu ngil…®ga. V…®ga l…®gowun. Wuna nyaek wunkat wupma wand…® maa v…®ga l…®gowun waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 19 Nd…®nai waa nyaang…®k kat wutaa Juda ngambuga l…®ga mbaapma v…®l…®l…®k s…®ndi.  
\v 20 Nat mbaapmamba la n…®mba wandi. Kavle waagan tavind…® maa nd…® tungwengwan yiga l…®gand…®. Nd…®na kwundi wupmak kat n…®n kai wan…®n waa wandi.  
\v 21 Nat mbaapmamba la n…®mba wandi. Kavle waagan tavilaa l…®l…®ga nyan wupma wanda vla ana waigand…®. Kavle waagan tavilaa l…®l…®ga nyan m…®ni kiya nyana m…®ni ana kwunakiyand…® waa wandi.   
\s1 JUDA JISAS KAT KWUNDIMBA ND∆ó KAT WALEAL∆óNDI  
\p
\v 22 Judana n…®ma nandinya yand…®. Wan tamba Godna ngay kwunataa wuleilaa l…®nja nj…®mbla yelav…®ka l…®nja n…®ma nandinya. Yipma yila nj…®mbla yelav…®ka l…®nja n…®ma nandinya. Yipma yila nj…®mbla.  
\v 23 Wan nj…®mbla Jisas Godna gay wuleilaa tamba la nyan Solomon kwutaw kavamba l…®ga yi yal…®nd…®.  
\v 24 T…®nd…® maa Juda nd…® kat ya wegwulaa wagalandi. Manda kat n…®n kat kapmba yigumba walapman yim…®n maa n…®na maawut kavle vat yelav…®ka l…®gan…®n. Mbambala n…®n kat kapmba mbukiyam…®n. M…®n God wand…®, yaa nyan m…®n? M…®n Kraist m…®n? N…®n kat ambup m…®la waa wandi.   
\p
\v 25 Wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Ngwuk kat Kraistnat t…®wa vak tamba mbukwun maa wun kat woseka wand…® waa wangwuk. Wuna nyaek wun kat kwiya nj…®vwa kwut…®wun. Wan kwut…®wa nj…®vwa Kraistnat t…®wa vat ndinyangu kat v…®s…®mogwil…®gand…®.  
\v 26 Ngwuk Kraistnat t…®wa vat ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Ngwuk wuna sip sip ana ngwuk. Ngwuk kat tamba wowun.  
\v 27 Wuna sip sip wuna kwundi wuka l…®gandi. Ndina s…® k…®ta k…®ta wuka l…®gowun. Wuna kwundi wutaa wuna kwupmba yal…®gandi.  
\v 28 Ndi kat nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat t…®njeya vat kwil…®gowun. Ndi ana kavle yigiyandi. K…®ta nyan ana ndi kat kwutaga alaguat kloga kaligiyand…®. Wun ndi kat kwutaa l…®gowun.  
\v 29 Wuna nyaek ndi kat kwutaa l…®wangat wandi. Nd…® njambwi nyana. Nat nyan nd…® kat ana kwulakiyand…®. K…®ta nyan ana al…®ps…®ga ndi kat kwutaga alaguat kloga kaligiyand…®. God nd…®no ndi kat kwutaa l…®gand…®.  
\v 30 Wuna nyaeknonala an k…®ta lulu t…®gali. An k…®ta vat t…®gali waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 31 Jisas wand…® maa nd…® kat vatnyavat Juda kambak klalaa yaagi m…®na l…®ndi.  
\v 32 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Wuna nyaek wun kat kwiya apma n…®ma nj…®vwa n…®ma sakwat kwut…®wun. Anda apma nj…®vwa kwut…®wa nj…®vwa kat v…®laa wun kat vatnya m…®na l…®gangwuk waa wagaland…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 33 Wagaland…® maa Juda nd…® kat wandi. Kwut…®ma apma nj…®vwa kat v…®laa m…®n kat ana vatnya m…®na l…®gan…®n. God kat kavle vat wam…®n. Ngwuk ndu ngwuk. Wun God wun waa manda kat apma wam…®n. Wamangat m…®n kat vatnya m…®na l…®gan…®n waa wandi.   
\p
\v 34 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. ngwutna tamba la nyan God waa nyaang…®t wutaa p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\p Ngwuk Godno k…®tamba k…®ta lulu l…®gangwuk waa tamba p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\v 35 Wan tamb la nyan p…®l…®wukna nyan ndinyangu kat ndi God ndi waa p…®l…®wutnd…®. Wan p…®l…®wukna nyan Godna nyaang…®t wutaa God kwiya nj…®vwa kwuta nyan nd…®. Wan p…®l…®wuknda nyaang…®t woseka waa ana p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\v 36 Wungi kat t…®ga wun Godna nyan wun waa wawa vat wutaa ngwut manda kat nd…® kavle vat wand…® waa wal…®gangwuk. God wun kat ay wand…® nd…®na vat ndinyangu kat s…®magavat kan k…®pmat ngaga yawun.   
\p
\v 37 Wuna nyaek God wun kat kwinda nj…®vwa kwutapman yiweyan wuna kwundi ana wukiyangwuk.  
\v 38 God kwinda nj…®vwa kwut…®gowun. Wal…®wa kwundi wupmak kat kai wangweyan kwut…®wa nj…®vwa v…®laa nd…® God kwiya nyana waa wun kat yelav…®kiyangwuk. Nd…® Godna kwondumba nj…®vwa kwut…®gand…® maa wun kat yelav…®kiyangwuk. Nd…®nogwi Godno k…®ta lulu l…®gamb…®t waa yelav…®k…®iyangwuk. Waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 39 Wand…® maa nd…® kat vatnyavat kwupmat wandi. Ndi kat kwagalalaa pagwuga yind…®.   
\p
\v 40 Ndi kat kwagalalaa Jodan wal…®nja ndandang…® nat naang…® val…®gend…®. Wan yinda kava tat Jon ndinyangu kat ngu yagula kava. Wumba yilaa yet…®nd…®.  
\v 41 Wumba l…®nd…®, nd…® kat n…®ma sakwat n…®mba yal…®ndi. Yalaa nd…® kat wal…®ndi. Jisas kwunat…®nda n…®ma nj…®vwa Jon wupma ana kwut…®nd…®. Jon nd…® kat wanda nyang…®t woseka ana wal…®nd…® waa wal…®ndi.  
\v 42 Wan kava la n…®ma sakwat n…®mba Jisas kat v…®laa God wand…® maa yaa nyana waa wal…®ndi.   
\c 11  
\s1 LASARAS KIYAND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 K…®ta nyan nd…®na s…® Lasaras nd…® yelogwen kat t…®nd…®. D…®na ngepma Betani. Nd…®na mb…®t yakwa lagwa v…®l…®l…®k Mario Mato ndi k…®ta ngepma n…®mba ndi.  
\v 2 Nd…®na yakwa lagwa Maria apma njangu veila ngu klalaa Jisasna mamba taagalaa salataa l…®la s…®vla n…®mb…® yuwimba nyangata taagwat.  
\v 3 Lasaras yelogwen kat t…®nd…® maa nd…®na yakwa lagwa nyaang…®t wamb…®t, wan nyaang…®t kwutaa Jisas kat yiga mbutndi. Njambwi nyan woviyaguga l…®ma nyan yelogwen kat t…®gand…® waa wamba nyaang…®t yiga mbutndi.  
\v 4 Mbutja nyaang…®t wutaa Jisas wand…®. Kiyangeya yelogwen ana nd…®. Godna s…® kwutaa katsogiyaa yelogwena l…®ga. Godna nyana s…® kwutaa katsogiyaa yelogwena l…®ga waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 5 Mato, l…®la yakwa lagwo, Lasaras kat Jisas woviyaguga l…®nd…®.  
\v 6 Lasaras yelogwen kat t…®gand…® waa wandi wutaa Jisas ana yind…®. T…®nda kavamba nandinya v…®l…®l…®k t…®ga kwo yet…®nd…®.  
\v 7 Nandinya v…®l…®l…®k t…®ga nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat wand…®. Laap ngwula. Judia nat njamb…® yigat waa wand…®.   
\p
\v 8 Wand…® maa nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba nd…® kat wandi. Njambwi nyan Judiamba l…®ga njambwi Juda tak m…®n kat vatnyavat kambak kwutaa l…®ndi m…®n kat yaagivat. At nat njamb…® ndina ngepma yigiyam…®n? Waa wandi.   
\p
\v 9 Wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Nya s…®l…®ga nandinya k…®ta tamba v…®li kiyeli v…®l…®l…®k aua t…®gand…®. nya s…®l…®ga nj…®mbla ndu nyan man veiga yindeyan kambapmba man s…®laa ana ndaigand…®. Nya s…®nd…®, m…®ni v…®ga yigumba veiga yigiyand…®.  
\v 10 K…®ta nyan ngan man veiga yindeyan wan nyan kambapmba s…®laa ndaigand…®. M…®ni v…®lapman ndaigand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga Judia yigiyan…®n nj…®vwa kwupmat.   
\p
\v 11 Wan nyaang…®t walaa at nat njamb…® wand…®. N…®na al…® nyan Lasaras s…®ndu kwand…®. Yilaa nd…® kat s…®v…®l…®wun, laakiyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 12 Wand…® maa nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba wandi. Njambwi nyan yelogwen kat t…®ga n…®mba s…®ndu kwanjeyan apma vatna. Manda kat s…®v…®l…®giyam…®n waa wandi.  
\v 13 Lasaras kiyanda vat kat pagwuvat nd…® s…®ndu kwaand…® waa wand…® Jisas. Nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba wutaa nd…® s…®ndu kwaand…® waa yelav…®ka l…®ndi.   
\p
\v 14 Ngi kat t…®ga Jisas ndi kat kapmba wand…®. Lasaras kiyand…® waa wand…®.  
\v 15 Kiyanda nj…®mbla wun ana wumba l…®wun. Apma vatna. Wumba l…®gewan ng…®ni kwukweya n…®ma nj…®vwa v…®laa nd…® njambwi nyana waa ana waingwuk. Mbambala yigiyan…®n wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 16 Jisas wand…® maa Tomas waa Didimas wal…®nja v…®l…®gu nyan wand…®. Wovun yigiyan…®n. Nd…®nogwinana kiyaigan…®n waa njambwi Juda kat vaaka wand…® Tomas.   
\s1 KIYA N∆óMBA KAT LAAK NGWULA WAA WAIGA NYAN JISAS  
\p
\v 17 Jisas yanda nj…®mbla Lasaras nandinya aynat tamba waangumba l…®nd…®.  
\v 18 Lasaras ta ngepma Betani Jerusalemna ngwaymba l…®nd…®. Nd…®na s…®vla mail v…®l…®l…®k.  
\v 19 N…®ma sakwat Jerusalemba l…®ga Juda ndu lagwa yalaa Mato Maria kat tangat…®ndi. Mb…®la yakwa nyan kat lasaras kat n…®ma n…®ma vat yelav…®ka t…®mb…®t maa tangat…®ndi.  
\v 20 Jisas tamba yaand…® waa wandi maa wutaa Mato Jisas kat yiga ava yamb…®mba v…®l…®. Maria ana yil…®. Ngaymba ndaal…®l…®.   
\p
\v 21 Mata Jisas kat yalaa wal…®. Njambwi nyan kumba t…®geman wuna yakwa ndu ana kiyaind…®.  
\v 22 Mbambala God kat wagalameyan wagalameya vat wutaa God apma vat yigiyand…®. V…®ga l…®gowun waa wal…® Mata.   
\p
\v 23 Wal…® maa Jisas l…® kat wand…®. Ny…®na yakwa ndu kiyalaa laakyand…® waa wand…® maa Mata wal…®.  
\v 24 Ngiyambak wam…®n. Ng…®ni yaiga nandinya kiya n…®mba aywaa laatjeya nandinya nd…®no laaptaa t…®giyand…®. V…®ga l…®gowun waa wal…® Mata.  
\v 25 Wal…® maa Jisas wand…®. Kiya n…®mba kat laak ngwula waa waiga nyan wunay…®. Apma vat yiga yet…®njeya vak kwil…®ga nyan wunay…®. K…®ta nyan njambwi nyanat t…®wa vat yelav…®tndeyan kiyalaa l…®ga lalapkiyand…®. K…®ta nyan njambwi nyanat tuwa vat yelav…®tndeyan apma vat yiga yet…®njeya vak nd…® kat kwigiyowun.  
\v 26 Kwo l…®ga n…®mba njambwi nyanat t…®wa vat wun kat yelav…®tnjeyan ndi ana kavle yigiyandi. Kan wal…®wa nyaang…®t yelav…®ka l…®gany…®n? Waa wagaland…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 27 Wagaland…® maa Mata nd…® kat wal…®. Njambwi nyan. M…®n Kraist m…®n. M…®n kat v…®ga l…®gowun. M…®n Godna nyan m…®n. M…®n God kwiya nyan m…®n. Kawiga l…®na nyan m…®n. Tamba v…®ga l…®gowun waa wal…®.   
\s1 JISAS NGLAND∆ó  
\p
\v 28 Mata walaa lungwamataa yiga l…®la yakwa lagwa Maria kat pagwuga mbut…®. Njambwi nyan wungi ya. Ny…®n kat wal…®gand…®. Maria yaal…® waa wand…® waa Mata mbut…®.  
\v 29 Maria wutaa kwiyatapman laaptaa Jisas kat yil…®.  
\v 30 Jisas ngepma ana wuleind…®. Tat Mata nd…® kat va kava ava yamb…®mba l…®nd…®.  
\v 31 Maria Jisas kat v…®vat kwiyatapman laataa ngay kwagalalaa yil…® maa v…®laa ngaymba l…®ga l…® kat tangata n…®mba l…®la kwupmba yiga wandi. Nd…® kat taaganja waangu kavat nglavat yil…®gal…®. L…® kat kwupmba yiga tangakaiyan…®n waa waga yindi.   
\p
\v 32 Jisas ta kavat Maria yalaa nd…® kat v…®laa nd…®na mangand…®mba kwali mamba s…®laa nd…® kat wal…®. Njambwi nyan kumba t…®geman wuna yakwa ndu ana kiyaind…® waa nglaga wal…® Maria.   
\p
\v 33 Nglal…®la vakat l…®logwinala la ndi Juda nglal…®nja vak kat v…®laa Jisas ndi kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka l…®ga ndi kat wagaland…®.  
\v 34 Nd…® kat taaganja waangu andamapmba l…®gand…® waa wand…® maa yaa av…® waa wandi.   
\p
\v 35 yil…®ndi maa Jisas nglal…®nd…®.  
\v 36 Nglal…®nda vak kat v…®laa Juda wandi. Kiya nyan kat Jisas n…®mamba woviyaguga l…®nd…® waa wandi.  
\v 37 Ndina n…®mba wandi. Wan nyan tak m…®ni kiya nyana m…®ni kwunatnd…®, v…®nd…®. Wan nyan kat kwaglalnd…® maa kiyand…®. Manda kat wupma yind…® waa wandi.   
\s1 JISAS WAND∆ó MAA LASARAS LAATND∆ó  
\p
\v 38 Ndina nyaang…®t wutaa Jisas n…®ma vat yelav…®ka l…®ga waangu la kavat yand…®. Wan waangu kambak m…®na la waangua. Wan waanguna tak waangu n…®ma kambapmba kuviyalagulaa t…®v…®ndi.  
\v 39 Wan kavat yalaa Jisas wand…®. T…®v…®nja kambak kumba ngwula waa wand…® maa kiya nyana yakwa lagwa Mata Jisas kat wal…®. njambwi nyan nandinya aynat waangumba l…®nd…®. Nd…®na s…®m kavle njangu veil…®gand…®. Kambak kumba ngwula waa ke waa waa wal…® Mata.  
\v 40 Jisas l…® kat wand…®. Tak ny…®n kat tamba wowun. Kai walapman y…®nyeyan God kwutndeya apma nj…®vwa v…®giyany…®n waa tak ny…®n kat wowun waa Jisas wand…® maa  
\v 41 kambak kwutaa kumbandi. Kumbandi maa kiya nyan ta waangu kwo l…®nd…®. Jisas nyinangwutnat tanamb…®taa wand…®. Nyaek, wagalawa vat tamba wupm…®n. M…®n kat s…®vu k…®l…®gowun.   
\p
\v 42 nj…®mbla nj…®mbla wagal…®wa vak wuka l…®gam…®n. Wunogwina l…®ga n…®mba wutnjangat m…®n kat kwundimba wowun. Wagalal…®wa vak wuka l…®gam…®n waa kwundimba wowun. Wutaa God wand…® maa yaa nyana waa wun kat yelav…®ka l…®giyandi waa God kat wand…®.   
\p
\v 43 God kat walaa n…®ma kwundimba Lasaras laataa ngaga yaa m…®la waa walend…® maa  
\v 44 kiyaa nyan laaptaa yand…®. kiyand…® maa waangumba taagavat t…®nja nj…®mbla s…®vla waavwimba nd…®na mbang…® mbaataa taagandi. Nd…®na man taamba wan waavwi ngilaa l…®nd…® maa wogwend…®. Nd…®na m…®ndama waavwimba kapmandi maa wogwend…®. Wogwend…® maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Nd…®na waavwi njalak ngwula. Kwo l…®giyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 JUDANA NJAMBWI N∆óMBA JISAS KAT VATNYAVAK YELAV∆óTNDI  
\p
\v 45 Maria kat tangapmat ta Juda Jisas yalaa kwuta nj…®vwa v…®laa nd…® God wand…®, yaa nyana waa yelav…®ka l…®ndi.  
\v 46 Ndina nat n…®mba wupma ana yelav…®tndi. Jisas kwutaa vak kat v…®laa yiga Ferisi kat mbutndi.   
\p
\v 47 Mbutndi maa Ferisio God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mbo wandi maa ndino nat n…®ma sakwat njambwi n…®mbo ngambuvat yisolaa l…®ndi. yisolaa l…®ga wandi. N…®n angamak yigiyan…®n nd…® kat. N…®ma sakwat apma n…®ma nj…®vwa kwut…®gand…®.  
\v 48 Nd…® kat kai walapman yineyan n…®na ngepmana n…®mba aywaa nd…®na kwupmba yigiyandi. Yindi maa n…®n kat v…®ga Romba l…®ga n…®mba yalaa n…®n kat s…®giyandi. Wan vak kat kai waigandi waa wandi.   
\p
\v 49 Ndina k…®ta nyan Kaiafas kat naambi God kat kwunat…®ga n…®mbana njambwi nyanat t…®nd…®. Nd…® laataa ndi kat wand…®. Ngwuk apma maawut ana yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk.  
\v 50 Wan nyan Jisas kat vatnyaneyan n…®n aywaa ana kavle yigiyan…®n. Romba l…®ga n…®mba n…®n Juda kat ana yaa s…®giyandi. N…®n kat t…®ga nd…® Jisas kiyandeyan wovuna waa wand…®.   
\p
\v 51 Wanda nyaang…®t nd…®na maawupmba yelav…®taa ana wand…®. Kat naambi ndina njambwi nyanat t…®ndangat God nd…®na maawupmba ngambund…® maa wand…®. Jisas ndinyangu kat t…®ga kiyaigand…® waa wand…® Kaifas. Wanda nyaang…®tna angwa kat ana yelav…®ka l…®nd…®. Nd…® kwo wand…®.  
\v 52 Wanda nyaang…®tna angwa k…®ngiyan. Jisas Juda kat m…®na kwunapmat ana kiyand…®. Kava kavamba l…®ga n…®mba kat aywaa kwunapmak kiyand…®. Ndi kat aywaa kwutaa kaliga Godna mbaapmamba tangavak kat kiyand…®. Taagand…® maa Godna nyaanguat t…®giyandi.   
\p
\v 53 Wungi nandinyamba yisolaa l…®ga nyaang…®t ngambulaa Jisas kat s…®vak kat.  
\v 54 Wungi kat t…®ga Juda la ngepma ngepma Jisas ana yi ya yet…®l…®nd…®. Kwo kavamba l…®ga ngepmat yind…®. Efraim wal…®nja ngepmat yind…®. Wan ngepma yilaa nd…®nogwi nd…®na mbaapma n…®mbo k…®ta vat yet…®ndi.   
\s1 JISAS KAT KWAT∆óNDI  
\p
\v 55 Judana pesto pasova wal…®nja pesto tamba ngway toland…®. Kava kavamba la Juda laataa Jerusalemat yindi. Tat n…®na nglambi njangigiyan…®n ng…®ni pesto kat wuleigiyan…®n waa yelav…®taa Jerusalemat yindi.  
\v 56 Jerusalemat yilaa Jisas kat kwat…®ndi. God kat kwunat…®nja ngayat wuleilaa awat sowat ngambul…®ndi. Pesto kat anagand…® yaiga waa awat sowat ngambul…®ndi.  
\v 57 God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mbogwi Ferisio nyaang…®t tamba kwindi. K…®ta nyan Jisas kat v…®ga l…®meyan n…®n kat mbuiyam…®n waa wandi. Nd…® kat kwupmat wan…®n waa wandi.   
\c 12  
\s1 MARIA APMA NJANGU VEIL∆óGA NGU JISASNA MAMBA KAL∆óT∆ó  
\p
\v 1 Nandinya s…®la k…®ta l…®ga pasova wal…®nja pesto t…®giyand…®. Jisas Betaniat yind…®. Wan ngepma Lasaras ta ngepma. Tat wan nyan Lasaras kiyand…® maa Jisas laap m…®la wand…® mala laatnd…®.  
\v 2 Ndina ngay wuleind…® maa nd…® kat k…®g…®nda kwutndi. Lasarasna nyange Mata k…®g…®nda wan n…®mba kat kansaga kwil…®l…®. Lasaras nd…® njab…®mba nat n…®bagwinala ndal…®nd…®.  
\v 3 T…®ga l…®ga Maria apma njangu veila ngu klalaa Jisasna taga mamba salat…®. Wan ngu n…®ma sanyamba wan gu kat nyangat…®. Wan nguna njangu wan ngaymba la n…®mba aywaa wutndi. Apma njangu veil…®nd…®.  
\v 4 Kal…®t…® maa Jisasna mbaapmamba la k…®ta nyan Judas Iskeriot, ng…®ni t…®ga Jisas kat kamwin kwigiyaa nyan l…® kat wand…®.  
\v 5 Wan njangu veila ngu manda kat kwo kal…®t…®. Wan ngu kwilaa sanya klalaa sanya lapman n…®mba kat kwigelan wovuna. 300 dola anagal…® klaiga waa wand…® Judas.  
\v 6 Sanya lapman ta n…®mba kat ana n…®ma vat yelav…®taa wand…®. Jisasna mbaapmamba la n…®mba k…®ta yisoga taagal…®nja mani nd…®nai v…®ga la. V…®ga l…®ga nat nj…®mbla s…®kwut…®nd…®. Wan ngu k…®ilaa klaleya sanya nd…® v…®ga l…®ga s…®kwupmat yelav…®taa wand…®.   
\p
\v 7 Wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. L…® kat wupma ke waa. Kiyawun maa wun kat waangumba taaganjeya nj…®mbla kat yelav…®taa wan njangu veila ngu kal…®t…® wun kat.  
\v 8 Sanya lapman t…®ga n…®mba ngwulogwinala nj…®mbla nj…®mbla t…®l…®ndi maa ndi kat kwigiyangwuk. Wun ng…®ni ngwulogwina nj…®mbla nj…®mbla ana l…®g…®yowun waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 LASARAS KAT VATNYVAT WAND∆ó  
\p
\v 9 Jisas betanimba t…®nda vak kat wutaa Juda n…®ma sakwat laataa yandi nd…® kat v…®vat. Jisas kat m…®na v…®vak kat ana yandi. Nd…®no Lasaras kat v…®vak kat yandi. Tat Jisas wand…® maa Lasaras kiyalaa l…®ga laatnd…®. Ng…® kat t…®ga nd…® kat v…®vak kat yandi.  
\v 10 God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mba Lasaras kat vatnyavak kat yelav…®ka l…®ndi.  
\v 11 Lasaras kat Juda n…®ma sakwat v…®laa n…®n kat kwagalalaa Jisasna mbaapmamba n…®ma sakwat n…®mba yil…®gandi waa yelav…®taa Lasaras kat vatnyavat wandi.   
\s1 JISAS KING T∆óGA VLA JERUSALEM WULEIND∆ó  
\p
\v 12 Nat nandinya pesto kat yilaga n…®ma sakwat n…®mba mbambala Jisas Jerusalemat yaigand…® waa wandi maa wutaa njambwi nyanat t…®nda vak kat yelav…®taa  
\v 13 t…®pma ngla kal…®ka kwutaa nd…® kat v…®vat yandi. Nd…® kat v…®laa wandi. Wovun yam…®n. M…®n n…®n Isrel wal…®na n…®mbana king m…®n. God wand…® maa yam…®n. M…®n apma njambwi nyan m…®n waa n…®ma kwundimba walega wal…®ndi.   
\p
\v 14 Jisas kwand…® donki k…®ta kwutaa l…®la mbunimba ndaal…®ga yand…®. Nd…® tamba la nyan p…®l…®wuta vak vla ndaal…®ga yand…®.  
\v 15 Tamba p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\li1 saionmba l…®ga n…®mba ngwuk ke n…®mamba yelav…®ka  
\li1 l…®ngwa. Ngwutna njambwi nyan yaigand…®. Donkina  
\li1 mbunimba ndaal…®ga yaigand…®  
\p waa tamba p…®l…®wutnd…®.   
\p
\v 16 Wan tamba p…®l…®wutnda nyaang…®t Jisasna mbaapma n…®mba di ana yelav…®ka l…®ndi. Tamba la nyan p…®l…®wutnda vak vla nd…® kat yindi waa ng…®ni yelav…®ka l…®ndi.   
\p
\v 17 Tak Lasaras kiyand…® maa waangumba taagandi, l…®nd…®. L…®nd…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…® maa laatnd…®. Laatnda vak va n…®mba ngepma ngepma yi ya mbut…®nd…®i.  
\v 18 Lasaras kat wand…®, laatnda vak kat wutaa n…®ma sakwat n…®mba Jisas kat v…®vat yandi.  
\v 19 N…®ma sakwat n…®mba Jisas kat ya vak v…®laa Ferisi awat sowat wandi. Nd…® kat kwulapmat t…®na vat tamba kwo vatnat t…®gand…®. ndinyangu aywaa nd…®na kwupmba yil…®ndi.   
\s1 GRIK WAL∆óNJA N∆óMBA JISAS V∆óVAT WANDI  
\p
\v 20 Wan pesto kat ya n…®mbana nat n…®mba Juda ana ndi Di Grik ndi. God kat yelav…®pmak Jerusalemat yindi.  
\v 21 Wundi Grik Filip kat yandi. Filipna ngepma Betsaida. Galilimba la ngepma. Nd…® kat yalaa wandi. M…®n, Jisas kat v…®laa ngambuvat yalaa l…®gan…®n waa wandi.  
\v 22 Wandi maa wutaa Filip yiga Endru kat mbutnd…®. Mbutnd…® maa mb…®k Jisas kat yiga mbupmb…®k.  
\v 23 Mbupmb…®k maa Jisas wand…®. Wan nyinangwutna vak ndinyangu kat s…®mogwil…®ga nyan wun. Wun kat kwutaa vatnyanjeya nj…®mbla tamba ngway tolagand…®. Wun kat vatnyandi maa God wuna s…® kwutaa katsogiyand…®.  
\v 24 Mbut…®wa nyaang…®t awuk ngwula. K…®l…®nja mina s…®k k…®pmamba dalaa n…®ng…®ndeyan n…®ma sakwat mi s…®k wataa t…®giyand…®. K…®pmamba ndalapman yindeyan nd…® s…®k k…®ta t…®giyand…®.  
\v 25 N…®no ndinyangu wungi vat s…®g…®t. K…®ta nyan nd…®na mbag…®na nj…®vwa m…®na kwuka nd…®na mbang…® m…®na kwunaka yet…®l…®ndeyan wan nyan nd…® kavle yigiyand…®. K…®ta nyan nd…®na mbang…® kwunapmak kat nd…®na mbag…®na nj…®vwa kwupmak kat kai wandeyan nd…® nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat t…®ndeya vat kaligand…®.  
\v 26 K…®ta nyan wunogwinala nj…®vwa kwupmat wandeyan wunai yet…®ga vak vla yet…®giyand…®. K…®ta nyan wunogwinala nj…®vwa kwutndeyan wuna nyaek nd…®na s…® kwutaa katsogiyand…®.   
\s1 WUN KAT KWUTAA KATSOGIYANDI WAA WAND∆ó JISAS  
\p
\v 27 Wun mbambala maawut n…®ma vat yelav…®ka l…®gowun. Wuna nyaek wagalagiyowun. Manda vatna wagalaweyan. Wun kat yavat t…®ga kavle vak kat kai awa waa walu? Kai. Wupma ana wagalgiyowun. Wun kat yavat t…®ga kavle vat klavat kan k…®pmat ngaga yawun.  
\v 28 Kupma waigowun wuna nyaekat. Avla m…®na s…® kwutaa katso m…®la waa waigowun waa wand…® Jisas. Jisas wand…® maa nyinangwupmba l…®ga ngaga yaa kwundi wutaa wandi. Tak avla wuna s…® kwutaa katsowun. Ng…®ni nat njamb…® kwutaa katsogiyowun waa wand…®.  
\v 29 Wumba la n…®mba nyinangwupmba l…®g…® ngaga yaa kwundi wutaa wandi. Vlap mlak wand…® waa wandi. Nat n…®mba wutaa wandi. Ensel Jisas kat wand…® waa wandi.   
\p
\v 30 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Wan nyinangwupmba l…®ga yand…®, wukngwa kwundi wukwangat ana wand…®. Wukngwangat wand…®. Ngwutna maawut kwunapmak wand…®.  
\v 31 Kan k…®pmana kavle vat aywaa v…®giyandi. V…®njeya nj…®mbla tamba ngway tolagand…®. Kan k…®pmana n…®mba kat kavle maawut kwil…®ga nyan kat kwulakiyaa vat tamba ngway tolagand…®.  
\v 32 Wun kat kwutaa katsondi maa k…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mba kat yagwa waigowun. Wuna mbaapma yaa wulei ngwula waa waigowun waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 33 Nd…® kat ng…®ni vatnyanjeya vak kat yelav…®taa wand…®. Wun kat kwutaa katsogiyandi waa wand…®.   
\p
\v 34 Jisas wand…® maa wumba la n…®mba nd…® kat wandi. Tamba la n…®mba God waa nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutnja vak v…®n…®n. God kwiya nyan Kraist nj…®mbla nj…®mbla t…®giyaa nyana waa p…®l…®wutnja vak v…®n…®n. M…®n wam…®n. Wun Godna vak k…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mba kat v…®s…®mogwil…®ga nyan wun. Wun kat ng…®ni vatnyagiyandi waa wam…®n. M…®n kanda m…®n. M…®n wan nyan m…®n? Waa wagalandi.  
\v 35 Wagalandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Mbambala ngwutnogwinala l…®wan kemba l…®ga ya vla l…®gowun. Mbambala wun kat v…®l…®…® Godna apma vat v…®s…®mogwi l…®ga nyana waa yelav…®k ngwula. Samat t…®ga ngwuk kat kwagalalaa yigiyowun. Yiwun maa ngwuk ngan vla l…®giyangwuk. Wuna apma vat ana v…®ga l…®giyangwuk. Wun kat v…®lapma Godna apma vat v…®s…®mogwi l…®ga nyana waa ana yelav…®kiyangwuk.  
\v 36 Mbambala ngwutnogwinana t…®wa vak v…®laa yelav…®k ngwula. Wun kat v…®laa Godna apma vat v…®s…®mogwi l…®ga nyana waa yelav…®kngweyan ngwuk apma vat t…®giyangwuk waa wand…® Jisas. Jisas walaa ndi kat kwagalalaa yind…®. Yiga wun kat v…®landi waa nd…®na mbang…® yiga pagwulaa l…®ndi.   
\s1 JUDA N∆óMA SAKWAT JISAS KAT KAI WANDI  
\p
\v 37 N…®ma sakwat n…®ma nj…®vwa kwut…®nda vak ndi v…®l…®ndi. V…®laa God wand…® maa yaa nyana waa ana yelav…®tndi.  
\v 38 Yelav…®tapman yil…®nja vak kat tamba la nyan Aisaia tamba p…®l…®wutnd…®. P…®l…®wutnda nyaang…®pmba ng…®ni wan vak yil…®ndi.  
\li1 Njambwi nyan, but…®na nyaang…®t ana wuka v…®ga  
\li1 l…®ndi. Godna kwondu v…®laa nd…® n…®ma nyana waa  
\li1 ana yelav…®ka l…®ndi  
\p waa tamba p…®l…®wutnd…® Aisaia.  
\v 39 Wan Jisasogwinala ta Juda angamak Jisas njambwi nyanat t…®nda vak v…®lapman yindi. Ndi tamba la nyan Aisaia p…®l…®wutnda nyaang…®pmba yil…®ndi.  
\v 40 Nd…® tamba p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\li1 God wand…® maa ndina m…®ni ana v…®l…®ndi. Ndina  
\li1 maawut ana yelav…®t…®ndi. Ngi kat t…®ga God ndi kat  
\li1 yil…®nda vat ndina m…®ni ana v…®ga l…®ndi. Ndina  
\li1 maawut ana yelav…®ka l…®ndi. Ngi kat t…®ga God ndi  
\li1 kat ana kwunakiyand…®  
\p waa p…®l…®wutnd…® Aisaia.  
\v 41 Tamba Aisaia p…®l…®wukna nyaang…®t Jisas njambwi nyanat t…®nda vak v…®laa p…®l…®wutnd…®.   
\p
\v 42 Ferisi Juda kat wal…®ndi. K…®ta nyan Jisas njambwi nyana waa wandeyan nd…® kat kai waigan…®n. God kat yelav…®pmak yisolaa l…®neya ngay ana wuleigiyand…® wan nyan waa wal…®ndi Ferisi. Judana nat njambwi n…®mba Jisas kat v…®laa nd…® njambwi nyana waa yelav…®t…®ndi. Kwundimba ana wal…®ndi. Ferisi kat vaaka l…®ndi.  
\v 43 Yelav…®ta vak kat pagwua n…®mba nat n…®mba dina s…® kwutaa katsonjangat n…®mamba yelav…®ka l…®ndi. God ndina s…® kwutaa katsondangat ana n…®mamba yelav…®ka l…®ndi.   
\s1 MBUTUWA NYAANG∆óT N∆óMBI NDA VLA L∆óGAND∆ó  
\p
\v 44 Jisas laataa n…®ma kwundimba walega wand…®. K…®ta nyan wun kat v…®laa njambwi nyanat t…®wa vak kat yelav…®tndeyan wun kat ay waa nyan God nd…®no nd…® kat njambwi nyanat t…®nda vak kat yelav…®kiyand…®.  
\v 45 K…®ta nyan wun kat v…®ndan wun kat ay waa nyan God kat nd…® v…®l…®gand…®.  
\v 46 Kemba l…®ga ya vla v…®ga kan k…®pma ngaga yawun. Njambwi nyanat t…®wa vak kat k…®ta nyan yelav…®tndeyan kulun walaa la kavle vat kwagalalaa apma vat kemba l…®ga vak vla yet…®giyand…®.  
\v 47 K…®ta nyan mbukwa nyaang…®t wutaa njambwi nyanat t…®wa vak kat yelav…®tapman yindeyan nd…® kat ana s…®giyowun. Kan k…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mba kat s…®vat ana yawun.  
\v 48 Mbukwa nyaang…®t wupmak kat kai waga wun kat kai wal…®ga nyan nd…® kavle vat klaigand…®. Ng…®ni yaiga nandinya mbambala mbut…®wa nyaang…®t wan nyan kat n…®mbi nda vla s…®nd…® maa kavle yigiyand…®.  
\v 49 Mbut…®wa nyaang…®t wuna yelav…®ka vapmba ana mbut…®wun. Nyaek wunkat wand…® maa yaa mbut…®wun.  
\v 50 Wuna nyaek mbuta nyaang…®t wutaa nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vak m…®na yet…®giyandi. V…®l…®gowun. Ngi kat t…®ga kwo ana mbut…®gowun. Wuna nyaek wun kat waa nyaang…®t m…®na mbut…®gowun waa wand…® Jisas.   
\c 13  
\s1 JISAS ND∆óNA MBAAPMA N∆óMBANA MAN NJANGIND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 Pasova wal…®nja pesto tamba ngway tolond…®. Jisas tamba yelav…®tnd…®. Kan k…®pma kwagalalaa wuna nyaek t…®ga kavat yiweya nj…®mbla tamba ngway tolond…® waa yelav…®ka l…®nd…®. Jisas kan k…®pmamba l…®ga nd…®na mbaapmamba la n…®mba kat nj…®mbla nj…®mbla n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka l…®l…®nd…®.   
\p
\v 2 Ndi kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka l…®ga ndinogwina nao k…®nd…®. Wan nglaambu nao k…®ga k…®yagindi maa Seten yaa Judas iskeriot Saimona nyan nd…®na maawupmba ngwand…®nd…® maa Judas kamwin kwindeya vak kat yelav…®ka l…®nd…®.  
\v 3 Jisas v…®ga l…®nd…®. Nd…®na nyaek God nd…® kat kwanda kwanda aywaa v…®ga l…®ndangat kwind…®. God wand…® maa valaa l…®gowun waa v…®ga l…®nd…® Jisas. Ng…®ni God t…®ga kavat lungwamataa yigiyowun waa v…®ga l…®nd…® Jisas.  
\v 4 Jisasna mbaapma nimba awat sowat kwulaka njambwi n…®mbat t…®vak val…®nja nyaang…®t wutaa Jisas k…®g…®nda k…®l…®nja njamb…®mba ndaa l…®ga laataa nd…®na kumbula l…®nda waavwi s…®venga taagalaa taul klalaa nd…®na yipma s…®tnd…®.  
\v 5 Sitaa n…®ma awmba ngu kendolaa nd…®na mbaapmamba la n…®mbaba man ngu klalaa njangilaa yipma s…®tnda taulmba lapmiga klalaa ndina man wungi taulmba nyangatnd…®.   
\p
\v 6 Njangilaa yiga Saimon Pitana man njangivat t…®nd…®. Pita nd…® kat wand…®. Njambwi nyan manda kat wuna man njangigiyam…®n. Ana nglaatnd…® waa wand…® Pita.   
\p
\v 7 Wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Kwutuwa nj…®vwana angwa ngwuk ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Ng…®ni v…®ga l…®giyangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 8 Pita nd…® kat wand…®. Wuna man njangivak kat kai wowun waa Pita wand…® maa jisas nd…® kat wand…®. M…®n kat ngu njangilapman yiweyan wuna mbaapmamba ana l…®giyam…®n waa wand…® maa Pita wand…®.  
\v 9 Njambwi nyan wuna man m…®na ke njangiga. Wuna nambu wuna taamba aywaa njangi m…®la waa wand…® maa Jisas wand…®.   
\p
\v 10 M…®na man m…®na njangiweyan kwo l…®giyam…®n. Ngwuk kat ngumba njangiweyan m…®namba kavle vak ana l…®giyand…®. Ngwut apma vat t…®giyangwuk. Ngwuk kat aywaa ana wupma wowun waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 11 Wan taamba v…®li kiyeli v…®l…®l…®k n…®mbana k…®ta nyan wun kat kamwin kwigiyand…® waa yelav…®taa ngwuk aywaa ana apma vat t…®gangwuk waa ndi kat wand…®.  
\v 12 Ndina man aywaa njangilaa nd…®na kumbula l…®nda waavwi klalaa kwusolaa nda l…®ga wand…® ndi kat. Ngwuk kat yuwa vatna angwa yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk? wand…®.  
\v 13 Wun kat s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan njambwi nyan m…®n waa wal…®gangwuk. Wovun wupma wal…®gangwuk. Wun s…®mogwi l…®ga njambwi nyan wun.  
\v 14 Wun ngwutna njambwi wun. Mat nyan vla l…®ga ngwula man njangil…®gowun. Ngwuk wupma awat sowat njangi ngwula.  
\v 15 Kan ngwuk kat nj…®vwa kwuta nyan vla yuwa vat v…®laa ngwulo wupma yiga yet…®mba ngwuk.  
\v 16 Ngwuk kat k…®ta nyaang…®t waigowun. Ngwuk awuk ngwula. Nj…®vwa kwut…®ga nyan nd…® kat nj…®vwa kwil…®ga nyana njambwi nyan ana nd…®. Ya nyan nd…® kat ay waa nyana njambwi nyan ana nd…®.  
\v 17 Wawa nyaang…®t ngwuk yelav…®k ngwula. Wutaa wan nyaang…®tmba yiga yet…®ngweyan ngwutna maawut apma vat t…®giyand…®.   
\p
\v 18 Ngwuk kat aywaa ana wowun. Wuna mbaapmamba taagaweya n…®mba v…®ga l…®gowun. Ngwula k…®ta nyan God waa tamba p…®l…®wutnja nyaang…®pmba yigiyand…®.  
\li1 K…®ta nyan wunogwinala k…®g…®nda k…®l…®ga nyan wun  
\li1 kat kavle yind…®  
\p waa tamba la nyan p…®l…®wutnd…®.   
\p
\v 19 Ng…®ni ngwula k…®ta nyan wun kat kavle yigiyand…®. Tak ngwuk kat mbukowun. Wan yindeya kavle vak v…®laa Jisas nd…® God wand…®, yaa nyana waa yelav…®kiyangwuk.  
\v 20 Ngwuk kat k…®ta nyaang…®t waigowun. Ngwuk awuk ngwula. Wuna nj…®vwa yiga agwut wowun ma kwukiya n…®mba kat apma vat yinjeyan wunkat apma vat yi vla l…®giyandi. K…®ta nyan wun kat apma vat yivat wandeyan wuna nj…®vwa yiga agwut wowun maa kwukiya nyan kat apma vat yigiyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 JUDAS JISAS KAT S∆óNJANGAT KAMWIN KWIGA L∆óND∆ó  
\p
\v 21 Jisas wan nyaang…®t ngambul…®nd…®, nd…®na maawut viyal…®nd…®, wand…®. Ngwuk awuk ngwula. Ngwutna k…®ta nyan wun kat s…®njangat kamwin kwigiyand…® waa wand…® maa  
\v 22 nd…®na mbaapmamba la n…®mba awat sowat v…®ga anda nyana waa wagalandi.  
\v 23 Nd…®na mbaapmamba la nat nyan Jisasna ngwaymba l…®nd…®. Jisas nd…® kat woviyaguga l…®nd…®.  
\v 24 Pita nd…® kat v…®laa Jisas kat wagala m…®la waa wand…®.  
\v 25 Pita wand…® maa Jisasna ngwaymba la nyan wagaland…® Jisas kat. Njambwi nyan anda nyan kat wam…®n waa wand…®.  
\v 26 Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. K…®g…®nda kwutaa njangwimba salataa kwiweya nyan kat wowun waa walaa k…®g…®nda kwutaa njangwimba taagalaa Judas Iskeriot Saimona nyan nd…® kat jisas kwind…®.   
\p
\v 27 Kwind…® maa k…®nd…®. K…®nd…® maa Seten nd…®na maawut wuleind…® maa Jisas Judas kat v…®laa wand…®. yimeya vak kwiyatapman ay m…®la waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 28 Jisas waa nyaang…®tna angwa njamb…®mba ndaa l…®ga k…®g…®nda k…®la n…®mba ana yelav…®ka l…®ndi.  
\v 29 Ndina nat n…®mba yelav…®tndi. Judas yisoga laagal…®na sanya nd…® v…®ga l…®gand…®. Pesto yaiga nandinya n…®n al…®ps…®ga k…®g…®nda klaigan…®n. Nd…® klavat anagand…® ya. Sanya lapman n…®mba kat sanya kwivat anagand…® ya waa nat n…®mba yelav…®tandi.  
\v 30 Judas k…®g…®nda k…®laa laataa wogwend…®. Tamba ngan ndand…®, wogwend…®.   
\s1 KUPI NYAANG∆óT  
\p
\v 31 Yind…® maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Wun Godna vat ndinyangu kat v…®s…®mogwil…®ga nyan wun. Njambwi nyanat tuwa vak samat t…®ga v…®giyandi. V…®laa yelav…®ka God njambwi nyana waigangwuk.  
\v 32 Wun kat v…®laa Godna s…® kwutaa katsongweyan God wuna s…® kwutaa katsogiyand…®. Samat t…®ga katsogiyand…®.  
\v 33 Wuna nyangu ngwutnogwinala s…®vla ana l…®giyowun. Samat t…®ga yiwun maa wun kat kwakiyangwuk. Tak Juda kat wowun. Yiweya kava ngwuk ana al…®ps…®ga yaigangwuk. Ngwutno ngwuk kat waigowun. Yiweya kava ana wuna kwupmba yaigangwuk.  
\v 34 Ngwuk kat mand…®p kupi vat yiga yet…®ngweya vat mbukiyowun. Awat sowat ngwuk ngwula maawupmba n…®ma vak yelav…®k ngwula. Ngwuk kat n…®ma vak yelav…®ka luwa vak vla awat sowat n…®ma vak yelav…®ka al…® ngwula.  
\v 35 Awat sowat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka t…®ngweya vak v…®laa nat n…®mba waigandi ngwuk kat. Ndi Jisasna mbaapmamba la n…®mba ndi waa waigandi waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 PITA JISAS KAT KAI WAIGAND∆ó  
\p
\v 36 Jisas wand…® maa Pita nd…® kat wand…®. Njambwi nyan m…®n andamala yimeya waa wand…® maa Jisas wand…®. Yiweya kava mbambala ana al…®ps…®ga yigiyam…®n. Samat t…®ga ng…®ni yigiyam…®n waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 37 Pita nd…® kat wand…®. njambwi nyan manda kat ana al…®ps…®ga yigiyam…®n waa wun kat wam…®n. M…®na s…® kwunapmak kat t…®ga kiyaweyan wovuna. Ana vaakiyowun waa wand…® Pita.   
\p
\v 38 Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. M…®na s…® kwunapmak kat t…®ga kiyameyan wam…®n? Wun kat. Wupma kwo wam…®n. Waweya nyaang…®t m…®n awup m…®la. Ngambi ngan wun kat njamb…® kuvut kai wam…®n maa ava nyaaga viyagand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\c 14  
\s1 GOD KAT YINEYA YAMB∆ó JISAS  
\p
\v 1 Jisas nd…®na mbaapmamba la n…®mba kat wand…®. Ngwuk n…®ma maawut ke yelav…®ka l…®ngwa. God njambwi nyana n…®n kat v…®ga l…®giyand…® waa yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk. Wuno wun kat wupma yelav…®a al…® ngwula.  
\v 2 Wuna nyaek t…®ga kava n…®ma sakwat t…®l…® kava l…®gand…®. T…®l…® kava t…®lapman t…®gendan ngwuk kat mbukewun. T…®ngweya kava yiga kwunakiyowun.  
\v 3 Yiga t…®ngweya kava kwunataa ngwuk kat kalivat at yaigowun. Ngwuk kat kaliwun mala wunai t…®ga kavamba k…®ta vat yet…®giyan…®n.  
\v 4 Yiweya kava ngwuk v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Yiweya ava yamb…® ngwuk v…®ga l…®gangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 5 Wand…® maa Tomas nd…® kat wand…®. Njambwi nyan yimeya kava n…®n ana v…®ga l…®gan…®n. yimeya ava yamb…® n…®n anda vapmba v…®giyan…®n waa wand…® maa Jisas wand…®.   
\p
\v 6 Wun wunay…® ava yamb…®. Wun savagu l…®ga nyaang…®t angwa nyaang…®t mbut…®ga nyan wun. Wun ndinyangu kat apma vat yiga yet…®njeya vak kwil…®ga nyan wun. Wuna nyaek t…®ga kava wuleinjeya nat yamb…® kai. Wun wunay…® ava yamb…®. Nat ava yamb…® kai. Ava yamb…® k…®tak.  
\v 7 Wuna angwa vak kat v…®ga l…®gengwan wuna nyaek kat v…®ga l…®gengwuk. Samat t…®ga wuna angwa vak v…®laa nd…® kat v…®ga l…®l…®giyangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 8 Jisas wand…® maa Filip nd…® kat wand…®. Njambwi nyan m…®na nyaek kat n…®n kat v…®s…®mogwi m…®la. V…®vat wan…®n. Nd…® kat v…®laa nat nda kat ana wagalagiyan…®n waa wand…® Filip.   
\p
\v 9 Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Tamba ngwutnogwinala nj…®mbla nj…®mbla t…®l…®gowun. Filip tuwa vak ana v…®ga l…®gam…®n? Wun kat va nyan wuna nyaek kat tamba v…®nd…®. M…®na nyaek kat n…®n kat v…®s…®mogwi m…®la waa manda kat wam…®n.  
\v 10 Wun wuna nyaeknonala k…®ta lulu t…®gali. Ngwuk wupma ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk? Ngwuk kat mbutuwa nyaang…®t wunai yelav…®ka l…®ga vapmba ana mbut…®gowun. Wuna nyaek wuna maawupmba t…®nd…®, mbut…®gowun. Kwutuwa nj…®vwana angwa nd…®namba l…®gand…®.  
\v 11 Jisas nd…®na nyaeknonala k…®ta lulu t…®gamb…®t waa yelav…®k ngwula. Wupma yelav…®tapman yingweyan kwutuwa n…®ma nj…®vwa v…®laa Jisas nd…® njambwi nyana waa yelav…®ka al…® ngwula.   
\p
\v 12 Ngwuk kat nyaang…®t k…®ta waigowun. Ngwuk awuk ngwula. K…®ta nyan njambwi nyanat tuwa vak kat yelav…®ka l…®ndeyan kwutuwa nj…®vwa vla nd…®no kwukiyand…®. Kan k…®pma kwagalalaa wuna nyaek t…®ga kavat yiwun maa wunai kwut…®ga nj…®vwa nd…® kwulaka kwukiyand…®.  
\v 13 Ngwuk kat kwagalalaa nyinangwut yiwun mala wuna s…® waga wuna nyaek kat wagalangweya nda ngwuk kat kwigiyowun. Wunamba klalaa wuna nyaekna s…® kwutaa katsogiyangwuk.  
\v 14 Wuna s…® waga wuna nyaek kat wagalangweya nda ngwuk kat kwigiyowun.   
\s1 GODNA WAAGAN YAIGA VAK  
\p
\v 15 w Wun kat woviyaguga l…®ngweyan wunai waa nyaang…®pmba yiga yet…® ngwula.  
\v 16 Nyaek kat wagalawun mala ngwuk kat kwunat…®giya nyan kwigiyand…®. Wan nyan ngwutnogwinala nj…®mbla nj…®mbla kwunaka t…®giyand…®.  
\v 17 Wan nyan Godna waagana. Nd…® apma maawut kwil…®ga nyana. Nd…®namba klalaa apma vak yelav…®ka l…®giyangwuk. Kan k…®pmamba l…®ga kwo n…®mba kat ana yaigand…®. Kwo n…®mba nd…® kat ana v…®giyandi. Nd…®na s…® wuka nd…®na m…®ndama v…®ga ana l…®gandi. Ngwuk v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Ngwutnogwinala t…®gand…®. Ng…®ni ngwutna maawupmba t…®giyand…®.   
\p
\v 18 Ngwus…® nyangu vla l…®ngwangat ana ngwuk kat kwagalagiyowun. yilaa smat t…®ga lungwamataa yaigowun.  
\v 19 Samat t…®ga k…®pmamba l…®ga ndu lagwa wun kat ana v…®giyandi. Ngwuk apma maawupmba yelav…®ka wun kat v…®giyangwuk. Wun apma vat yiga yet…®l…®gowun. Ngwuk wunai yet…®ga vla yet…®giyangwuk.  
\v 20 Yaweya nandinyamba v…®giyangwuk. Wun God vla tuwa vak kat v…®giyangwuk. Wuna yelang…®mba l…®ngwangat v…®giyangwuk. Ngwutna maawupmna luwa vak vla wuna yelang…®mba l…®gangwuk.  
\v 21 K…®ta nyan wunai waa nyaang…®t wutaa kwutaa l…®ndeyan wan nyan woviyaguga l…®nda vak v…®l…®gowun. K…®ta nyan wunkat woviyaguga l…®ndeyan wuna nyaek nd…® kat woviyaguga l…®giyand…®. Wuno nd…® kat woviyaguga l…®giyowun. Wan nyan kat yetuwa vak v…®s…®mogwi kiyowun. V…®s…®mogwiwun maa wuna angwa vak v…®giyand…®.   
\p
\v 22 Judas Jisas kat wand…®. (Jisas kat kwutnjangat kamwin kwiya Judas Iskeriot ana nd…®. Nat Judas.) Nd…® wand…®. Njambwi nyan. Ng…®ni ngwuk kat yetuwa vak v…®s…®mogwiweyan kwo l…®ga n…®mba ana v…®giyandi waa wam…®n. Anda vatna v…®lapman yinjeya waa wand…® Judas.  
\v 23 Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. K…®ta nyan wun kat woviyaguga l…®ndeyan wunai waa nyaang…®pmba yet…®giyand…®. Wan nyan kat wuna nyaek woviyaguga l…®giyand…®. Wunagwio wuna nyaekno yalaa nd…®na maawupmba t…®giyali. Kwo l…®ga n…®mba ana v…®giyandi.  
\v 24 K…®ta nyan wun kat kai wandeyan wunai waa nyaang…®pmba ana yet…®giyand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga ana v…®giyandi. Wawa nyaang…®t wuna maawupmba ana wowun. Wun kat nyaek ay m…®la wand…® maa ywawun. Wawa nyaang…®t nd…®namba klawun.   
\p
\v 25 Mbambala ngwulogwinala yetuwa nj…®mbla wan nyaang…®t mbut…®gowun.  
\v 26 Ng…®ni wuna nyaek nd…®na waagan ndi kat ay waigand…®. Wuna wug…®n t…®vak yaigand…®. Ngwula lak kwaigand…®. Ngwuk kat apma vak aywaa v…®s…®mogwi kiyand…®. Ngwutna maawut kwunatnd…® maa ngwuk kat wawa nyaang…®t kat ngwutna maawut ana t…®v…®giyand…®.   
\p
\v 27 Ngwuk kat apma maawut kwilaa kwagalalaa yigiyowun. K…®pmamba l…®ga kwo n…®mba apma maawut kwil…®nja vla ana kwigiyowun ngwuk kat. Yelav…®tuwa apma maawut ngwula lak kwagalalaa yigiyowun. Ngi kat t…®ga ngwuk n…®ma maawut ke yelav…®kngwa. Ke vaaka l…®ngwa.  
\v 28 Ngwuk kat kwagalalaa yilaa ak llungwamataa ngwuk kat yaigowun. Tamba wowun ngwuk kat. Ngwuk wuka l…®gangwuk. Wutaa manda kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk. Wunkat woviyaguga l…®gengwan wuna njambwi nyan kat wuna nyaek kat yiga v…®giyowun waa wowun maa wutaa solat s…®ga l…®gengwuk. Yiwun maa wuna nyaek ngwuk kat apma nglei vat yigiyand…® waa wowun maa solat s…®ga l…®giyangwuk.  
\v 29 Yiweya vak kat tak ngwuk kat mbukwun. Ng…®ni yigiyowun. Yiwun maa yelav…®kiyangwuk. Tak n…®n kat mbutnd…® yindeya vak. Nd…® njambwi nyana waa yelav…®kiyangwuk.   
\p
\v 30 At nat njamba ngwutnogwinala n…®ma sakwat nyaang…®t ana ngambugiyowun. Kan k…®pmamba l…®ga kwo n…®mbana njambwi nyan Seten nat nyamba wuleilaa yaigand…®. Wan yaiga nyan wun kat ana al…®ps…®ga kwulakiyand…®. Yalaa wun kat kwutndi maa v…®laa n…®ma maawut wana yelav…®kngweya. Nd…® ana kwulakiyand…®.  
\v 31 Wun wuna nyaek kat woviyaguga l…®gowun. Nd…®na kwundi wuka l…®gowun. Nd…® kat woviyaguga luwa vak nd…®na kwundi wuka luwa vak kat k…®pmamba la n…®mba v…®njangat wowun. Laataa yigiyan…®n waa wand…® Jisas.   
\c 15  
\s1 JISAS ANGWA MI VLA L∆óGAND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 Jisas wand…®. Wun apma k…®l…®nja s…®tna mina angwa vla l…®gowun. Nat nyan wupma kai. Wun wunay…® k…®ta. Wuna nyaek mi kat v…®ga l…®ga nyan vla l…®gand…®.  
\v 2 Wunamba l…®ga nyan mi sand…® vla l…®gand…®. Sik kwalapman yil…®ga sand…® wuna nyaek yalaa kal…®taa yaagil…®gand…®. S…®k kwal…®ga sand…® samat kal…®taa kwunat…®gand…®. Kwunatnd…® maa s…®k n…®ma sakwat kwaigand…®.  
\v 3 Ngwuk kat mbutuwa nyaang…®t ngwutna maawut tamba kwunatnd…® maa kwo l…®ga ngwuk.  
\v 4 Wuna mbaapmamba l…®ga wun kat ke kwagalangwa. Wun ngwutna maawupmba yet…®giyowun. Mi sand…® kapma l…®ndeyan s…®k ana kwaigand…®. Mi sand…® angwo l…®ndeyan s…®k kwaigand…®. Ngwutno wungivat s…®g…®t. Wuna mbaapmamba t…®lapman yingweyan apma nj…®vwa ana kwukiyangwuk.   
\p
\v 5 Wun angwa mi vla l…®gowun. Ngwuk sand…® mi vla l…®gangwuk. K…®ta nyan wuna mbaapmamba l…®ndeyan nd…®na maawupmba l…®weyan nd…® n…®ma sakwat apma nj…®vwa kwukiyand…®. Wun kat kwagalalaa kapma l…®ngweyan apma nj…®vwa ana kwukiyangwuk.  
\v 6 Nd…® k…®ta nyan wun kat kwagalalaa yindeyan kal…®tndi maa l…®ga wula l…®ga sand…® vla l…®giyand…®. Nd…® kat k…®ta l…®vwimba yisolaa yamba tugiyandi.   
\p
\v 7 Wuna mbaapmamba l…®ga mbutuwa nyaang…®t maawupmba yelav…®ka wun kat wagalangweya nda ngwuk kat kwigiyowun.  
\v 8 Ngwuk kat kwiwun maa n…®ma sakwat apma nj…®vwa kwukngweyan nat n…®mba v…®laa Godna s…® kwutaa katsogiyand…®. N…®ma sakwat apma nj…®vwa kwukngweyan wuna mbaapma n…®mba vla l…®giyangwuk.  
\v 9 Wuna nyaek wun kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka l…®nda vla ngwuk kat wuno n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka t…®gowun. Ngwuk kat yelav…®ka tuwa vak ngwula maawut ke t…®v…®nda. Nj…®mbla nj…®mbla yelav…®ka ali ngwula.  
\v 10 Mbutuwa nyaangipmba yiga yet…®ngweyan ngwuk kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka luwa vak ngwutna maawut ana t…®v…®giyand…®. Wuno wuna nyaek mbut…®nda nyaang…®pmba yiga yet…®gowun. Yet…®ga l…®ga wun kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka l…®nda wuna maawut ana t…®v…®l…®gand…®.  
\v 11 Ngwuk kat mbutuwa nyaang…®t wutaa solat s…®ga yet…®l…®mbangwuk walaa mbut…®gowun. N…®mamba solat s…®ga yet…®l…®mbangwuk walaa mbut…®gowun.   
\p
\v 12 Ngwuk kat k…®t nyaang…®t mbupmat yigowun. K…®ngi nyaang…®pmba yiga yet…®l…®mbangwuk. Ngwuk kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka al…® njwula.  
\v 13 K…®ta nyan nd…®na al…® n…®mba kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka l…®ga ndi kat t…®ga kiyandeyan wan n…®ma vatna. Nat vak wan vak kat ana kwulakiyand…®.  
\v 14 Mbutuwa nyaang…®pmba yiga yet…®ngweyan ngwuk wuna al…® n…®mba t…®giyangwuk.  
\v 15 Ndi wuna nj…®vwa kwut…®ga n…®mba ndi waa ana ngwuk kat ng…®ni waigowun. Nj…®vwa kwut…®ga n…®mba njambwi nyana maawupmba l…®ga vak ana v…®ga yelav…®ka l…®gandi. Ngwuk wupma kai. Ndi wuna al…® n…®mba ndi waa ngwuk kat wal…®gowun. Wuna nyaeknanamba wukwa nyaang…®t ngwuk kat aywaa v…®s…®mogwiwun, v…®ga wuka yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk.   
\p
\v 16 Ngwutna maawupmba wuna mbaapma ana wuleingwuk. Ygwa wowun, wuleingwuk. Yiga apma nj…®vwa kwupangwuk walaa ngwuk kat wowun. Kwukngweya nj…®vwa ana kwo vatnat t…®giyand…®. Wuna s…® waga wuna nyaek kat wagalangweya nda ngwuk kat kwigiyand…®.  
\v 17 Awat sowat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka al…® ngwula waga wowun ngwuk kat. Wan ngwuk kat wawa nyaang…®tna angwa nyaang…®t.   
\s1 KAN K∆óPMANA N∆óMBA NGWUK KAT KAI WAIGANDI  
\p
\v 18 K…®pmamba l…®ga kwo yet…®ga n…®mba ngwuk kat kai wanjeyan ngwuk yelav…®k ngwula. Tak Jisas kat kai wandi waa yelav…®k ngwula.  
\v 19 Ndina mbaapma n…®mba t…®gengwan ngwuk kat ana kai waigandi. Ngwuk kapma mbaapmamba l…®ga n…®mba ngwuk. Ngwuk kat wowun mala ndi kat kwagalalaa kapma mbaapma wuleingwuk. Ngi kat t…®ga ngwuk kat kai waigandi.  
\v 20 Tak ngwuk kat mbutuwa nyaang…®t yelav…®k ngwula. Tak wowun ngwuk kat. Nj…®vwa kwut…®ga nyan nd…®na njambwi nyan kat ana kwulat…®gand…® waa tak ngwuk kat wowun. Wun kat n…®ma vat kavle vat yil…®gandi. Ngwulo ngwuk kat wupma n…®ma vat kavle vat yigiyandi. Wuna nyaang…®t wupmak kat ndi kai wandi. Ngwulo ngutnai mbut…®giya nyaang…®t wupmak kat ndi kai waigandi.  
\v 21 Wun kat ay waa nyan kat ndi ana v…®ga l…®gandi. Ngi kat t…®ga wuna s…® waga yiga yet…®ngweyan ngwuk kat n…®ma vat kavle vat yigiyandi.   
\p
\v 22 Ndi kat yalaa wan apma nyaang…®t mbutapman yingweyan kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®nja vak ana v…®gendi. Tamba yalaa mbukwun maa v…®ga l…®gandi. Kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®na vak ana maawupmba yelav…®tn…®n waa ana al…®ps…®ga waigandi.  
\v 23 Wun kat kai wal…®ga nyan wuna nyaang…®k kat kai waigand…®.  
\v 24 Ndi kat yalaa kwutuwa nj…®vwa tak yaa nyan wupma ana kwutnd…®. Wupma kwutapman yigewan kavle vak yiga yet…®l…®nja vak ana v…®gendi. Mbambala ndina kavle vat tamba v…®ga l…®gandi. V…®laa wunogwi wuna nyaek kat kai wal…®gandi.  
\v 25 Ndina tamba la nyan God wand…®, p…®l…®wutnda nyaang…®pmba ndi wungi vapmba yiga yet…®ndi.  
\p Wun kat kwo kai wandi. Angwa kai waa tamba p…®l…®wutnd…®.   
\p
\v 26 Ng…®ni nyaek kat wagalawun maa ngwuk kat kwunat…®ga nyan kat ay wand…® maa ngwuk kat yaigand…®. Nd…® Godna waagana. Nd…® Godno k…®ta vat t…®ga nyana. Nd…® savagu l…®ga apma nyaang…®t mbut…®ga nyana. Ngwuk kat yalaa wunai mbut…®ga vak vla ngwuk kat mbukiyand…®. Mbutnd…® maa wuna vak v…®ga l…®giyangwuk.  
\v 27 Ngwutno nat n…®mba kat wunai mbut…®ga vak vla mbukiyangwuk. Tak wunogwinala t…®ngwuk. Wuna nj…®vwa lakna nj…®mbla wunogwinala t…®ngwuk. Mbambala wunogwinala t…®ga wuna nj…®vwa kwuselakwun maa v…®ga l…®gangwuk. V…®l…®ngwa vak mbukiyangwuk.   
\c 16  
\p
\v 1 Maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®ngwa vak wata kwagala l…®ngweya. Ngivak kat t…®ga kan nyaang…®t ngwuk kat wowun.  
\v 2 Ng…®ni God kat yelav…®pmak yisolaa l…®nja ngay ngwuk ana wuleigiyangwuk. Juda ngwuk kat kai walaa k…®klindi maa ng…®ni ana wuleigiyangwuk. Godna nj…®vwa kwupmak ndi kat vatnyagiyan…®n waa ngwuk kat waigandi.  
\v 3 Wuna nyaek at ana v…®ga l…®gandi. Wuno wun kat ana v…®ga l…®gandi. Ngi kat t…®ga kavle vat n…®ma vat ngwuk kat yigiyandi.  
\v 4 Ng…®ni yaiga vak kat mbambala ngwuk kat mbukowun. Ng…®ni wan vak yand…® maa yelav…®kiyangwuk. N…®n kat mbutnda vak tamba yaand…® waa yelav…®kiyangwuk. Tak ngwuk kat ana mbukwun. Ngwuk kat kwagala m…®na l…®ga kan mbukowun.   
\s1 GODNA WAAGAN KWUTA NJ∆óVWA  
\p
\v 5 Wun kat ay waa nyan t…®ga kavat yi m…®na l…®gowun. Andamala yimeya waa ngwutna k…®ta nyan ana wun kat wagalal…®gand…®. Yiweya vak kat ana yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk. Kwagalalaa yiwun mala kapma l…®ngweya vak kat m…®na yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk.  
\v 6 Yigiyowun wowun maa n…®ma vat yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk.  
\v 7 N…®ma maawut ke yelav…®ka l…®ngwa. Ngwuk kat woseka ana waigowun. Ngwuk kat kwagalalaa yiweyan apma vatna. Ngwuk kat kwagalalaa yilapman yiweyan ngwutna maawuk kat kwunakiyaa nyan ana yaigand…®. Yilaa wowun maa ngwuk kat yaigand…®.  
\v 8 Yalaa nj…®vwa kuvuk kwukiyand…®. K…®pmamba la kwo n…®mba kavle vak yiga yet…®l…®nja vak yalaa ndi kat v…®s…®mogwind…® maa v…®giyandi. Apma vat ndi kat v…®s…®mogwi kiyand…®. Maawupmba l…®ga vak v…®laa s…®ga nagugiyand…®.  
\v 9 Ndina kavle vat anda vatna. Njambwi nyanat tuwa vak ana yelav…®ka l…®ndi. Kan kavle vatna.  
\v 10 Ngwuk kat kwagalalaa wuna nyaek t…®ga kava yigiyowun. Yiwun maa k…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mba kat apma vat s…®mogwigiyaa nyan kai. Ngi kat t…®ga yaiga nyan ndi kat apma vat s…®mogwi kiyand…®.  
\v 11 Wan nyan yalaa k…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mba s…®ga nagul…®nja vak kat kai walaa kavle vak apma vak s…®magalaa savagu vapmba s…®ga nagugiyand…®. S…®ga nagund…® maa k…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mba v…®laa yelav…®kiyandi. N…®na njambwi nyan kavle maawut yelav…®ka l…®gand…® waa yelav…®kiyandi.   
\p
\v 12 Ngwuk kat mbukweya n…®ma sakwat nyaang…®t k…®ngi l…®ga. Ngwuk kat mbukweya mbambala ana yelav…®kiyangwuk.  
\v 13 Ng…®ni apma maawut kwil…®ga nyan Godna waagan yalaa ngwuk kat apma maawut kwind…® maa yelav…®ka l…®giyangwuk. Avla nd…®nai yelav…®kiyaa vapmba ana ngwuk kat mbukiyand…®. Wunamba wutnda nyaang…®t yiga ngwutnamba mbukiyand…®. Ng…®ni yaiga vak ngwuk kat v…®s…®mogwi kiyand…®.  
\v 14 Wuna s…® kwutaa katsogiyand…®. Wunamba wutnda nyaang…®t yiga ng…®ni ngwutnamba mbutnd…® maa wutaa yelav…®ka l…®giyangwuk.  
\v 15 Wuna nyaek ta vak aywaa v…®ga kwutaa l…®gowun. Ngivak kat yelav…®taa wowun. Wunamba wutnda nyaang…®t yiga ngwutnamba mbutind…® maa wutaa yelav…®ka l…®giyangwuk waa wowun.   
\s1 NGLALAA L∆óGA NG∆óNI SOLAT S∆óGIYANGWUK  
\p
\v 16 Samat t…®ga wun kat ana v…®giyangwuk. T…®ga l…®ga ng…®ni nat njamb…® v…®giyangwuk. Wuna nyaek t…®ga kava yivat t…®gowun waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 17 Jisas wand…® maa nd…®na mbaapmamba la nat n…®mba wandi. Samat t…®ga wun kat ana v…®giyangwuk. T…®ga l…®ga ng…®ni wun kat nat njamb…® v…®giyangwuk. Wuna nyaek t…®ga kava yivat t…®gowun waa manda kat wand…® waa wandi.  
\v 18 Samat t…®ga v…®giyangwuk waa wanda nyaang…®t manda kat wand…®. N…®n ana yelav…®ka l…®gan…®n waa wandi.   
\p
\v 19 Jisas kat wagalavat yelav…®ka l…®nja vak v…®laa ndi kat Jisas wand…®. Awat sowat ngambuga manda kat wagala l…®gangwuk. Samat t…®ga wun kat ana v…®giyangwuk. T…®ga l…®ga ng…®ni wun kat nat njamb…® v…®giyangwuk waa wawa vak kat manda kat yelav…®t…®gangwuk.  
\v 20 Ngwuk kat woseka ana wawun. Yiwun maa n…®ma vak yelav…®ka nglaigangwuk. Yiwun ma k…®pmamba la kwo n…®mba ndi solat s…®giyandi. N…®ma vak yelav…®ka nglangwa vak ng…®ni ng…®l…®giyand…®. Ng…®ni solat s…®giyangwuk.  
\v 21 Kan vak taagwa nyan kwupmat t…®ga t…®la vak k…®ta vatna. Nyan kwupmak t…®la nj…®mbla ana solat s…®l…®gal…®. Kavle vat t…®l…®gal…®. Ng…®ni nyan kwutaa n…®ma vak solat s…®ga tak t…®la kavle vak maawut t…®v…®giyal…®. Wun nyan tamba kwukwun, kwo l…®gand…® waa yelav…®ka solat s…®ga l…®giyal…®.  
\v 22 Mbambala n…®ma vak yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk. Ng…®ni ngwuk kat yaa v…®wun ma solat s…®giyangwuk. Solat s…®ngweya vak k…®ta nyan ana viyesendagiyand…®.  
\v 23 Wan yaiga nandinya n…®mamba solat s…®ga k…®ta nda kat wun kat ana wagalgiyangwuk. Ngwuk kat nyaang…®t k…®ta waigowun. Awuk ngwula. Mbambala wuna s…® waga wuna nyaek kat wagalangweya nda nd…® kwigiyand…®.  
\v 24 Tak wupma ana wagalangwuk. Wagala ngwula. Wagalangweya vapmba klaigangwuk. Klalaa n…®mamba solat s…®giyangwuk.   
\s1 JISAS K∆óPMANA VAK KAT KWULAT∆óGAND∆ó  
\p
\v 25 Mbambala ngwuk kat pagwuga nyaang…®t nandinya nandinya mbut…®gowun. Ng…®ni yaiga nj…®mbla pagwuga mbukwa nyaang…®t kwagalalaa kapmba wuna nyaekna vak kat mbukiyowun ngwuk kat.  
\v 26 Wan yaiga nandinya wuna s…® waga wuna nyaek kat avla wagalagiyangwuk. Ngwutna n…®nd…®mba l…®ga ngwuk kat t…®ga ana wagalagiyowun. Ngwuk avla wagalgiyangwuk. Nd…® wukiyand…®.  
\v 27 Nd…® ngwuk kat woviyaguga l…®gand…®. Wukiyand…®. Wunkat woviyaguga yelav…®ka l…®ngwa vak kat wuna nyaek v…®laa ngwuk kat woviyaguga l…®gand…®.  
\v 28 Tak wuna nyaek t…®ga kavamba t…®wun. kwagalalaa wuna nyaek t…®ga kavat lungwamataa yigiyowun waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 29 Jisas wand…® maa nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba nd…® kat wandi. Pagwula l…®ga nyaang…®t ana mbut…®gamb…®n. Kapmba l…®ga nyaang…®t m…®na mbut…®gan…®n.  
\v 30 N…®n v…®ga l…®gan…®n. N…®ma nambuo l…®ga nyan m…®n. Nambu klavat nat n…®mba kat ana wagalgiyam…®n. Apma nambu l…®ma vak v…®laa yelav…®t…®gan…®n. Godno t…®ga yam…®n waa v…®l…®gan…®n waa wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wagaland…®.   
\p
\v 31-32 Njambwi nyanat tuwa vak ngwuk wun kat v…®ga l…®gangwuk? Kai? Ng…®ni yaiga nj…®mbla tamba ngway tologand…®. Ngwuk kat n…®ma vat yindi ma ngwuk kava kava vaaka yigiyangwuk. Wun kat kwagalangwuk maa kapma t…®giyowun. Kapma ana l…®giyowun. Wuna nyaek wunogwinala t…®giyand…®.  
\v 33 Apma vat yelav…®ka l…®mbangwuk waa wan nyaang…®t ngwuk kat mbut…®wun. K…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mba ngwuk kat n…®ma vat yigiyandi. Ngwuk wata yelav…®ka l…®ngweya. Ndi kat tamba kwulakwun waa wand…® Jisas. Walaa God kat wand…®.   
\c 17  
\s1 JISAS ND∆óNA MBAAPMA N∆óMBA KAT T∆óGA GOD KAT WAGALAND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 Jisas tanamb…®ka nyinangwutnat v…®laa nd…®na nyaek kat wagaland…®. Wuna nyaek, yaiga nj…®mbla tamba yalaa l…®gand…®. Ndi kat njambwi nyanat tuwa vak v…®s…®mogwimba m…®n. Ndi kat v…®s…®mogwim…®n, wun m…®na nyan m…®na s…® kwutaa katsowun maa v…®ga wukiyandi.  
\v 2 K…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mbana njambwi nyanat tuwangat wun kat kwondu kwim…®n. Wun kat kwima n…®mba kat nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat yiga yet…®njeya vak kwiwangat wun kat kwondu kwim…®n. Ngi kat t…®ga wun kat kwima kwondu ndi kat s…®mogwi m…®la.  
\v 3 Nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vak yiga yet…®njeya vak k…®ngiyan. M…®n God apma nyan m…®n. M…®nai l…®ga vla l…®ga nyan ana l…®gand…®. M…®n njambwi nyan k…®ta l…®gam…®n. M…®na s…® wuka m…®na m…®ndama v…®ga wuno wun kat Jisas Kraist ay wama nyan wun wuna s…® wuka wuna m…®ndama v…®ga l…®l…®njeyan apma vak yet…®giyandi.   
\p
\v 4 Kan k…®pmamba yalaa wunkat wama nj…®vwa tamba kwutnyagiwun. Wama nj…®vwa kwutaa m…®na s…® kwutaa kwosowun.  
\v 5 Tamba kan k…®pma ana l…®nd…®, wun tamba n…®ma nyanat t…®wun. Nyaek, tamba njambwi nyanat tuwa vak wun kat nat njamb…® agwi m…®la.   
\p
\v 6 Kan k…®pmamba l…®ga wam…®n maa wun kat yaa n…®mba ndi kat m…®nai l…®ga vat s…®mogwiwun. Tak ndi m…®na nyanguat t…®ndi. Ndi kat wuna lak kwim…®n. M…®nai kwiya nyaang…®t maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa yi ya yet…®l…®gandi.  
\v 7 Kwutuwa nj…®vwa m…®nai yelav…®ka l…®ga vapmba kwut…®gowun. Ndi tamba v…®ga wuka l…®gandi.  
\v 8 Wun kat mbupma nyaang…®t ndi kat tamba mbukwun maa tamba wuka l…®gandi. M…®nai l…®ga kavamba l…®ga wam…®n maa yaa nyan wun. Wuka l…®gandi.   
\p
\v 9 Ndi kat t…®ga m…®n kat wagalal…®gowun. Kan k…®pmamba l…®ga kwo n…®mba kat t…®ga ana wagalal…®gowun. Wun kat kwima n…®mba kat t…®ga m…®n kat wagalal…®gowun. Wun kat kwima n…®mba kat t…®ga m…®n kat wagalal…®gowun. M…®na n…®mba ndi.  
\v 10 M…®na n…®mba wuna n…®mba ndi. Njambwi nyanat tuwa vak v…®ga l…®ga wuna s…® kwutaa katsol…®gandi.   
\p
\v 11 M…®na lak yavat kan k…®pma tamba kwagala m…®na l…®gowun. Ndi kan k…®pmamba kwagalalaa yawun, kapma l…®giyandi. Wuna apma nyaek m…®na kwondumba wun kat kwima n…®mba kat awup m…®la. Wam…®n maa ndi k…®ta vat yet…®giyandi. M…®n wun k…®ta vat yet…®lia vla yet…®giyandi. Wun ndi kat kwagalalaa m…®na lak yaigowun.  
\v 12 Ndinogwinala kan k…®pmamba tuwa nj…®mbla ndi kat m…®na kwondumba kwutaa l…®wun. Wun kat kwima n…®mba ndi kat apma vak v…®ga l…®wun. Ndi aywaa apma vat t…®gandi. Ndinagwi l…®ga k…®ta nyan m…®na kavle yind…®. Nd…® kavle nyana. Tamba la nyan p…®l…®wukna vapmba nd…® kavle vat yind…®.  
\v 13 Mbambala ndi kat kwagalalaa m…®na lak ya m…®na l…®gowun. M…®n kat wagalaluwa nyaang…®t wutnjangat m…®n kat kwundimba wagalal…®gowun. Wutaa n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka l…®nja vak kwagalalaa apma vat t…®ga solat s…®giyandi. Solat s…®wa vla solat s…®giyandi.   
\p
\v 14 M…®na nyaang…®t ndi kat mbukwun. Ndi k…®pmamba la kwo n…®mbagwi k…®ta vat ta n…®mba ana ndi. Kapma nyan tuwa vla ndino wuna mbaapmamba la n…®mba kapma n…®mba ndi. Kan k…®pmamba l…®ga kwo n…®mba ndi kat kai wal…®gandi.  
\v 15 Ndi kat kwutaa nat kavat kali waa m…®n kat ana wagalawun. Kan k…®pmamba t…®giyandi. Ndi kat Seten yaa kavle vat yiland…® walaa m…®n kat wagalal…®gowun.  
\v 16 Ndi kan k…®pmana n…®mba ana ndi. Ndi kapma ngepma n…®mba ndi. Kapma ngepmana nyanat tuwa vla ndino kapma ngepmana n…®mba ndi.  
\v 17 M…®nai yelav…®ka l…®ga apma nyaang…®t ndi kat s…®mogwi. S…®mogwim…®n maa wutaa nat vat kwagalalaa m…®na nj…®vwa m…®na kwuka yet…®giyandi.  
\v 18 Wun kat ay wam…®n yawa vla ndi kat ay wowun, ngepma ngepma yigiyandi.  
\v 19 Ndi kat kwunapmak nat vak kwagalalaa wama nj…®vwa m…®na kwuka yet…®giyowun. Ndino m…®na apma nyaang…®t wutaa nat vak kwagalalaa m…®na nj…®vwa m…®na kwuka yet…®giyandi.   
\p
\v 20 M…®n kat k…®nd…®gi n…®mba kat t…®ga m…®na ana wagalal…®gowun. Yiga wuna s…® mbutndi maa wutaa maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®giyaa n…®mba kat t…®ga m…®n kat wagalal…®gowun.  
\v 21 Ndi aywaa k…®ta mbaapmamba t…®mbandi walaa m…®n kat wagalal…®gowun. Nyaek m…®nagwi wunogwi k…®ta lulu t…®lia vla ndino wupma anogwi k…®ta lulu t…®mbandi walaa m…®n kat wagalal…®gowun. Wupma k…®ta lulu l…®njeyan kwo l…®ga n…®mba t…®nja vak kat v…®laa yelav…®kiyandi. Jisas God wand…®, yaa nyana waa yelav…®kiyangi.  
\v 22 Wun kat kwima apma vak ndi kat tamba kwiwun. Klalaa m…®nogwi wunogwi k…®ta lulu t…®lia vak vla ndino anogwi k…®ta lulu t…®giyandi.  
\v 23 M…®n m…®nai waa vak wuna maawupmba t…®gand…®. Wun wunai waa vak ndina maawupmba t…®gand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga k…®ta vapmba apma vak yet…®giyandi. Nat n…®mba yetnjjeya apma vak kat v…®laa yelav…®kiyandi. Jisas God wand…®, yaa nyana. God nd…®na nyan kat woviyaguga l…®nda vla ndino ndi kat woviyaguga l…®gand…® waa yelav…®kiyandi.   
\p
\v 24 Nyaek wun kat kwima n…®mba wunai yet…®giya kava yet…®mbandi walaa m…®n kat wagalal…®gowun. Tamba k…®pma ana l…®nd…®, wun kat woviyaguga l…®ga wun kat n…®ma kwondu kwim…®n. Wunai l…®giya kava yalaa kwima kwondu v…®laa yelav…®t…®mbandi walaa m…®n kat wagalal…®gowun.  
\v 25 Apma vat t…®ga wuna nyaek, kan k…®pmamba l…®ga kwo n…®mba m…®n kat ana v…®ga l…®gandi. Wun m…®n kat v…®ga l…®gowun. K…®ndi wunogwi l…®ga n…®mba ndi v…®ga l…®gandi m…®n kat. Ay wam…®n, yaa nyan wun ndi tamba v…®ga l…®gandi.  
\v 26 M…®na vat ndi kat tamba v…®s…®mogwiwun. V…®s…®mogwiluwa vat ana ng…®l…®nd…®. Nat njamb…® v…®s…®mogwigiyowun. Wun kat woviyaguga l…®ma vla ndino ndi kat woviyaguga l…®ma vak v…®mbandi walaa m…®n kat wagalal…®gowun. Wun ndina maawupmba t…®mbawun walaa m…®n kat wagalal…®gowun waa wagaland…® Jisas.   
\c 18  
\s1 JISAS KAT S∆óNJANGAT KAMWIN KWIND∆ó JUDAS  
\p
\v 1 Jisas wagaland…® maa nd…®na mbaapma n…®mbonala wan kava kwagalalaa Kidron wal…®nja ndandang…® s…®wuka val…®gendi. Val…®gelaa apma mi wata la kavat wuleindi.  
\v 2 Wuleinja kava Jisas kat kamwin kwiya nyan Judas nd…®no v…®ga l…®nd…®. Jisas nd…®na mbaapma n…®mbonala wan kava n…®ma sakwat njamb…® yil…®ndi.  
\v 3 God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mba Ferisio wandi maa njambwi la soldia kwo soldia kat wand…® maa Judasonala k…®ta vat yindi. Lam tuway n…®mbi nda kwutaa yindi Jisas kat kwupmat.  
\v 4 Jisas nd…® kat kavle vat yinjeya vak tak v…®ga l…®nd…®. Ngi kat t…®ga yiga wogwega ndi kat v…®nd…®. V…®laa wand…®. Anda nyan kat kwat…®gangwuk waa wand…® maa wandi.   
\p
\v 5 Jisas Nasaretna nyan kat kwat…®gan…®n waa wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Wunay…® waa wand…®. Kamwin kwiya Judas yaa soldiana n…®nd…®mba l…®nd…®.  
\v 6 Wunay…® waa wand…® maa ndi kwup man veilaa vaaka k…®pmamba ndandi.  
\v 7 Ndandi maa Jisas ndi kat wagaland…®. Ngwuk kanda kat kwaka yangwuk waa wagaland…® ma ndi wandi. Jisas Nasaretna nyan kat kwaka nyan…®n waa wandi.  
\v 8 Wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Wunay…®. Tamba ngwuk kat wowun. Wun kat kwat…®gangwuk. Wunogwinala l…®ga n…®mba kat ke kwukngweya. kwat…®ngwa nyan wunay…® waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 9 Tak Jisas nd…®na nyaek kat wand…®. Wun kat kwima n…®mba kat apma vak v…®ga l…®wun. ndina k…®ta nyan ana kavle vat yind…®. Jisas tak wanda nyaang…®t kat yelav…®taa wand…®. Ndi kat ke kwukngweya wand…®.   
\p
\v 10 Saimon Pita nd…® yaak ngway avamba sandalaa yind…®. Yaak kwutaa God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi nyana nj…®vwa kwut…®ga nyana waan kal…®tnd…®. Yaagindan naang…®mba la waan kal…®tnd…®. Waan kal…®tnda nyana s…® Malkus.  
\v 11 Pita kal…®tnd…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Wa yaak m…®na ngway avamba sanda. Wuna nyaek kwiya kavle vak kwindeyan wan kavle vak klaigowun. Ke kavle vak kwindeyan wan kavle vak klaigowun. Ke yelav…®ka waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 JISASANAS KAT KALINDI  
\p
\v 12 Judana njambwi soldia nat kwo soldia Jisas kat twutaa taamba ngilaa kwutaa kalindi.  
\v 13 Anas wal…®nja njambwi nyan kat v…®vat kalindi. Wan nj…®mbla Kaiafas God kat kwunat…®ga n…®mbana njambwi nyana. Anas Kaiafasna nasakwatna.  
\v 14 Kaiafas tak Juda kat mbutnd…®. K…®ta nyan n…®n kat t…®ga kiyand…® maa kwo l…®neyan apma vatna waa tak wand…® Kaiafas.   
\s1 JISAS KAT ANA V∆óGA L∆óGOWUN WAA WAND∆ó PITA  
\p
\v 15 Jisas kat kwutaa kalindi maa Pita ndina kwupmba yind…®. Jisasna mbaapmamba la nat k…®ta nyan nd…®no wupma yind…®. Wan nat kwupmba ya nyan kat God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi nyan v…®ga l…®nd…®. Nd…® Anasna ngay Jisasonala wuleind…®.  
\v 16 Pita nd…® ana wuleind…®. Nd…®na m…®ndama ana v…®ga l…®ndi. Ndaamangemba l…®nd…®. God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi nyan v…®ga la Jisasna mbaapmamba la k…®ta nyan wogwelaa ndaamange kat v…®ga la taagwa nyan kat walaa Pita kat nyagat kal…®nd…®.  
\v 17 Kalind…® maa ndaamange kat v…®ga la taagwat Pita kat wal…®. M…®n nd…®na mbaapmamba la nyan m…®n? Waa wagalal…® maa Pita wand…®. Wun kai waa wand…®.   
\p
\v 18 Wan ngayna nj…®vwa kwuta n…®mbo soldiana njambwi n…®mbo ya sal…®laa mbang…® tul…®ndi. Yipma yila nj…®mbla. Pita nd…®no mbang…® ya tul…®nd…®.   
\s1 NJAMBWI NYAN JISAS KAT WAGALAND∆ó  
\p
\v 19 Ngaymba l…®ga God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi nyan Jisas kat wagaland…®. Nd…®na mbaapmamba la n…®mba kat wagaland…®. Tak mbutnda nyaang…®t kat wagaland…®.  
\v 20 Wagaland…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Ndinyangu kat pagwuga ana wowun. Kapmba m…®na wowun. Juda yisolaa l…®nja ngay wuleilaa mbut…®wun. God kat kwunat…®nja ngay wuleilaa mbut…®wun. Juda nj…®mbla nj…®mbla wan ngay yisolaa l…®l…®ndi.  
\v 21 Manda kat wun kat wagala l…®gam…®n. Mbutuwa nyaang…®t wuta n…®mba ndi kat wagala. Ndi tamba wutaa yelav…®ka l…®gandi. Wagalam…®n maa m…®n kat mbukiyandi waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 22 Jisas wand…® ma njambwi soldia laataa Jisasna m…®ndamamba taamamba viyand…®. Viyaga wand…®. Ke wupma waa God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi nyan kat waa waga viyand…®.   
\p
\v 23 Viyand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Kavle vat yiweyan m…®n mbukiyam…®n. Kavle vat yilapman yiweyan wun kat manda kat viyam…®n waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 24 T…®ga l…®ga Anas wand…® maa God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi nyan Kaiafas kat kalindi.   
\s1 JISAS KAT ANA V∆óGA L∆óGOWUN WAA PITA NAT NJAMB∆ó WAND∆ó  
\p
\v 25 Pita nd…®na mbang…® ya tul…®nd…® maa nat n…®mba nd…® kat wagalandi. M…®n nd…®na mbaapmamba la nyan m…®n? Waa wagalandi maa Pita wand…®. Kai nd…®na mbaapma nyan ana wun waa wand…® Pita.  
\v 26 God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi nyana nj…®vwa kwuta nyan tak waan kal…®tnda nyana yakwa nyan Pita kat v…®laa wagaland…®. Tak apma mi wata la kavamba yiga wuleilaa Jisasonala t…®ga m…®n kat w…®wun? E? Waa wagaland…® maa Pita wand…®.  
\v 27 Kai. Wunai ana nd…®. Nat nyana v…®ma waa wand…® maa ava nyaaga viyand…®.   
\s1 PAILAT KAT JISAS KAT KWUTAA KALINDI  
\p
\v 28 Kaiafasna ngay kwagalalaa Romba la nyan n…®ma jas ndaa l…®ga ngayat kalindi Jisas kat. Tamba ngambi ngana. Ndi Juda wan ngay ana wuleindi. Pesto kat ndina nglambi tamba njangindi. Nat nglambi klavak kat kai wandi. Ana wuleindi. Nglambi klainjan wan pasova wal…®nja pestona k…®g…®nda ana k…®gendi.  
\v 29 Ngi kat t…®ga Pailat wal…®nja n…®ma jas wan ngaymba l…®ga wogwend…®. Wogwelaa Juda kat wand…®. Nd…® kat manda kat kotmak kat kiyangwuk. Manda vatna yinda waa wand…® maa nd…® kat Juda wandi.  
\v 30 Kavle vat yiga yet…®la nyanat t…®lapman t…®gendan ana nd…® kat kwutaa m…®na lak kiyain…®n waa wandi maa Pailat ndi kat wand…®.   
\p
\v 31 Ngwuk avla kwutaa kalilaa ngwutna ngepmana vapmba nagilaa ay ngwula waa wand…® maa Juda wandi. K…®ta nyan kat s…®landi walaa n…®n kat tamba wam…®n. N…®na ngepmana vapmba nagineyan nd…® kat vatnyavat t…®giyan…®n.  
\v 32 Tak Jisas nd…® kat vatnyanjeya vak tamba nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat mbutnd…®. Rom vatnyala vatna wun kat vatnyagiyandi wand…®. Jisas waa nyaang…®t tamba kak kiyand…®.   
\p
\v 33 Pailat wan kot…®nja ngay wuleilaa Jisas kat wand…®. yagwa m…®la waa wand…®. Wand…® maa Jisas wuleind…®. Wuleind…®, maa nd…® gat wagaland…®. M…®n Judana king m…®n? E? Waa wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®.   
\p
\v 34 M…®n yelav…®ka avla wagalagam…®n? Nat n…®mba m…®n kat wandi maa wagalagam…®n? Waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 35 Wand…® maa Pailat wand…®. Wun Juda ana wun. M…®na ngepma n…®mba m…®na ngepmana njambwi n…®mba m…®n kat kwutaa wuna lak kalindi. Anda kavle vatna yima waa wagaland…® maa Jisas wand…®.   
\p
\v 36 V…®ga luwa kava kan k…®pma ana nd…®. V…®ga luwa kava kan k…®pma l…®gendan wuna mbaapma n…®mba kao yiga waleagendi. Kao yiga waleandi maa Juda wun kat ana kwukendi. V…®ga luwa kava kan k…®pma ana nd…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 37 Jisas wand…® maa Pailat nd…® kat wagalandi. M…®n king m…®n? E? Waa wagaland…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. M…®n king m…®n waa ngiyambak wama. Wun nj…®vwa kwukwangat kan k…®pmamba wuna ny…®me wun kat kwut…®. Wan nj…®vwa kwupmak kan k…®pma ngaga yawun. Savagu l…®ga apma vat t…®ga nyaang…®t mbupmat yawun. Savagu maawut t…®ga n…®mba wuna nyaang…®t wuka l…®gandi waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 38 Jisas wand…® maa Pailat wand…®. Manda kat wupma wam…®n. Savagu l…®ga nyaang…®t ana v…®ga l…®gowun waa walaa Juda kat mbupmat wogwend…®. Wogwelaa ndi kat wand…®. Nd…®na kavle vat yinda vak ana wuka v…®wun.  
\v 39 Ngwutna ngepmana vak k…®ngiyan. Pasova wal…®nja pesto yal…®nja nj…®mbla naambi naambi kalabusma l…®l…®ga k…®ta nyan kat kwagalal…®gowun. Ngwut Judana kingat kwaglalu? Ngula lak yigand…®? Waa wagaland…® maa walega wandi.   
\p
\v 40 Ndi kai. Nd…® kat ke kwagalaga. Barabas kat kwagalam…®n maa n…®na lak yaand…® waa walega wandi. Barabas nat n…®mba kat s…®ga vatnyaga s…®kwut…®ga nyana. Kavle nyana.   
\c 19  
\p
\v 1 Pailat wand…® maa Jisas kat kwutaa viyandi.  
\v 2 Soldia n…®mbio l…®ga yamboy klalaa nd…®na nambumba king kwusoa hat vla kavle hat kwutaa kaalandi. King kwusoa vla yelogwen mbang…® waavwi klalaa nd…®na mbang…®mba kwusondi.  
\v 3 Kwusolaa nd…® kat nj…®ka waga viyal…®ndi. Njambwi nyan m…®n. M…®n Judana king m…®n nj…®ka waga nd…® kat taambamba viyal…®ndi.   
\p
\v 4 Pailat ngaymba l…®ga wogwelaa ndi kat wand…®. Kavle vat vinda vat wun ana v…®ga l…®gowun. Ngwuk kat kwo kiyawun waa wand…® maa Jisas alaguat wogwend…®.  
\v 5 N…®mbio la yamboy nd…®na nambumba l…®nd…®, yelogwen mbang…® waavwi kwusoga alaguat wogwend…® maa Pailat nd…® kat v…®laa Juda kat wand…®. Wan nyan kat av…® ngwula waa wand…® Pailat.   
\p
\v 6 Pailat wand…® maa wutaa God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mbogwi njambwi soldio Jisas kat v…®laa n…®ma kwundimba walega wandi. Nd…® kat diwai krosmba kaala m…®la. Diwai krosmba kaala m…®la wandi. Wandi maa Pailat ndi kat wand…®. Kavle vat yil…®nda vak wun ana v…®ga l…®gowun. Wun diwai krosmba ana kaalagiywoun. Ngwut avla ngwula lak nd…® kat kwutaa kaliga yiga diwai krosmba kaalagiyangwuk waa wand…® Pailat.  
\v 7 Pailat wand…® maa Juda nd…® kat wandi. Wan nyan wun Godna nyan wun waa wand…®. N…®na ngepma vapmba wan wanda vak kat kai wand…®. N…®na ngepma vapmba wan nyaang…®t wal…®ga nyan kat s…®l…®gan…®n waa wandi.   
\p
\v 8 Wanja nyaang…®t kat wutaa Pailat maawut viyal…®nd…® yelav…®ka l…®ga  
\v 9 kot t…®nja ngay wuleilaa Jisas kat wagaland…®. Andamba l…®ga yaa nyan m…®n waa Jisas kat wagaland…® maa Jisas nd…® kat ana wand…®.  
\v 10 Jisas nd…® kat kwundi walapman yind…® maa Pailat at nd…® kat wand…®. Manda kat wal…®wa nyaang…®t kat kulumaka walapman yil…®gam…®n. Wowun maa kwagalagiyandi. Wowun maa m…®n kat diwai krosmba kaalagiyandi. Njambwi nyanat tuwa vak ana wuka l…®gam…®n? Waa wand…® Pailat.   
\p
\v 11 Pailat wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Wun kat kavle vat yivat t…®ma kwondu Godnanamba klam…®n. Avla m…®na kwondumba ana al…®ps…®ga wun kat kavle yigiyam…®n. Wun kat kwutaa m…®n kat kalia nyan kavle vat yinda vat kavle yil…®ma vak kat kwulat…®gand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 12 Pailat wutaa Jisas kat kwagaland…®, yindeya vak kat yelav…®tnd…®. Pailat yelav…®ka l…®nda vak kat wutaa Juda nd…® kat wandi. Nd…® kat kwagalameyan njambwi nyan Sisana al…® nyanat ana l…®giyam…®n. Wan nyan wun king wun wandan Sisa kat kai wal…®gand…® waa Juda wandi.   
\p
\v 13 Wanja vak Pailat wutaa Jisas kat kwutaa alaguat kawa kalind…®. Alagumba l…®ga kot…®nja kavamba yiga ndaa l…®nd…® Pailat. Kambapmba saginja njamb…® la kavamba ndaa l…®nd…®. Juda ndina kwundi wan kavana s…® Gabata wandi.  
\v 14 Tamba n…®ma nandinya. Juda pasova wal…®nja pesto kat kwanda kwanda nda kwunat…®ndi. Pailat Jisas kat alaguat kalilaa Juda kat wand…®. Kan nyan ngwutna kinga. Nd…® kat av…® ngwula waa wand…® maa Juda n…®ma kwundimba walega wandi.   
\p
\v 15 Nd…® kat kwutaa kali. Nd…® kat kwutaa kaliga yiga diwai krosmba kaala m…®la waa walega wandi maa Pailat ndi kat wagaland…®. Ngutna kingat kwutaa diwai krosmba kaalalu waa wagaland…® ndi kat. Wagaland…® maa God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mba nd…® kat wandi. Nd…® n…®na king ana nd…®. N…®na king Sisa. Nat nyan kai waa wandi.  
\v 16 Wandi maa Pailat Jisas kat ndina lak kwind…®, nd…® kat diwai krosmba kaalanjangat. Ndina lak kwind…® maa Jisas kat kwutaa ndina lak kalindi.   
\s1 JISAS KAT DIWAI KROSMBA KAALANDI  
\p
\v 17 Jisas kiwai kros kwutaa nd…®na nyaambupmba walalaa kalind…®. Kaliga yiga nambu ava vla l…®ga nduwiat yind…®. Wan nduwina s…® Judana kwundimba Golgota waa wandi.  
\v 18 Wan nduwimba nd…® kat kwutaa diwai krosmba kaalandi. V…®l…®l…®k pal…® kat kwutaa nd…®nai la kavamba angang…® mb…®k kat diwai krosmba kaalandi. Jisas nd…® n…®nd…®mba l…®nd…®.   
\p
\v 19 Pailat nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutaa Jisasna diwai krosmba taagand…®. Jisas nasaret nyan. Judana kinga waa p…®l…®wutaa taagand…®.  
\v 20 Jisas kat kaalanja kava ngepma ngwaya. S…®vla ana nd…®. Ngi kat t…®ga wan ngepmana Juda n…®ma sakwat yalaa p…®l…®wutnda nyaang…®t kat v…®ndi. Pailat kwundi kuvuk p…®l…®wutnd…®. Judana kwundi p…®l…®wutaa Grikna kwundi p…®l…®wutaa Romna kwundi p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\v 21 P…®l…®wut…®nda nyaang…®k kat v…®laa God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mba pailat kat wandi. Judana kinga waa p…®l…®wupma nyaang…®t v…®n…®n ana nglaatnd…®. Judana king wun waa wand…® waa p…®l…®wupmeyan wovuna waa wandi maa Pailat ndi kat wand…®.   
\p
\v 22 P…®l…®wukwa nyaang…®t wupma l…®giyand…®. Ana mand…®k p…®l…®wukiyowun waa wand…® Pailat.   
\p
\v 23 Soldia Jisas kat kaalalaa nd…®na waavwi nat nda klalaa l…®galaa ang…® aynat taagandi. Nat soldia nat k…®ta ang…® waavwi kland…®. Nd…®na alagumba kwusonda waavwi v…®laa klalaa tavanja kava kat v…®levilaa l…®ndi. Tavanja kava kai.  
\v 24 Ngi kat t…®ga awat sowat ngambuga l…®gavak kat kai wandi. Satumba kasaga k…®ta nyanat klaigand…® waa ngambulaa satumba kasendi. Tamba la nyan God waa nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\li1 Wuna waavwi tangaka klal…®ndi. Wuna nat waavwi  
\li1 klavat satumba kasel…®ndi  
\p waa tamba la nyan p…®l…®wutnd…®. Tamba p…®l…®wutnda nyaang…®pmba soldia yindi.   
\p
\v 25 Jisas kat kaalanja diwai krosna nagwamba nd…®na ny…®me laataa l…®l…®. l…®la yakwa lagwo l…®lo wumba k…®ta vak t…®mb…®k. klpasna taagwa nat Maria l…®lo t…®l…®. Magdala wal…®nja ngepmana nat Maria t…®l…®.  
\v 26 Jisas nd…®na ny…®meagwi nd…®na mbaapmamba la k…®ta nyan kat v…®laa mb…®k kat wand…®. Wan nd…®na mbaapmamba la nyan k…®ta nyan kat Jisa woviyaguga l…®nd…®. Mb…®k kat v…®laa wand…®. Ny…®me kat wand…®. Taagwa, wan nyan ny…®na nyan vla l…®giyand…®.  
\v 27 Nd…®na mbaapmamba la nyan kat v…®laa wand…®. M…®n, wat taagwa m…®na ny…®meat t…®giyal…® waa mb…®k kat wanda maa wutaa ng…®ni wan nyan Jisasna ny…®me kat kwutaa nd…®na ngayat kalind…®. Nd…®na ngaymba t…®l…®l…®.   
\s1 JISAS KIYAND∆ó  
\p
\v 28 T…®ga l…®ga Jisas yelav…®tnd…®. Wuna nj…®vwa tamba ng…®l…®gand…® waa yelav…®tnd…®. Tamba la n…®mba God waa nyaang…®pmba p…®l…®wutndi. Kraist ngu kat wagalagiyand…® waa tamba p…®l…®wutndi. Jisas wan p…®l…®wutnja nyaang…®t kat yelav…®taa wuna mbanj…®ge tamba ngu kat t…®ga pund…® waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 29 Jisas wand…® maa wutaa awmba l…®ga nyingi l…®ga ngu nam…®n…®ng…® klalaa taagalaa nj…®mbwi mbaomba s…®laa Jisas kat kwusoga nd…®na t…®pmwimba taagandi.  
\v 30 Taagandi maa Jisas k…®laa wand…®. Kwutuwa nj…®vwa tamba ng…®l…®nd…® waa walaa nambu s…®landalaa wundumbu yind…®.   
\s1 SOLDIA N∆óMBI NDA KLALAA JISASNA MALAVAMBA S∆óNDI  
\p
\v 31 Wan nandinya pasova wal…®nja pesto kat kwanda kwanda kwunat…®nja nandinya. kinya nandinya nj…®vwa lapman t…®njeya nandinya. N…®ma njambiya l…®ga nandinya. Juda wan diwai krosmba la kuvut n…®mba kinya nj…®vwa lapman nandinya t…®vak kat kai wandi. Kwiyatapman vaangugiyangwuk walaa Pailat kat wandi. Wam…®n maa ndina man ava pangwutndi maa kiyandi vaangumbandi. Kwo mbaa t…®landi. Vaangumbandi wandi.  
\v 32 Wandi maa Pailat wand…® maa soldia yiga Jisasna angang…®mba la mb…®t nyana man ava pangwutndi, kiyamb…®t.  
\v 33 Jisasna man ava pangwupmak yiga nd…® kat v…®ndi. Tamba kiyand…®. Kwo ana l…®nd…®. Ngi kat t…®ga nd…®na man ava ana pangwutndi.  
\v 34 Soldia k…®ta n…®mbi nda klalaa nd…®na malava s…®nd…® maa nguogwi yelogweno salaka ndaind…®.  
\v 35 Wun wan vak tamba v…®wun. Ana woseka wowun. V…®laa wukngwangat kan nyaang…®t p…®l…®wut…®gowun. Jisas God wand…®, yaa nyana waa yelav…®kngwangat wan nyaang…®t p…®l…®wut…®gowun.  
\v 36 Wan v…®wa vak tamba la profet p…®l…®wukna vak vla l…®gand…®. Tamba p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\p Nd…®na ava ana pangwukiyandi. Waa tamba p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\v 37 Nat nyan nd…®nogwi p…®l…®wutnd…® tamba.  
\p N…®mbi ndamba s…®njeya nyan v…®giyandi. Waa tamba p…®l…®wutnd…®.   
\s1 JISASNA S∆óM KWUTAA YIGA KAMBAK TA WAANGUMBA TAAGANDI  
\p
\v 38 T…®ga l…®ga Arimatia wal…®nja ngepmamba la nyan Josep Pailat kat yand…®. Nd…® tamba Jisasna mbaapmamba la nyana. Judana njambwi n…®mba kat t…®ga vaaka l…®ga Jisasna mbaapmamba l…®nda vak kat pagwund…®. Pailat kat yalaa Jisasna s…®m kwutaa kaliga vaanguvak kat wagaland…®. Pailat nd…® kat kali wand…® maa nd…®na s…®m kwutaa kalind…®.  
\v 39 Josep nd…® kapma ana yand…®. Nat nyan Nikodimasonala yand…®. Nikodimas tak ngamba Jisas kat v…®vat yaa nyana. Apma njangu veila ngwak kwutaa yand…®. Ngwat n…®ma sakwat kwutaa kiyand…®. Wan ngwak sanya n…®ma sakwat kwilaa kland…®.  
\v 40 Jisasna s…®m kwutaa Judana vapmba njangu veil…®ga ngwak nd…®na mbang…® kulaviga kwutaa waavwimba mbaaka ngimb…®k.  
\v 41 Jisas kat kaalanja kava ngwaymba apma mi wat…®ga k…®pma l…®nd…®. Wan kavamba kaambapmba vanja waangu t…®nd…®. Tak kiya nyan kat wan waangumba ana taagandi. Kwo ta waangua.  
\v 42 S…®vla kavamba yiga vaanguvak kat nd…®na s…®m kat kai wamb…®t. Judana pesto tamba ngway tolond…®. Ngi kat t…®ga wan ngwaymba la waangumba nd…®na s…®m vaangumb…®t.   
\c 20  
\s1 JISAS KIYALAA LAATND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 Sande ngambi gleimba Magdalana taagwa Maria Jisas kat vaangunja kava v…®vat laataa yil…®. Nd…®na waangu teg…®l…®nja kambak ana l…®nd…®, v…®levilaa yil…®.  
\v 2 P…®l…®ga yiga Pitogwi Jisasonala k…®ta vak ta nyan kat wal…®. Nat nyan nd…® kat Jisas woviyaguga l…®nda nyana. N…®na njambwi nyan waangumba taagandi, l…®nd…®, nd…® kat tamba kwutaa s…®kwutaa kalindi. Kalinja kava ana v…®ga l…®gowun waa mb…®k kat mbut…®.   
\p
\v 3 Mbut…® maa Pitagwi Jisasonala k…®ta vak ta nyan laataa waangu la kavat p…®l…®ga yimb…®t.  
\v 4 P…®l…®ga yiga nat nyan Pita kat kwulaka p…®l…®nd…®. Nd…® tatak waangu la kava wuleind…®.  
\v 5 Tamblalaa yisolaa v…®nd…®. Ana wuleind…®. Jisas kat mbat…®nja kwo waavwi m…®na t…®nd…®, v…®nd…®.  
\v 6 Nd…®na kwupmba p…®l…®ga Saimon Pita yalaa wan waangu wuleilaa kwo waavwi m…®na t…®nd…® maa v…®nd…®.  
\v 7 Nd…®na nambu kamonja waavwi nat waavwi ta kavamba ana l…®nd…®. Nd…® mband…®ga laagandi, kapma kavamba l…®ndi.  
\v 8 Pita wuleind…® maa nat nyan nd…®na kwupmba wuleind…®. Wuleilaa v…®laa Jisas kiyalaa tamba laatnd…® waa yelav…®tnd…®. Jisas kiyalaa laakiyand…® waa tak ana yelav…®ka l…®nd…®.  
\v 9 Tamba la profet p…®l…®wukna nyaang…®t kwo m…®ni v…®ga l…®mb…®t.  
\p Kraist kiyalaa l…®ga laakiyand…®. Waa tamba p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\v 10 V…®laa wumb…®t nyan kwagalalaa ngegavat yimb…®t.   
\s1 MAGDALANA MARIA JISAS KAT LAATAA L∆óND∆ó, V∆óL∆ó  
\p
\v 11 Yimb…®t maa Maria mb…®tna kwupmba ana yil…®. Waangu la kavamba t…®ga l…® nglaga l…®l…®. L…®lo nglaa l…®ga tamblalaa waangu kat yisolaa v…®l…®.  
\v 12 Sawun mbang…® waavwi kwusola la ensel v…®l…®l…®k t…®mb…®k, v…®l…®. Nat ensel Jisasna s…®mna nambu la kavamba ndaa l…®nd…®. Nat ensel Jisasna s…®mna man ta kavamba ndaa l…®nd…®.  
\v 13 L…® kat v…®laa wamb…®t. Taagwa, ny…®n manda kat nglaa l…®gany…®n waa wamb…®t maa wal…®. Wuna njambwi nyana s…®m kwutaa kalinja kava ana v…®ga l…®gowun. Ngi kat t…®ga nglal…®gowun waa walaa.  
\v 14 L…®mbanda Jisas kat v…®l…®. V…®laa Jisas waa ana yelav…®t…®.   
\p
\v 15 Jisas l…® kat wand…®. Taagwa, ny…®n manda kat nglaa l…®gany…®n. Kanda kat kwaka v…®l…®gany…®n waa wand…®. Maria nd…® kat v…®laa kan k…®pma kat v…®ga l…®ga nyana waa yelav…®taa wal…®. M…®n, nd…®na s…®m kwutaa kaliga taagameyan wun kat ambuk. Wam…®n maa nd…®na s…®m kwutaa kaligiyowun waa wal…®.   
\p
\v 16 Wal…® maa Jisas l…® kat l…®la s…® wand…®. Maria wand…®. Wand…® maa l…®mbanga Jisas kat v…®laa wal…®. Judana kwundimba Rabonai wal…®. Rabonai waa s…®maga l…®ga nyan waa wal…®.   
\p
\v 17 Wal…® maa Jisas l…® kat wand…®. Wun kat ke kwuka. Wuna nyaek kat v…®vak wata ana wokewun. Wuna mbaapmamba l…®ga n…®mba kat yiga ambuk. Wun nyaek v…®vak wokevat t…®gowun. Nd…® ngwutna nyaek n…®mbun. Wuna njambwi nyan kat v…®vak wokevat t…®gowun. Nd…® ngwutna njambwi nyan n…®mbun waa ndi kat abuk ny…®la waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 18 Jisas wand…® maa Magdalana Maria Jisasna mbaapmamba la n…®mba kat yiga mbut…®. Njambwi nyan kat tamba v…®wun waa mbut…®. Jisas ndi kat yiga ambut ny…®la waa wanda nyaang…®t ndi kat mbut…®.   
\s1 JISASNA MBAAPMAMBA LA N∆óMBA ND∆ó KAT V∆óNDI  
\p
\v 19 Wan Sande nglaambu Jisasna mbaapmamba la n…®mba ngaymba wuleiga yisolaa l…®ndi. Judana njambwi n…®mba kat vaaka l…®ga mbapmo kwalalaa t…®ndi. Yisolaa l…®ndi maa Jisas ndinai la kavamba kak kiyalaa ndi kat wand…®. Ngwula maawut n…®mamba viyal…®nd…® ke t…®ngwa waa waga  
\v 20 nd…®na taambamba la paw nd…®na malavamba la paw ndi kat s…®mogwind…®. Nd…® kat v…®laa kan n…®na njambwi nyana yaa walaa nd…® kat solat s…®l…®ndi.  
\v 21 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Apma maawut yelav…®ka al…® ngwula. Wuna nyaek wun kat ay wand…®, yiwa vak vla ngwuk kat ay wagowun waa walaa  
\v 22 ndi kat mwuk v…®l…®taa wand…®. Godna waagan ngwuk klaigangwuk.  
\v 23 Nat n…®mba yiga yet…®giyaa kavle vak kat v…®laa ndi kat miwa yilaa s…®l…®mbwingweyan wan kavle vak ng…®l…®giyand…®. Ana ndinamba t…®giyand…®. Nat n…®mba yiga yet…®giyaa kavle vak kat v…®laa s…®l…®mbwilapman yingweyan ndinamba kwo l…®giyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 TOMAS JISAS KAT V∆óND∆ó  
\p
\v 24 Tak Jisas nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat kak kiyanda nj…®mbla Tomas Didimas v…®ligu nyan nd…® ana l…®nd…®.  
\v 25 Nat n…®mba nd…® kat wandi. Njambwi nyan tamba laataa yand…®, v…®n…®n. Kwo l…®gand…® wandi. Wandi maa wand…®. Ngwuk wun kat woseka wangwuk. Nd…®na taambamba l…®ga paw v…®laa wuna taamba s…®ga v…®laa nd…®na malava l…®ga paw wuna taamba s…®ga v…®weyan woseka wangwuk waa ana waigowun. V…®lapman yiweyan woseka wangwuk waigowun waa wand…® Tomas.   
\p
\v 26 Nandinya s…®la kuvuk yind…® maa Jisasna mbaapmamba la n…®mba ngayat wuleiga yisolaa l…®ndi. Wan t…®nja nj…®mbla Tomas ndinogwinala l…®nd…®. Mbapmo kwalalaa t…®ndi maa Jisas at nat njamb…® yaa ndi kat kak kiyalaa ndi kat wand…®. Apma maawut yelav…®ka al…® ngwula waa walaa.  
\v 27 Tomas kat wand…®. M…®n laataa yagwa m…®la. Wuna taambamba l…®ga paw m…®na taamba s…®ga av…®. Kiyalaa l…®ga ana laatnd…® waa yelav…®ka l…®ma vak m…®n kwagala. Kiyalaa laatnd…® waa yelav…®ka al…® m…®la waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 28 Jisas wand…® maa Tomas wand…®. Tamba yelav…®ka l…®gowun. M…®n wuna njambwi nyan m…®n. M…®n God m…®n wand…®.  
\v 29 Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Tomas wun kat m…®nimba vl…®aa njambwi nyanat tuwa vak yelav…®ka l…®gam…®n. Nat n…®mba wuna mbang…® m…®nimba v…®lapman t…®ga njambwi nyanat tuwa vak yelav…®ka l…®njeyan wundi n…®mba ndi apma nglei vat t…®giyandi waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 JON P∆óL∆óWUKNA NYAANG∆óTNA ANGWA  
\p
\v 30 Jisas nat n…®ma sakwat n…®ma nj…®vwa kwut…®nd…®, nd…®na mbaapmamba la n…®mba vl…®l…®ndi. Wan nat n…®ma sakwat nj…®vwa kat ana p…®l…®wukwun.  
\v 31 Wan p…®l…®wukwa nyaang…®t nat n…®mba v…®laa nd…® Jisas God wand…®, ndinyangu kat kwunapmak yaa nyana, nd…® Godna nyana waa yelav…®pmbandi walaa p…®l…®wukwun. Wupma Jisas kat yelav…®ka yet…®l…®njeyan nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat yiga yet…®l…®njeya vak klaigandi.   
\c 21  
\s1 JISASNA MBAAPMAMBA LA S∆óLA V∆óLI N∆óMBA JISAS KAT V∆óNDI  
\p
\v 1 T…®ga l…®ga Jisas nd…®na mbaapmamba la n…®mba kat nat njamb…® yand…® maa v…®ndi. Taibirias wal…®nja sapmba t…®ga l…®ga nd…® kat v…®ndi. V…®nja vak k…®ngiyan.  
\v 2 Jisasna mbaapmamba la ndi s…®la v…®li nyangu k…®ta mbupmba yisolaa l…®ndi. Pita, Tomas waa Didimas wal…®nja nyan, Nataniel Kena wal…®nja ngepmamba la nyan Galili nyana, Sebidina nyan v…®l…®l…®k, nat v…®l…®l…®k pal…® k…®ta mbupmba yisolaa l…®ndi.  
\v 3 Yisolaa l…®ndi maa Pita ndi kat wand…®. Kami kwupmak yigiyowun waa wand…® maa n…®no yigiyan…®n waa wandi. Njamb…®t kulaa yindi. Ngan ngan kami kwupmak kat yet…®l…®ndi.  
\v 4 Nya wokel…®nd…® maa Jisas t…®vagawimba ngaga yalaa l…®nd…®. Nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba njaamb…®pmba l…®ga nd…® kat v…®laa kwo nyana waa yelav…®ka l…®ndi.  
\v 5 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Nyangu kami kwukngwuk? Waa wand…® maa wandi. Kami kat kwatevilaa l…®gan…®n waa wandi.  
\v 6 Wandi maa wand…®. Njamb…®tna yaagindan naang…®mba njula ana tawngwuk. Yaagindan naang…®mba tawngweyan kwukiyangwuk waa wand…® maa wupma tawlaa n…®ma sakwat kami njulamba ndand…®, kwutndi. Katsovak yilavindi wan njula.   
\p
\v 7 Jisas woviuaguga l…®nda nyan Pita kat wand…®. Angwi n…®na njambwi nyana waa wand…® Pita kat. Wand…® maa wutaa tak s…®venda waavwi kwutaa kwusolaa ngumba ndaiga n…®mbu veind…®.  
\v 8 Nat n…®mba njamb…®pmba weleindi n…®mbak. Jisas kat v…®nja s…®vla 300 fit vla l…®nd…® maa m…®ndi. S…®vla ana l…®. Wan njula njaamb…®pmba ngilaa laaka klokalindi n…®mbak.   
\p
\v 9 Klokaliga kawilaa v…®ndi. Jisas ya laagalaa kami yamba tuga bret-nao n…®mbun yamba tund…®, v…®ndi.  
\v 10 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Wan kwukngwa kami njulonala laaka agiya ngwula waa wand…® maa  
\v 11 Pita laataa laaka kiyand…® n…®mbak. Kwutnja kami n…®ma sakwatna. 153 t…®nd…®. Wan njula ana ng…®l…®tnd…®.   
\p
\v 12 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Yaa ag…® ngwula waa wand…®. Nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba ng…®paliga ndalaa anda nyan m…®n waa ana wagalandi. Ndi aywaa nd…® kat tamba v…®ga l…®nd…®. Njambwi nyanat t…®nd…®.  
\v 13 Jisas yalaa bret-nao kamio kwutaa ndi kat aywaa kwind…®.  
\v 14 Jisas kiyalaa l…®ga laataa yand…® maa nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba nd…® kat v…®ndi kuvuk wan njamb…®.   
\s1 JISAS PITA KAT NJSVWA KWIND∆ó  
\p
\v 15 K…®ndi maa Jisas Pita kat wand…®. Saimon Jonana nyan wundi n…®mba wun kat woviyaguga l…®nja vak kat m…®n kwulat…®gam…®n wun kat woviyaguga l…®ma vak? Waa wagaland…® maa Pita nd…® kat wand…®. Awa luwa. M…®n kat n…®man woviyaguga l…®gowun. V…®ga l…®gam…®n waa wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Sip sip kat k…®g…®nda kwinja vla wuna nyangu kat kwunaka v…®ga al…® m…®la waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 16 V…®l…®l…®k wan njamb…® Jisas Pita kat wagaland…®. Saimon Jonana nyan wun kat woviyaguga l…®gam…®n? E? Kai? Waa wagaland…® maa Pita wand…®. Njambwi nyan m…®n kat woviyaguga l…®gowun. V…®ga l…®gam…®n waa wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Sip sip kat v…®ga l…®nja vla wuna nyangu kat kwunaka al…® m…®la.   
\p
\v 17 Kuvuk wan njamb…® Jisas Pita kat wagaland…®. Saimon Jonana nyan wun kat woviyaguga l…®gam…®n? E? Kai? Waa wagaland…® maa Pita samat k…®l…®pang…® yind…®. Yilaa yelav…®tnd…®. Wun kat manda kat njamb…® kuvuk wagaland…® waa yelav…®tnd…®. Yelav…®taa wand…®. Njambwi nyan maawupmba l…®ga vak aywaa v…®ga l…®gam…®n. M…®n kat woviyaguga luwa vak v…®ga l…®gam…®n waa wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Sip sip kat k…®g…®nda kwinja vla wuna nyangu kat kwunaka v…®ga al…® m…®la.   
\p
\v 18 M…®n kat k…®ta nyaang…®t mbutu. Awup m…®la. Tak kwand…® nyanat t…®ma nj…®mbla y…®pma yaaw s…®taa m…®na maawupmba yi ya yet…®m…®n. Ng…®ni av…®t ndu t…®meya nj…®mbla taamba kwiyalalaa l…®m…®n maa nat n…®mba m…®n kat ngilaa kaligiyandi nat kavat. M…®n kat ana wagalgiyandi. Ndina waawupmba m…®na yelav…®ka kaligiyandi waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 19 Ng…®ni Pita kiyandeya vak kat Jisas nd…® kat smogwivat wupma mbutnd…®. Kiyandeya nj…®mbla Pita Godna s…® kwutaa katsogiyand…®. Jisas wan vak walaa Pita kat wand…®. M…®n wuna kwupmba yagwa waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 JISAS JON KAT MBUTA NYAANG∆óT  
\p
\v 20 Jisasna kwupmba yiga Pita l…®mbanga Jisas woviyaguga la nyan kat v…®nd…®. Nd…® mb…®tna kwupmba yind…®. Wan nyan tat k…®g…®nda k…®l…®nja nj…®mbla Jisasna ngwaymba l…®ga Jisas kat wagaland…®. Njambwi nyan kandana kamwin m…®n kat kwigiya waa wagaland…®.  
\v 21 Pita nd…® kat v…®laa Jisas kat wand…®. Njambwi nyan an nyan ng…®ni manda vala yindeya waa wand…® Pita.  
\v 22 Pita wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Yaweya nj…®mbla kat kawiga kwo l…®ndeyan m…®na vak ana nd…®. M…®n wuna nyaang…®t wuka wawa nj…®vwa agwup m…®la waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 23 Nat n…®mba wutaa mbutseli mbutsela mbuka kalindi. Jon ana kiyaigand…® waa Jisas wand…® waa mbutseli mbutsela mbuka kalindi. Jisas wupma ana wand…®. Yaweya nj…®mbla kat kawiga kwo l…®ndeyan m…®na vak ana nd…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 24 Wan nyan wunay…®. Wunay…® wan nyaang…®t p…®l…®wukna. Woseka waga ana p…®l…®wukwun. N…®n Jisasna mbaapma n…®mba v…®ga l…®gan…®n.   
\p
\v 25 Jisas yila n…®ma sakwat vak wan vak kat ana p…®l…®wukwun. Wan vak nat n…®mba p…®l…®wutnjeyan n…®ma nglei sakwat lavu nyinga p…®l…®wukiyandi. Kava kava taakiyand…®.   